16-12-01 13:11:45','<h3>Before marrying Prince William, Kate Middleton was one of those girls who attend university to pursue a degree. But back in 2002, a wild night on ramp changed everything when she took part in a fashion show held at her university. That was the exact night when the Prince settled his mind that this is the girl of his dream, she is the ONE.</h3>\r\n<h3><strong> </strong></h3>\r\n<h3>Prince William of course fell in love with Kate by being mesmerized by her natural beauty. This dress however blew away the last doubt from the prince’s mind.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-169\" src=\"http://35.163.51.132/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/1-min-241x300.png\" alt=\"1-min\" width=\"400\" height=\"498\" /></h3>\r\n<h3><strong><!--nextpage--></strong></h3>\r\n<h3>It had not been more than three months that Kate hit the court after giving birth to George, to show her volleyball prowess. She was seen wearing a casual top and skin-tight jeggings.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-170\" src=\"http://35.163.51.132/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/2-1-209x300.jpg\" alt=\"2\" width=\"348\" height=\"498\" />\r\n<h3><strong><!--nextpage--></strong></h3>\r\n<h3>At first look it seems like she is being chased by some paparazzis. No wonder she is known as more of a ‘commoner’ than a princess.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-171\" src=\"http://35.163.51.132/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/3-min.png\" alt=\"3-min\" width=\"430\" height=\"546\" />\r\n<h3><strong><!--nextpage--></strong></h3>\r\n<h3>Kate doesn’t let go a chance to do justice to her fame as ‘princess of the people’. Here, she is attending a children’s fundraiser in a not too revealing but appealing dress.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-172\" src=\"http://35.163.51.132/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/4-min.png\" alt=\"4-min\" width=\"428\" height=\"539\" /></h3>\r\n<h3><strong><!--nextpage--></strong></h3>\r\n<h3>Perhaps she doesn’t have an agreement with the wind, like Marilyn Monroe did! This happened back in 2014 in Australia.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-173\" src=\"http://35.163.51.132/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/5-min.png\" alt=\"5-min\" width=\"367\" height=\"443\" /></h3>\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h3>It is believed that Kate is so strong willed that she won’t even bow to the Queen. Paparazzis nevertheless have no regard for that.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-174\" src=\"http://35.163.51.132/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/6-min.png\" alt=\"6-min\" width=\"429\" height=\"538\" /></h3>\r\n<h3><strong><!--nextpage--></strong></h3>\r\n<h3>In spite of being a Princess, she never shies away from enjoying life to the fullest. Wearing revealing clothes is apparently is not a big deal to her.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-175\" src=\"http://35.163.51.132/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/7-min.png\" alt=\"7-min\" width=\"432\" height=\"532\" /></h3>\r\n<h3><strong><!--nextpage--></strong></h3>\r\n<h3>We don’t know whether the queen was outraged seeing this photo. It discloses the human side of the royal family.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-176\" src=\"http://35.163.51.132/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/8-min.png\" alt=\"8-min\" width=\"608\" height=\"336\" /></h3>\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h3>There are very few photos of Kate’s baby bump. This one picture more or less makes up for that.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-177\" src=\"http://35.163.51.132/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/9-min.png\" alt=\"9-min\" width=\"595\" height=\"329\" /></h3>\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h3>Kate is definitely one of the most fashion conscious princesses that the royal family has seen. She has established her own way of clothing and style – making her easily noticeable.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-154\" src=\"http://35.163.51.132/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/10.png\" alt=\"10\" width=\"428\" height=\"549\" /></h3>\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h3>In this ‘Blue Wonder’ shot, Kate looks gorgeous and smart. She looks like a princess in one of those Disney princess movies.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-179\" src=\"http://35.163.51.132/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/11-1.jpg\" alt=\"11\" width=\"397\" height=\"530\" /></h3>\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h3>Who could be a better choice than the royal pair to improve ties between Great Britain and Australia? Here she is in a wonderful floral design dress.</h3>\r\n<h3><strong> <img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-180\" src=\"http://35.163.51.132/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/12-1.jpg\" alt=\"12\" width=\"397\" height=\"530\" /></strong></h3>\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h3>Even in a silly hat she looks great. This is perhaps the best thing about the princess of people – she looks smoking hot even in the dullest dresses.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-181\" src=\"http://35.163.51.132/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/13-1.jpg\" alt=\"13\" width=\"397\" height=\"530\" /></h3>\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h3>The Princess never loses her composure. She knows how to make quick comebacks even when caught off-guard.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-182\" src=\"http://35.163.51.132/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/14-1.jpg\" alt=\"14\" width=\"397\" height=\"530\" /></h3>\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h3>The Princess enjoys a game of cricket wearing a red velvet dress. We however could not know whether she managed to hit a few boundaries.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-183\" src=\"http://35.163.51.132/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/15-1.jpg\" alt=\"15\" width=\"397\" height=\"530\" /></h3>\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h3>Kate never falls short of fulfilling her fans’ wishes. In the meantime, she is also giving the crowd a show.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-184\" src=\"http://35.163.51.132/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/16-1.jpg\" alt=\"16\" width=\"397\" height=\"530\" /></h3>\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h3>Another picture showing how rarely the Princess cares about those camera clicks. Could it be that she knows people enjoy getting those glimpse?</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-185\" src=\"http://35.163.51.132/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/17-1.jpg\" alt=\"17\" width=\"584\" height=\"360\" /></h3>\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h3>Just like a supermodel, she is moving forward with a never dull expression in her face. Trademark Kate!</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-186\" src=\"http://35.163.51.132/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/18-1.jpg\" alt=\"18\" width=\"397\" height=\"530\" /></h3>\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h3>During the Australia tour in 2014, the Princess saw her skirt scooting up while she was holding Prince George. She just smiled and continued her steps, confidently.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-187\" src=\"http://35.163.51.132/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/19-1.jpg\" alt=\"19\" width=\"398\" height=\"530\" /></h3>\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h3>Kate wore this sweet blue while attending a red carpet, back in 2012. Anyone would admit that that body-hugging gown rocks.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-188\" src=\"http://35.163.51.132/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/20-1.jpg\" alt=\"20\" width=\"397\" height=\"530\" /></h3>\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h3>This cocktail dress matched Kate so good that there is no way to tell that she is pregnant. She knows very well just how much revealing you can be, without being slutty.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-189\" src=\"http://35.163.51.132/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/21-1.jpg\" alt=\"21\" width=\"397\" height=\"530\" /></h3>\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h3>Kate has always been known for her demure choices. This dress justifies that even more.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-190\" src=\"http://35.163.51.132/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/22-1.jpg\" alt=\"22\" width=\"397\" height=\"530\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->','22 Photos that Prove Kate Middleton is Too Hot and the Prince is a Lucky Man','','publish','open','open','','22-photos-that-prove-kate-middleton-is-too-hot-and-the-prince-is-a-lucky-man','','','2016-12-01 17:19:31','2016-12-01 17:19:31','',0,'http://35.163.51.132/?p=144',0,'post','',0),(145,2,'2016-12-01 12:54:25','2016-12-01 12:54:25','','1','','inherit','open','closed','','1-2','','','2016-12-01 12:54:25','2016-12-01 12:54:25','',144,'http://35.163.51.132/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/1.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(146,2,'2016-12-01 12:54:28','2016-12-01 12:54:28','','2','','inherit','open','closed','','2-2','','','2016-12-01 12:54:28','2016-12-01 12:54:28','',144,'http://35.163.51.132/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/2.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(149,2,'2016-12-01 12:54:38','2016-12-01 12:54:38','','5','','inherit','open','closed','','5-2','','','2016-12-01 12:54:38','2016-12-01 12:54:38','',144,'http://35.163.51.132/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/5.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(150,2,'2016-12-01 12:54:43','2016-12-01 12:54:43','','6','','inherit','open','closed','','6-2','','','2016-12-01 12:54:43','2016-12-01 12:54:43','',144,'http://35.163.51.132/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/6.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(151,2,'2016-12-01 12:54:47','2016-12-01 12:54:47','','7','','inherit','open','closed','','7-2','','','2016-12-01 12:54:47','2016-12-01 12:54:47','',144,'http://35.163.51.132/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/7.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(152,2,'2016-12-01 12:54:52','2016-12-01 12:54:52','','8','','inherit','open','closed','','8-2','','','2016-12-01 12:54:52','2016-12-01 12:54:52','',144,'http://35.163.51.132/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/8.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(153,2,'2016-12-01 12:54:55','2016-12-01 12:54:55','','9','','inherit','open','closed','','9-2','','','2016-12-01 12:54:55','2016-12-01 12:54:55','',144,'http://35.163.51.132/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/9.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(154,2,'2016-12-01 12:54:59','2016-12-01 12:54:59','','10','','inherit','open','closed'