n bow to the Queen. Paparazzis nevertheless have no regard for that.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-174\" src=\"http://35.163.51.132/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/6-min.png\" alt=\"6-min\" width=\"429\" height=\"538\" /></h3>\r\n<h3><strong> </strong></h3>\r\n<h3>In spite of being a Princess, she never shies away from enjoying life to the fullest. Wearing revealing clothes is apparently is not a big deal to her.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-175\" src=\"http://35.163.51.132/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/7-min.png\" alt=\"7-min\" width=\"432\" height=\"532\" /></h3>\r\n<h3><strong> </strong></h3>\r\n<h3>We don’t know whether the queen was outraged seeing this photo. It discloses the human side of the royal family.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-176\" src=\"http://35.163.51.132/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/8-min.png\" alt=\"8-min\" width=\"608\" height=\"336\" /></h3>\r\n<h3>There are very few photos of Kate’s baby bump. This one picture more or less makes up for that.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-177\" src=\"http://35.163.51.132/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/9-min.png\" alt=\"9-min\" width=\"595\" height=\"329\" /></h3>\r\n<h3>Kate is definitely one of the most fashion conscious princesses that the royal family has seen. She has established her own way of clothing and style – making her easily noticeable.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-154\" src=\"http://35.163.51.132/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/10.png\" alt=\"10\" width=\"428\" height=\"549\" /></h3>\r\n<h3>In this ‘Blue Wonder’ shot, Kate looks gorgeous and smart. She looks like a princess in one of those Disney princess movies.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-179\" src=\"http://35.163.51.132/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/11-1.jpg\" alt=\"11\" width=\"397\" height=\"530\" /></h3>\r\n<h3>Who could be a better choice than the royal pair to improve ties between Great Britain and Australia? Here 