 style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-289\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/27-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"27\" width=\"422\" height=\"281\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">That time she was literally so perfect that a random photograph was more beautiful than any elaborately staged magazine cover.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-290\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/26-195x300.jpg\" alt=\"26\" width=\"262\" height=\"403\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Kate can’t seem to take her eyes off her prince – she’s been shooting William several sweet looks of love throughout the tour.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-291\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/25-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"25\" width=\"367\" height=\"275\" /></span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><!--nextpage--></span></h2>','27 Photos that Prove Kate Middleton is Too Hot and the Prince is a Lucky Man','','inherit','closed','closed','','288-revision-v1','','','2016-12-11 18:51:12','2016-12-11 18:51:12','',288,'http://theladypost.com/2016/12/11/288-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(321,2,'2016-12-11 18:53:15','2016-12-11 18:53:15','<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Before marrying Prince William, Kate Middleton was one of those girls who attend university to pursue a degree. But back in 2002, a wild night on ramp changed everything when she took part in a fashion show held at her university. That was the exact night when the Prince settled his mind that this is the girl of his dream, she is the ONE.</span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-293\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/2-236x300.png\" alt=\"2\" width=\"306\" height=\"389\" /></span>\r\n<h2><span st