2><span style=\"color: #000000\">What a better way to create a scene that to have a dress made out of recycled materials. Food papers, sweet wrappers, it does not matter but ensures that it is the right color. We love this wedding dress!</span></h2>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-359\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Go-Green-244x300.jpg\" alt=\"go-green\" width=\"297\" height=\"365\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Balloon Gown</span></strong></h1>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">This balloon wedding dress is an art. The second piece of art that we have seen, but to be honest, we really love it! Sometime it is good to mix things up and change the style of the wedding dress. And this balloon wedding dress should be the first one on your mind.</span></h2>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-358\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Balloon-Gown-221x300.jpg\" alt=\"balloon-gown\" width=\"303\" height=\"411\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Camo Camp Out</span></strong></h1>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">This camo-wedding dress is something only Honey Boo Boo’s mamma could go for on her special day. For an avid hunter, this is a perfect match but not for us; we would prefer something more of ivory.</span></h2>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-355\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Camo-Camp-Out-286x300.jpg\" alt=\"camo-camp-out\" width=\"341\" height=\"358\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Toilet Roll Creation</span></strong></h1>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Well, when you get the right toilet paper, you buy enough to ensure that you never run out of stock shortly, this bride went an extra step and designed a wedding dress from tissue papers. She knows what she loves and hopes she gets a matching pair of shoe.</span></h2>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-351\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Toilet-Roll-Creation-300x261.png\" alt=\"toilet-roll-creation\" width=\"346\" height=\"301\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Terrifically Tentacled</span></strong></h1>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Just like “The Little Mermaid” this tentacle-inspired wedding dress is definitely up to our alley. Irrespective of our dislike of seafood, we highly love this wedding dress.</span></h2>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-350\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Terrifically-Tentacled-271x300.jpg\" alt=\"terrifically-tentacled\" width=\"306\" height=\"339\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Bright Like A Diamond</span></strong></h1>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">The bride chose the custom-made wedding dress for her special day. A good match in case there would be an electricity blackout.</span></h2>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-347\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Bright-Like-A-Diamond-300x232.jpg\" alt=\"bright-like-a-diamond\" width=\"387\" height=\"299\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Double Wedding</span></strong></h1>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">As a matter of fact, no good can come from having a joint wedding with your best friend, especially when your tastes are this similar. On the contrary, this special day for the couple was brightened by the magenta.</span></h2>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-346\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Double-Wedding-300x213.jpg\" alt=\"double-wedding\" width=\"425\" height=\"302\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Wifey $ Lifey</span></strong></h1>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">There is nothing that shows your commitment more than having ‘Wifey’ emblazoned across your bottom wedding dress for the special day. At least this bride won’t forget what she’s up to. Turns in a mirror and Oh yes!</span></h2>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-342\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Wifey-4-Lifey-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"wifey-4-lifey\" width=\"409\" height=\"307\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">The Royal Dress</span></strong></h1>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">It is clear and self-explanatory – the wedding was “The Royal Wedding” themed. The dress looks amazingly royal to us!</span></h2>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-341\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/The-Royal-Dress-253x300.jpg\" alt=\"the-royal-dress\" width=\"326\" height=\"386\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Honeymoon Suite Ready</span></strong></h1>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">In case you had not noticed, the bride chose a dress made out of more than one thousand rubbers. A clear indication of her preparedness once they get to the honeymoon.</span></h2>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-340\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Honeymoon-Suite-234x300.jpg\" alt=\"honeymoon-suite\" width=\"300\" height=\"385\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Peek-A-Bump</span></strong></h1>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">It is hard work when you try to find a nice looking dress for your special day if you happen to be pregnant. Most brides want to cover their baby bump but not this bride here. She had her custom-made dress created to show off her bump, allowing her baby to watch the ceremony.</span></h2>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-339\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Peek-A-Bump-240x300.jpg\" alt=\"peek-a-bump\" width=\"311\" height=\"389\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Wedding Limo, Please!</span></strong></h1>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">It is said that the average wedding in the US costs not less than $20,000. Well, how much of the budget do you think this bride spent on her wedding hummer limo?</span></h2>\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-338\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Wedding-Limo-300x190.jpg\" alt=\"wedding-limo\" width=\"409\" height=\"259\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>','Epic Brides You Can’t Unsee','','inherit','closed','closed','','322-autosave-v1','','','2016-12-19 09:53:12','2016-12-19 09:53:12','',322,'http://theladypost.com/2016/12/11/322-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(325,2,'2016-12-11 20:15:07','2016-12-11 20:15:07','','bridal-balloon','','inherit','open','closed','','bridal-balloon','','','2016-12-11 20:15:07','2016-12-11 20:15:07','',322,'http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Bridal-Balloon.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(326,2,'2016-12-11 20:15:40','2016-12-11 20:15:40','','wedding-photos','','inherit','open','closed','','wedding-photos','','','2016-12-11 20:15:40','2016-12-11 20:15:40','',322,'http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Wedding-Photos.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(327,2,'2016-12-11 20:16:32','2016-12-11 20:16:32','','diy-dress','','inherit','open','closed','','diy-dress','','','2016-12-11 20:16:32','2016-12-11 20:16:32','',322,'http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/DIY-Dress.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(328,2,'2016-12-11 20:17:19','2016-12-11 20:17:19','','sassy-bride','','inherit','open','closed','','sassy-bride','','','2016-12-11 20:17:19','2