:36:45','','custom-wedding-dress','','inherit','open','closed','','custom-wedding-dress','','','2016-12-11 20:36:45','2016-12-11 20:36:45','',322,'http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Custom-Wedding-Dress.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(358,2,'2016-12-11 20:38:16','2016-12-11 20:38:16','','balloon-gown','','inherit','open','closed','','balloon-gown','','','2016-12-11 20:38:16','2016-12-11 20:38:16','',322,'http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Balloon-Gown.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(359,2,'2016-12-11 20:38:47','2016-12-11 20:38:47','','go-green','','inherit','open','closed','','go-green','','','2016-12-11 20:38:47','2016-12-11 20:38:47','',322,'http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Go-Green.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(360,2,'2016-12-11 20:39:43','2016-12-11 20:39:43','<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">A wedding venue is vital for every bride, book a honeymoon suite, and enjoy these unending dresses. Have a look at these truthfully unique brides.</span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Bridal Balloon</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">A wedding cannot be complete minus balloons, and what this bride did is to take a step further by having a dress that uniquely resembles small balloons!</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-325\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Bridal-Balloon-201x300.jpg\" alt=\"bridal-balloon\" width=\"314\" height=\"469\" /></span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Wedding Photos</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Well, this wedding photo is certainly a craft. This moment ca never be forgotten by the couple.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-326 \" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Wedding-Photos-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"wedding-photos\" width=\"344\" height=\"344\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">DIY Dress</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">A wedding is an expensive undertaking, and coming up with cost-cutting ideas is a nice idea. This bride decided to go for a DIY wedding dress.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-327\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/DIY-Dress-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"diy-dress\" width=\"287\" height=\"382\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Sassy Bride In Rented Limousine</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">When you give a bride freedom to come up with dress ideas, she will total take it to another level. We’re happy that this wedding dress fit into the rented limousine…otherwise, it would have turned disastrous.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-328\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Sassy-Bride-202x300.jpg\" alt=\"sassy-bride\" width=\"279\" height=\"414\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Bridal Gown</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">As you can note from the previous list of our wedding dresses, some brides have taken it to the next level. They end to insist on something unique for their special day really, but this lady took it to the extreme.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-329\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Bridal-Gown-218x300.jpg\" alt=\"bridal-gown\" width=\"281\" height=\"387\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Have Your Special Day Cake and Eat It</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">This bride disagrees with everything.  She went for a tailor-made dress that is also unique and edible. You can imagine the amount of time spent in creating this tasty wedding dress.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-330\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Have-Your-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"have-your\" width=\"354\" height=\"354\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>Crazy Cat Lady</strong></span></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Ever wondered how an animal themed wedding dress will look like, well this lady did exactly that by going for a cat themed tailor-made dress.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-331\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Crazy-Cat-210x300.jpg\" alt=\"crazy-cat\" width=\"284\" height=\"406\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Donut Be Nuts!</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Well, if you think you have seen enough of edible wedding dresses, then the next thing is a bride coming up with something more unique and original. I won’t lie; I would be attempted to take a bite out of her beautifully crafted wedding dress.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-332\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Donut-Be-Nuts-300x236.jpg\" alt=\"donut-be-nuts\" width=\"379\" height=\"298\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Disney Comes to Life</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">This bubblegum pink number executed the Disney idea perfectly. It is one of the unique and original wedding gowns we have seen so far.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-333\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Disney-Comes-188x300.jpg\" alt=\"disney-comes\" width=\"255\" height=\"407\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Cost Cutting</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">One way of cutting your wedding dress costs is to forget the suit and wedding dress entirely and just go with some decorative body art.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-334\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Cost-Cutting-300x260.jpg\" alt=\"cost-cutting\" width=\"351\" height=\"304\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">The Sweetest Bride</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Heard of the expression, “you can have your cake and eat it too”? That is that what this couple is living this quote. After all, it was a special day for them.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-335\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/The-Sweetest-Bride-208x300.jpg\" alt=\"the-sweetest-bride\" width=\"270\" height=\"389\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Double-Click</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Nothing will be romantic than geeking out on your special day. This bride took it to the next level with a tailor-made wedding gown, though it’s made of computer mice and not real mice. That would have turned weird.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-336\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Double-Click-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"double-click\" width=\"297\" height=\"396\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Katniss?</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">It looks like Katniss Everdeen from ‘The Hunger Games’ would have worn for her big day, a beauty made out of sunset shades and flames. Worry no more about grabbing the fire extinguisher, though in this case, you will surely get worried; they are not real flames.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-337\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Katniss-237x300.jpg\" alt=\"katniss\" width=\"300\" height=\"379\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">You’ve Been Tangoed</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Everyone wants to stand out during his/her wedding day. But this bride took it to the next level, don’t you think? She opted for a nice shade of tangerine on her wedding day.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-343\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/You-ve-Been-237x300.jpg\" alt=\"you-ve-been\" width=\"327\" height=\"414\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">White Chocolate Wonder</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Edible and original wedding dresses are coming right up. This one is another luscious wonder, made entirely of white chocolate. Hope it will not be too sunny on the bride’s special day otherwise she might start melting!</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-344\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/White-Chocolate-Wonder-219x300.jpg\" alt=\"white-chocolate-wonder\" width=\"274\" height=\"375\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Customer Wedding Dress</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">If you are thinking of a custom tailor-made dress for your wedding day, you should know that a blue color symbolizes stability, loyalty, and security. So blue is a no go zone!</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-345\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Custom-Wedding-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"custom-wedding\" width=\"389\" height=\"389\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Glittery Wedding Limo Service</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Nothing says “I love you” quite like a dress made up of lots of bright pink hearts with some glitter for added effect. Since this bride looks everything but traditional, we wonder if the rented wedding limo was covered in pink glitter, too.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-348\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Glittery-Wedding-263x300.jpg\" alt=\"glittery-wedding\" width=\"321\" height=\"366\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">No Regular Wedding Dress Rental</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Who doesn’t love a leopard print, don’t get me wrong, though? Let’s us just say this custom pink and leopard print wedding dress is not a normal wedding dress you can get from a regular dress rental store.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-349\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/No-Regular-Wedding-300x249.jpg\" alt=\"no-regular-wedding\" width=\"392\" height=\"325\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Where’s The Dress?</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Just trying to figure out what really going on in this picture. This bride decided to look like a tree. Did you notice the bride? You may need to take a closer look.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-352\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Wheres-The-Dress-239x300.jpg\" alt=\"wheres-the-dress\" width=\"312\" height=\"392\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Neon Bright</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Giving our bridesmaid freedom to choose their dresses for the special day is a nice way to keep everyone happy. Cost can be kept low, and your favorite people get the freedom to choose a dress of their choice. However, you might end up with something colorful as this neon themed dress.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-353\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Neon-Bright-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"neon-bright\" width=\"377\" height=\"251\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Origami Wedding Dress</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">To be honest, it is not the wedding day that is vital – It is the fact that you and your other half will be exchanging vows and promise to commit to each other for the remaining days of your lives. You would love to be with you bride even before picking such a dramatic gown like this.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-354\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Origami-Wedding-200x300.jpg\" alt=\"origami-wedding\" width=\"267\" height=\"401\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">All of The Lights</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Every bride wants to show off on the wedding day. She wants a hammered limousine and extravagant venue. She wants the perfect honeymoon suite in the most amazing seven-star hotel. And more than that, she wants to be perfectly dressed and look beautiful.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-356\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/All-Of-The-Lights-236x300.png\" alt=\"all-of-the-lights\" width=\"292\" height=\"371\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Custom Wedding Dress Or Wigs?</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Consider your special day and think of the “hair” or “wig” that can be right for the occasion. On the centrally the bride decided to get a dress made fully out of human hair at a price of $78,000 is a perfect match for the bride.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-357\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Custom-Wedding-Dress-262x300.jpg\" alt=\"custom-wedding-dress\" width=\"298\" height=\"341\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Go Green</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">What a better way to create a scene that to have a dress made out of recycled materials. Food papers, sweet wrappers, it does not matter but ensures that it is the right color. We love this wedding dress!</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-359\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Go-Green-244x300.jpg\" alt=\"go-green\" width=\"297\" height=\"365\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Balloon Gown</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">This balloon wedding dress is an art. The second piece of art that we have seen, but to be honest, we really love it! Sometime it is good to mix things up and change the style of the wedding dress. And this balloon wedding dress should be the first one on your mind.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-358\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Balloon-Gown-221x300.jpg\" alt=\"balloon-gown\" width=\"303\" height=\"411\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Camo Camp Out</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">This camo-wedding dress is something only Honey Boo Boo’s mamma could go for on her special day. For an avid hunter, this is a perfect match but not for us; we would prefer something more of ivory.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-355\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Camo-Camp-Out-286x300.jpg\" alt=\"camo-camp-out\" width=\"341\" height=\"358\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Toilet Roll Creation</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Well, when you get the right toilet paper, you buy enough to ensure that you never run out of stock shortly, this bride went an extra step and designed a wedding dress from tissue papers. She knows what she loves and hopes she gets a matching pair of shoe.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-351\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Toilet-Roll-Creation-300x261.png\" alt=\"toilet-roll-creation\" width=\"346\" height=\"301\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Terrifically Tentacled</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Just like “The Little Mermaid” this tentacle-inspired wedding dress is definitely up to our alley. Irrespective of our dislike of seafood, we highly love this wedding dress.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-350\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Terrifically-Tentacled-271x300.jpg\" alt=\"terrifically-tentacled\" width=\"306\" height=\"339\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Bright Like A Diamond</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">The bride chose the custom-made wedding dress for her special day. A good match in case there would be an electricity blackout.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-347\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Bright-Like-A-Diamond-300x232.jpg\" alt=\"bright-like-a-diamond\" width=\"387\" height=\"299\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Double Wedding</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">As a matter of fact, no good can come from having a joint wedding with your best friend, especially when your tastes are this similar. On the contrary, this special day for the couple was brightened by the magenta.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-346\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Double-Wedding-300x213.jpg\" alt=\"double-wedding\" width=\"425\" height=\"302\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Wifey $ Lifey</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">There is nothing that shows your commitment more than having ‘Wifey’ emblazoned across your bottom wedding dress for the special day. At least this bride won’t forget what she’s up to. Turns in a mirror and Oh yes!</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-342\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Wifey-4-Lifey-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"wifey-4-lifey\" width=\"409\" height=\"307\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">The Royal Dress</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">It is clear and self-explanatory – the wedding was “The Royal Wedding” themed. The dress looks amazingly royal to us!</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-341\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/The-Royal-Dress-253x300.jpg\" alt=\"the-royal-dress\" width=\"326\" height=\"386\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Honeymoon Suite Ready</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">In case you had not noticed, the bride chose a dress made out of more than one thousand rubbers. A clear indication of her preparedness once they get to the honeymoon.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-340\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Honeymoon-Suite-234x300.jpg\" alt=\"honeymoon-suite\" width=\"300\" height=\"385\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Peek-A-Bump</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">It is hard work when you try to find a nice looking dress for your special day if you happen to be pregnant. Most brides want to cover their baby bump but not this bride here. She had her custom-made dress created to show off her bump, allowing her baby to watch the ceremony.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-339\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Peek-A-Bump-240x300.jpg\" alt=\"peek-a-bump\" width=\"311\" height=\"389\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Wedding Limo, Please!</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">It is said that the average wedding in the US costs not less than $20,000. Well, how much of the budget do you think this bride spent on her wedding hummer limo?</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-338\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Wedding-Limo-300x190.jpg\" alt=\"wedding-limo\" width=\"409\" height=\"259\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>','Epic Brides You Can’t Unsee','','inherit','closed','closed','','322-revision-v1','','','2016-12-11 20:39:43','2016-12-11 20:39:43','',322,'http://theladypost.com/2016/12/11/322-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(361,2,'2016-12-11 21:09:10','2016-12-11 21:09:10','<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">1</span><span style=\"color: #000000\">. Sharapova Maria $195 Million</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"> Maria Sharapova is a big name in the sports world. Despite getting into trouble for going against anti-doping regulations, her bank account wasn’t shaken. She currently boasts of a whopping $195 million in worth.</span></h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-375\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/maria-sharapova.png\" alt=\"maria-sharapova\" width=\"596\" height=\"394\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">2. Shaquille O’Neal $350 Million</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"> Shaq is one of the hugest and the greatest players to ever grace a basketball court. Today, he works as a sports analyst. His worth stands at $350 million as per 2016.</span></h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-376\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/shaquille-oneil.png\" alt=\"shaquille-oneil\" width=\"509\" height=\"385\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">3. Kevin Garnett $180 Million</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"> Boston Celtics had never won the championship since inception in 1986. That changed when they signed Kevin Garnett who helped the team win the championship in 2007. He stayed with the team until his retirement in 2016. With a net worth of $180 million he has done good for himself.</span></h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-377\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/kevin-garnet.png\" alt=\"kevin-garnet\" width=\"584\" height=\"388\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">4. Roger Federer $400 Million</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"> Federer is one of the greatest tennis players of all time and one of the richest. After winning his 17 single title, his net worth is projected to exceed $400 million.</span></h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-378\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Roger-Federer.png\" alt=\"roger-federer\" width=\"517\" height=\"385\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">5. Kimi Raikkonen $200 Million</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"> Whenever he was behind the wheel Kimi thrilled fans. His art earned him many endorsements and a special spot on this least. With a $200 million worth of personal wealth he is good to go.</span></h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-379\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Kimi.png\" alt=\"kimi\" width=\"629\" height=\"356\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">6. Agassi Andre $175 Million</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"> Andre Agassi is a retired Tennis star with a very impressive career to his name. Know what winning eight Grand slam title back to back could earn you? $175 million.</span></h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-380\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Andre.png\" alt=\"andre\" width=\"577\" height=\"361\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">7. Peyton Manning $200 Million</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"> Manning hails from a family with a long history for football. The NFL quarterback’s brother and father were renowned football players so we can as well say he had legacies to beat and he did a good job at it.  </span></h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-388\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Payton-Manning.png\" alt=\"payton-manning\" width=\"556\" height=\"369\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">8. Michael Schumacher $800 Million</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"> Michael started driving at age 4. Since then, he never looked back. His career has lasted almost as long as he has lived and definitely among the richest athletes alive.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"c