er’s series.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Dakota Johnson</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000\">As famous as her parents, she’s the grown-up daughter of Melanie Griffith and Don Johnson. She came in the limelight after she starred in one of the famous movies, fifty shades of Grey.<!--nextpage--></span><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Zoe Kravitz</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Daughter of Lenny Kravitz, this girl took the looks of her parents and grew up to be a very beautiful girl. She took up the acting career all by herself and appeared in movies like X-MenFirst Class.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Liv Moore</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Taking attributes from both her parents, she has adopted her looks from her mother whereas her commendable height comes from her father.<!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Taylor Cranston</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Daughter of the Breaking Bad star has already begun her acting career although she is not that old. She appeared in her dad’s biggest hit for one episode.<!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Dylan Penn</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Trying to make it big in New York City as a model, starting off with a million part time jobs. What ended up contributing to her fame is her causal relationship with Robert Pattison, which kick started her modeling career. Now 25 years old, Dylan has modeled for GQ and W magazines.<!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Frances Bean Cobain</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>She spent most of her life trying to shuffle between her family members so what she is now is all because of hard work. The 23 year old is worth $170 million and comes on the cover of the Elle magazine.<!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Sistine Stallone</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Sylvester Stallone’s middle child, Sistine, has done everything in power to avoid the shadow of her infamous father. Sistine joined her friend Ireland Baldwinn in joining the IMG Models agency, where she displays her quirky sense of style. Sistine recently revealed she just doesn’t enjoy acting as much as modeling.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h2> <strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Rafferty Law</span></strong></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Having a very harsh childhood in the sense that he was 18 when news broke out that his father was having a son with his ex-girlfriend. It was since that he decided to start a career in singing and acting.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Connor Cruise</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">One of Hollywood’s most powerful and beautiful couples of the ’90s, Nicole Kidman and Tom Cruise adopted two children during their time together – Isabella and Connor Anthony. Connor is staying out of the Hollywood headlines, but the 21-year-old is known as a DJ.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Sosie Bacon</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Daughter of Kevin Bacon and Kyra Sedgwick, she was kept away from the spotlight so that she would not come into the field of acting however she still managed to star in movies like Lost Boy and some others.<!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Dominik Cristina</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">She is the eldest of Andy Gracia’s four children. She always wanted a career in dancer since she was little however she was not able to follow that career in particular. She is 32 now and has appeared in Wild Card recently.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Gia Mantegna</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Daughter of “Criminal Minds” superstar, Joe Mantegna, and restaurateur Arlene Vrhel, 26-year-old Gia looks better than ever. Gia trained to be a ballerina and a gymnast since she was a child, but has had more success on television in the recent years.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h2> <strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Lily Mo Sheen</span></strong></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">A young girl who looks as gorgeous as her mother at the age of 17. She had to bare a very emotional breakup when her parents decided to part ways that too in front of the public however she still has a good relationship with her father.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Jack Scott Ramsay</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Known for his cooking and brutal honesty, Gordon Ramsay now runs every top of the line restaurant in the UK. The Scottish chef is also the father of Jack Scott, who recently joined his father in the spotlight and has made quite the impression on social media.<!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Lucy Devito</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>DeVito’s and Perlman’s daughter Lucy, like many other celeb kids, followed her parents onto the stage. Lucy has made appearances in “DeadBeat” and her father’s star show “It’s Always Sunny In Philadelphia”. And yes, Lucy did inherit her father’s height!<!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Joseph Baena</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Born in 1997, Joseph Baena was quite the secret for many years. Arnold Schwarznegger, who had an affair with his housekeeper Mildred Baena, had Joseph and his son Christopher (from wife Maria Shriver”) just days apart! Joseph was Arnie’s hidden son until recently, when the media got a hold of the information.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Marcus Jordan</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Since he was the son of a famous basket ball player people had a lot of expectations from him. He was trying to follow his father since he was 13 and that’s why he got a basketball scholarship at the University of South Florida. Just this year he opened his own shoe shop since this career wasn’t right for him.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Hayley Hasselhoff</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>She was younger to the two children her parents had. Before starring in the show Hasselhoffs she appeared in the famous show Baywatch in 1999.<!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h2><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Ireland Baldwin</span></strong></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">A stunning young model with a phenomenal height of 6’2” was an IMG model at the age of 18 and has been popular ever since. She is famous for her fashionable lifestyle and high-profile friendships.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h2><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Cassidy Gifford</span></strong></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">She is yet another person in the spotlight. In 2005 she starred in the show Not So Raven and her latest works include Gods not dead and the Gallows.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Zelda Williams</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">The world was in mourning when in 2014 the world’s most loved comedian, Robin Williams, took his own life. Luckily, Williams’ daughter Zelda is a little piece of the star that is still with us. The 26-year-old followed her father into the spotlight by voicing the animated series “Teenage Mutant Ninja”<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Damian Charles Harley</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Since his mother could not have a daughter as beautiful looking as her he was seen with his mother most of the time. He is acting right now.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Lorraine Nicholson</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Although we love Jack Nicholson, whether he’s Randle McMurphy or Dr. Buddy, but do his daughter’s boyfriends think the same? Probably not; he’s pretty terrifying. Lorraine, one of Nicholson’s 6 children, is currently an actress, and even produced and directed her own film in 2011.<!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Brooklyn Beckham</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>The Beckham children were pretty much celebrities before they were even born. Victoria and David’s eldest son, Brooklyn, has been spotted with his parents in London quite frequently. Most recently, Brooklyn has shown interest to photography, as well as his recent romance with Chloe Grace Moretz.<!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Kate Hudson</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>You’ve definitely heard of Kate Hudson, but did you know she is the daughter of actress Goldie Hawn and comedian/actor Bill Hudson. She has carved out her own name in Hollywood, appearing in many films such as <em>Almost Famous</em> and <em>50 First Dates.<!--nextpage--></em></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Chance King</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>He is the child of famous Larry king. He was given the chance to host the first baseball show when he was 10 years old. He is living a regular life along with his infamous father.<!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h2> <strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Isabella and Olivia Giannulli</span></strong></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Lori Loughlin, aka Aunt Becky on <em>Full House, </em>has two daughters that are all grown up and already are creating their own space in the world of fashion by appearing in magazines and having huge followings on Twitter.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Rumer Willis</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Daughter of Bruce Willis she has appeared in several movies as well as shows like Pretty Little Liars and Workahoics. She is an amazing actor.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Eva Amurri</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Eva Amurri is the daughter of film director Franco Amurri and Susan Sarandon. She has become an actress as well, appearing in many films and TV shows. She recently got married and has a daughter and son of her own.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Miles Robbins</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>The youngest child of his parents Susan Sarandon and Tims Robbins. He is currently working as a DJ and is totally eccentric.<!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Violet Afflick</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Violet, daughter of Ben Affleck and Jennifer Garner, is growing up and is looking more and more like her famous mother every day. She also has a brother and a sister, though her parents have recently called it quits.<!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h2><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Rainey Qualley</span></strong></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">One of Andie MacDowell’s three children, Rainey Qualley, made a name for herself in the music industry, creating country hits like “Me and Johnny Cash”. Rainey also appeared in the final season of TV series “Mad Men”.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Colin Hanks</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Son of superstar actor Tom Hanks. Although he was recently seen in the series Fargo it not known to everyone that he forged the acting career on himself.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Brielle Biermann</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">The star of ‘The Real Housewives of Atlanta’ and her husband Kroy Biermann adopted Brielle and her sister, Ariana, a while ago. Since then, the sisters took their stepfather’s name and managed to build quite the fan base on Twitter. Today, Brielle is practically engaged to her boyfriend, baseball superstar Michael Kopech.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Annie Starke</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Daughter to one of the most praised actresses of her generation, Glenn Close, Annie, debuted into the industry at the age of 13 in the film “South Pacific”, and today, at the age of 28, is back on screen in “We Don’t Belong Here”.<!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Sailor Cook</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Already following her mother in the lime light, this girl landed 