age--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Dylan Brosnan</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">When your father is so handsome and popular among people you have to keep up. Not only is he the son of Brad Pitt but also the model for high-end brands like Saint Lauren. He also has relationship problems like other teenagers.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1> <strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Honey Boo Boo</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Mama June’s daughter. She first made an appearance when she was six years old. She became so popular that she hosted her show which was cancelled two years ago. Recently she made an appearance in which she looks very different.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h2> <strong>Zoe Jackson</strong></h2>\r\n<h2>Daughter of Samuel Jackson. She is 34 years old and followed her father into the industry and directed a movie called Everything is Samuel Jackson\'s fault.<!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Christiana Barkley</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Daughter of famous basketball player Charles Barkley. She is a socialite and is well known in the modelling world. She posts racy photographs on her Instagram account under the name “Villanova.”<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h2> <strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Jordan Zain Weiner</span></strong></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">The two politicians stole the spotlight when they had a fight over a sexting scandal. They have been fighting over the custody of their son who is four years now and growing quickly.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Cameron Douglas</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>He is the oldest son of Michael Douglas. He has appeared in some famous movies one of them was Jackie Chan’s Nice Guy. He has been arrested sometimes for serious drug offences and has spent up to seven years in jail.<!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Carys Zeta Douglas</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>She is the daughter of Michael Douglas and looks like both of her parents. She is just 13 years old. She is very close to both of her parents. Shopping for her mum and travelling around with her dad are her favourite past times.<!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Huma Abedin</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Daughter of educators in British India, she was Hillary Clintons Vice Chairwomen in this year\'s campaign. She was recently involved in a love scandal with her husband but got custody of her son.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Bristol Palin</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>A TV star and reality show personality she is the daughter of Todd and Sarah Palin. In 2010 she went to the show “Dancing with the Stars” and won third place. She also starred in a show in 2012 called “Bristol Palin: Life’s a Tripp.”<!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Sasha Spielberg</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Daughter of director Steven Spielberg Kate Capshaw. She is an American actress and attended Brown University. She is part of a band with Theo Spielberg.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Homer James Jigme Gere</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">After 41 years of their marriage his parents, Richard Gere and Cary Lowell, had a very bad divorce and parted their ways. Their divorce was all over the media. He is very close to his dad.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Suzanne Charlton</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Daughter of famous footballer Bobby Charlton, she is a British Weather Forecaster for BBC. She has one son and lives in Hertfordshire.<!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Emerson Tenney</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Daughter of Teri Hatcher, a famous actress in Desperate housewives. She is just 19 years old and says she has no plans to act yet.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Willow Smith</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">She is the daughter of famous Will Smith. She decided to take the music part instead of the acting one. She released an album in 2015 and has some modelling plans.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong> <span style=\"color: #000000\">Sophia Richie</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Born to Lionel Richie and his ex-wife. She is now 18 years old and is already a mode. Modelling for various magazines like Vogue China has made her famous, and she was recently involved in the Yeezy Fashion Show.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Maddox Jolie Pit</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">The was adopted by Angeline Jolie in 2002 from Columbia, and then Brad Pitt adopted him in 2006. He used to help his parents on the set but has recently been upset because of their split.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Paris Michael</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Second daughter of the famous pop star Michael Jackson with Debbie Rowie. She was very depressed after her father’s death and attempted suicide in 2013. Just recently she declared she is attending Alcoholics Anonymous meetings.<!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Corinne Bishop</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Eldest daughter of Jamie Foxx is now 19 years old and is a real beauty. She accompanies her father in award shows. Just this year she stole the spotlight by becoming miss golden globe and is now becoming both a model and an actress.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Kaia Gerber</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Daughter of an infamous model Cindy Crawford and Rande Gerber she is already in the spotlight because she was featured on the cover of Vogue Paris along with her mother. She has another sister Pressley.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Justin Combs</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">He has been in and out of Hollywood’s spotlight for a couple of years. He appeared on the show “My Super Sweet Sixteen” where his father gifted him $360,000. He is the only member of his family to have studied and gotten a degree.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Earvin Johnson</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">More commonly known as E.J, he is the oldest of his three siblings. He was very famous because of the Reality Tv series, Rich Kids of Beverly Hills.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Lily Atkinson</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Born to the legendary actor Roan Atkinson in 1995, she recently performed in a pretty raunchy cabaret this year around and her father seemed very calm about it.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Jaden Smith</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>He has won regarding genes. He first appeared with his father in Men in Black 2, and after that, he worked on projects independently. He also has his clothes line which goes by the name of MSFTSrep.<!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Lily Rose Depp</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Daughter of Jhonny Depp and Vanessa Paradis, she made her first acting debut in 2014 in the movie “Tusk” when she was only 15 years old. She is currently working on three projects at the same time.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Iris Law</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Born to actor Jude Law and Sadie Forest, she is only 15 years old and has signed her first modelling contract with Chanel which is a big achievement at her age.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Jane Carrey</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Having a father who was named as one of the funniest men in the world life couldn’t have been boring for her at all. She was interested in singing and tried her luck in American Idol 4 years back but did not make it to the end.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Pauline Gretzky</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Daughter of the famous Ice hockey player she isn’t a little girl. Inspired by her father, she married Dustin Johnson, a golfer. She also has some kids of her own.<!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Lourdes Leon</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>She was born to Madonna and Carlos Leon. She is the eldest daughter in the family and is campaigning for Stella McCartney currently while studying performing arts simultaneously.<!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h2></h2>','Kids Of Famous Parents- Then and Now','','inherit','closed','closed','','397-revision-v1','','','2016-12-12 09:58:02','2016-12-12 09:58:02','',397,'http://theladypost.com/2016/12/12/397-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(402,2,'2016-12-12 09:58:11','2016-12-12 09:58:11','<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Alexa Ray Joel</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000\">A beautiful girl with a dominant character, she is named after Ray Charles. She is a talented musician and although she has not had a lot of success in this field her best years are yet to come.<!--nextpage--></span><strong>Bella Hadid</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Beautiful daughter of the actress Yolanda foster who became famous after she moved to Beverly Hills and was known as one of the “real” housewives. Bella has one more sister and is beautiful.<!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Georgia May Jagger</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>She was passed on her stardom by her mother and became a very famous model from the age of 16 when she was signed by Independent Models. She has made several massive appearances and has modeled for famous brands like Chanel.<!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1>