vid’s eldest son, Brooklyn, has been spotted with his parents in London quite frequently. Most recently, Brooklyn has shown interest to photography, as well as his recent romance with Chloe Grace Moretz.<!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Kate Hudson</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>You’ve definitely heard of Kate Hudson, but did you know she is the daughter of actress Goldie Hawn and comedian/actor Bill Hudson. She has carved out her own name in Hollywood, appearing in many films such as <em>Almost Famous</em> and <em>50 First Dates.<!--nextpage--></em></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Chance King</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>He is the child of famous Larry king. He was given the chance to host the first baseball show when he was 10 years old. He is living a regular life along with his infamous father.<!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h2> <strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Isabella and Olivia Giannulli</span></strong></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Lori Loughlin, aka Aunt Becky on <em>Full House, </em>has two daughters that are all grown up and already are creating their own space in the world of fashion by appearing in magazines and having huge followings on Twitter.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Rumer Willis</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Daughter of Bruce Willis she has appeared in several movies as well as shows like Pretty Little Liars and Workahoics. She is an amazing actor.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Eva Amurri</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Eva Amurri is the daughter of film director Franco Amurri and Susan Sarandon. She has become an actress as well, appearing in many films and TV shows. She recently got married and has a daughter and son of her own.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Miles Robbins</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>The youngest child of his parents Susan Sarandon and Tims Robbins. He is currently working as a DJ and is totally eccentric.<!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Violet Afflick</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Violet, daughter of Ben Affleck and Jennifer Garner, is growing up and is looking more and more like her famous mother every day. She also has a brother and a sister, though her parents have recently called it quits.<!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h2><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Rainey Qualley</span></strong></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">One of Andie MacDowell’s three children, Rainey Qualley, made a name for herself in the music industry, creating country hits like “Me and Johnny Cash”. Rainey also appeared in the final season of TV series “Mad Men”.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Colin Hanks</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Son of superstar actor Tom Hanks. Although he was recently seen in the series Fargo it not known to everyone that he forged the acting career on himself.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Brielle Biermann</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">The star of ‘The Real Housewives of Atlanta’ and her husband Kroy Biermann adopted Brielle and her sister, Ariana, a while ago. Since then, the sisters took their stepfather’s name and managed to build quite the fan base on Twitter. Today, Brielle is practically engaged to her boyfriend, baseball superstar Michael Kopech.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Annie Starke</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Daughter to one of the most praised actresses of her generation, Glenn Close, Annie, debuted into the industry at the age of 13 in the film “South Pacific”, and today, at the age of 28, is back on screen in “We Don’t Belong Here”.<!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Sailor Cook</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Already following her mother in the lime light, this girl landed some gigs with Teen Vogue and later expressed her interest in acting. She is also very active on social media.<!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Mamie Gummer</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Mamie picked up many skills from her famous mother, Meryl Streep. She even acted alongside her in, <em>Ricki and the Flash </em><em>as</em> her on screen daughter. She is following in her mother’s footsteps and continuing to act. She had a recurring role on <em>The Good Wife</em>. Gummer is now 33 years old.<!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Sophie Von Haselberg</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>She is the only daughter of the legendary actress Bette Midler. At first she was not interested in acting but later she took courses from Yale. She made her debut in Irrational Man.<!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Maya Hawke</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">She is young and hence not involved in the acting world as yet. Her parents are no longer together but she is an image of both and is a sign of their once happy marriage.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h2> <strong>Maude Apatow</strong></h2>\r\n<h2>Appeared as Cleo in the TV series “Girls” in 2015. Since then, she has also earned the role of Alexandra in “Other People”. Aside from her on-screen career, Maude is just a regular teenager who helps Zooey Deschanel with her website, Hello Giggles.<!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Drana De Niro</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Daughter of Robert De Niro, she is an actor as well as a film producer. She was adopted. She currently lives in New York with her son.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h2> <strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Lily Costner</span></strong></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Daughter of Kevin Costner. In 2004 she was elected as the miss golden globe. She graduated from Wesleyan University in 2008. Her famous role is Lily in the Babysitters club. She currently lives in California.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Ella Travolta</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">With a father who is an amazing actor in the industry, the little girl is just 16 years old and made her first debut in 2001 on the set of “Not under my roof.”<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Georgia Ford</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Georgia Ford is the daughter of highly acclaimed actor, Harrison Ford. Georgia is known for her roles in the films <em>True Story, American Milkshake,</em><em> </em>and<em> </em><em>The Visitor. </em>Georgia battles Epilepsy and her father has said she is “his hero”.<!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Mia Honey Threapleton</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Daughter of Kate Winslet. She is already 16 years and is a copy of her mother regarding looks. She usually does not appear in front of people but appeared with her mum in the Wimbledon Championship last year.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Simone Alexandra Johnson</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Daughter of Dwayne Johnson also known as Rock and his first wife. Her parents separated when she as ten years old, but they remain good friends. She is good friends wither father and accompanies him to red carpet events.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1> <strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Shiloh Jolie-Pitt</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Already she is very young she has already made headlines because of the way she dresses. She likes to act like a boy, and rumours are caught that she might be transgender. Angelina Jolie recently said that she always wanted to be a boy, but this is not confirmed.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Julie Pacino</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Eldest daughter of Al Pacino she has followed her parent’s steps and is in the industry as a producer and writer. Her most recent work for which she is famous is ABRACADABRA.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Chloe Rose</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">She was born 11 years before her parents decided to divorce. Her parents met on the set of “Grease”. She made her debut in Australian soap opera when she was only seven years old but since then decided to go into the music industry.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Alexandra Hoffman</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Dustin Hoffman has two children from his first marriage, and she is one of them. She is 28 and was famous because of her “thing” with Jonah Hill but since it has ended the hype died down.<!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Syndey Brooke Simpson</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Daughter of the athlete who was jailed for murdering his wife. His son and daughter both stayed out of the spotlight for many years. She is 30, lives in Atlanta and works as an event planner. Her parents say she is kind and hardworking.<!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Ronan Farrow</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>The son of Hollywood legend Woody Allen has an amazing personality on his own. At the age of 28, he is a journalist, activist and former US government advisor.<!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Michael Neeson</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Born in 1995 to Liam Neeson, his mother passed away eight years earlier because of a serious head injury. Lastly, he was known to be effected badly by a serious drug addiction, but that was him dealing with his mother\'s death. He is working as fashion gallery curator nowadays.<!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Hazel Moder</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">The son of Julia Roberts who is the “pretty women”. He has a twin whose name is Phinnaeus. They are just ten years old but growing up quickly and have started looking like their mother.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Dylan Brosnan</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">When your father is so handsome and popular among people you have to keep up. Not only is he the son of Brad Pitt but also the model for high-end brands like Saint Lauren. He also has relationship problems like other teenagers.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1> <strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Honey Boo Boo</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Mama June’s daughter. She first made an appearance when she was six years old. She became so popular that she hosted her show which was cancelled two years ago. Recently she made an appearance in which she looks very different.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h2> <strong>Zoe Jackson</strong></h2>\r\n<h2>Daughter of Samuel Jackson. She is 34 years old and followed her father into the industry and directed a movie called Everything is Samuel Jackson\'s fault.<!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Christiana Barkley</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Daughter of famous basketball player Charles Barkley. She is a socialite and is well known in the modelling world. She posts racy photographs on her Instagram account under the name “Villanova.”<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h2> <strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Jordan Zain Weiner</span></strong></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">The two politicians stole the spotlight when they had a fight over a sexting scandal. They have been fighting over the custody of their son who is four years now and growing quickly.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Cameron Douglas</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>He is the oldest son of Michael Douglas. He has appeared in some famous movies one of them was Jackie Chan’s Nice Guy. He has been arrested sometimes for serious drug offences and has spent up to seven years in jail.<!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Carys Zeta Douglas</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>She is the daughter of Michael Douglas and looks like both of her parents. She is just 13 years old. She is very close to both of her parents. Shopping for her mum and travelling around with her dad are her favourite past times.<!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Huma Abedin</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Daughter of educators in British India, she was Hillary Clintons Vice Chairwomen in this year\'s campaign. She was recently involved in a love scandal with her husband but got custody of her son.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Bristol Palin</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>A TV star and reality show personality she is the daughter of Todd and Sarah Palin. In 2010 she went to the show “Dancing with the Stars” and won third place. She also starred in a show in 2012 called “Bristol Palin: Life’s a Tripp.”<!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Sasha Spielberg</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Daughter of director Steven Spielberg Kate Capshaw. She is an American actress and attended Brown University. She is part of a band with Theo Spielberg.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Homer James Jigme Gere</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">After 41 years of their marriage his parents, Richard Gere and Cary Lowell, had a very bad divorce and parted their ways. Their divorce was all over the media. He is very close to his dad.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Suzanne Charlton</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Daughter of famous footballer Bobby Charlton, she is a British Weather Forecaster for BBC. She has one son and lives in Hertfordshire.<!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Emerson Tenney</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Daughter of Teri Hatcher, a famous actress in Desperate housewives. She is just 19 years old and says she has no plans to act yet.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Willow Smith</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">She is the daughter of famous Will Smith. She decided to take the music part instead of the acting one. She released an album in 2015 and has some modelling plans.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong> <span style=\"color: #000000\">Sophia Richie</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Born to Lionel Richie and his ex-wife. She is now 18 years old and is already a mode. Modelling for various magazines like Vogue China has made her famous, and she was recently involved in the Yeezy Fashion Show.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Maddox Jolie Pit</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">The was adopted by Angeline Jolie in 2002 from Columbia, and then Brad Pitt adopted him in 2006. He used to help his parents on the set but has recently been upset because of their split.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Paris Michael</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Second daughter of the famous pop star Michael Jackson with Debbie Rowie. She was very depressed after her father’s death and attempted suicide in 2013. Just recently she declared she is attending Alcoholics Anonymous meetings.<!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Corinne Bishop</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Eldest daughter of Jamie Foxx is now 19 years old and is a real beauty. She accompanies her father in award shows. Just this year she stole the spotlight by becoming miss golden globe and is now becoming both a model and an actress.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Kaia Gerber</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Daughter of an infamous model Cindy Crawford and Rande Gerber she is already in the spotlight because she was featured on the cover of Vogue Paris along with her mother. She has another sister Pressley.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Justin Combs</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">He has been in and out of Hollywood’s spotlight for a couple of years. He appeared on the show “My Super Sweet Sixteen” where his father gifted him $360,000. He is the only member of his family to have studied and gotten a degree.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Earvin Johnson</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">More commonly known as E.J, he is the oldest of his three siblings. He was very famous because of the Reality Tv series, Rich Kids of Beverly Hills.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Lily Atkinson</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Born to the legendary actor Roan Atkinson in 1995, she recently performed in a pretty raunchy cabaret this year around and her father seemed very calm about it.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Jaden Smith</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>He has won regarding genes. He first appeared with his father in Men in Black 2, and after that, he worked on projects independently. He also has his clothes line which goes by the name of MSFTSrep.<!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Lily Rose Depp</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Daughter of Jhonny Depp and Vanessa Paradis, she made her first acting debut in 2014 in the movie “Tusk” when she was only 15 years old. She is currently working on three projects at the same time.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Iris Law</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Born to actor Jude Law and Sadie Forest, she is only 15 years old and has signed her first modelling contract with Chanel which is a big achievement at her age.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Jane Carrey</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Having a father who was named as one of the funniest men in the world life couldn’t have been boring for her at all. She was interested in singing and tried her luck in American Idol 4 years back but did not make it to the end.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Pauline Gretzky</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Daughter of the famous Ice hockey player she isn’t a little girl. Inspired by her father, she married Dustin Johnson, a golfer. She also has some kids of her own.<!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Lourdes Leon</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>She was born to Madonna and Carlos Leon. She is the eldest daughter in the family and is campaigning for Stella McCartney currently while studying performing arts simultaneously.<!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h2></h2>','Kids Of Famous Parents- Then and Now','','inherit','closed','closed','','397-revision-v1','','','2016-12-12 09:58:11','2016-12-12 09:58:11','',397,'http://theladypost.com/2016/12/12/397-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(403,2,'2016-12-12 09:59:10','2016-12-12 09:59:10','','alexa-ray','','inherit','open','closed','','alexa-ray','','','2016-12-12 09:59:10','2016-12-12 09:59:10','',397,'http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Alexa-Ray.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(404,2,'2016-12-12 10:00:01','2016-12-12 10:00:01','','bella-hadid','','inherit','open','closed','','bella-hadid','','','2016-12-12 10:00:01','2016-12-12 10:00:01','',397,'http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Bella-Hadid.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(405,2,'2016-12-12 10:01:01','2016-12-12 10:01:01','','georgia-may-jagger','','inherit','open','closed','','georgia-may-jagger','','','2016-12-12 10:01:01','2016-12-12 10:01:01','',397,'http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Georgia-May-Jagger.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(406,2,'2016-12-12 10:01:47','2016-12-12 10:01:47','','hailie-jade','','inherit','open','closed','','hailie-jade','','','2016-12-12 10:01:47','2016-12-12 10:01:47','',397,'http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Hailie-Jade.jpg',0,'attachment