queen but also because she graduated top of her class.<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-406\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Hailie-Jade.jpg\" alt=\"hailie-jade\" width=\"424\" height=\"282\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Ava Philippe</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Only 17 years old this pretty actress is very famous because she looks a lot like her mom. Her parents became famous after they were starred on Cruel Intentions but she came in the lime light just recently.<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-407\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Ava-Phillippe.jpg\" alt=\"ava-phillippe\" width=\"432\" height=\"288\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Ava Sambora</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">With a huge online fan following, this pretty girl looks exactly like her mother. She is about to take on her modeling career very soon although she is just 18 years old.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-408\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Ava-Sambora.jpg\" alt=\"ava-sambora\" width=\"434\" height=\"290\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Francesca Eastwood</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Focusing now mostly on being a socialite, this 22-year-old has been in and out of the film industry where she took part in several movies. She made her debut appearance in 2012 on Mrs. Eastwood and company.<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-409\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Francesca-Eastwood.jpg\" alt=\"francesca-eastwood\" width=\"435\" height=\"290\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Bindi Irwin</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Daughter to one of the most famous people, Steve Irwin, who was the ultimate crocodile hunter. She has flourished into a gorgeous girl and has a promising career ahead. She was recently a part of Dancing with the stars.<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-410\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Bindi-Irwin.jpg\" alt=\"bindi-irwin\" width=\"425\" height=\"283\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">John Lowe</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">With a very young father, this handsome young man is not only his father’s favorite workout partner but has amazing plans for the future. He does not really like acting but last year appeared in his father’s series.<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-411\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/John-Lowe.jpg\" alt=\"john-lowe\" width=\"432\" height=\"288\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Dakota Johnson</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000\">As famous as her parents, she’s the grown-up daughter of Melanie Griffith and Don Johnson. She came in the limelight after she starred in one of the famous movies, fifty shades of Grey.<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-412\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/dakota-Johnson.jpg\" alt=\"dakota-johnson\" width=\"393\" height=\"364\" /><!--nextpage--></span><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Zoe Kravitz</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Daughter of Lenny Kravitz, this girl took the looks of her parents and grew up to be a very beautiful girl. She took up the acting career all by herself and appeared in movies like X-MenFirst Class.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-413\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Zoe-Kravitz.jpg\" alt=\"zoe-kravitz\" width=\"400\" height=\"372\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Liv Moore</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Taking attributes from both her parents, she has adopted her looks from her mother whereas her commendable height comes from her father.<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-414\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Liv-Moore.jpg\" alt=\"liv-moore\" width=\"408\" height=\"315\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Taylor Cranston</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Daughter of the Breaking Bad star has already begun her acting career although she is not that old. She appeared in her dad’s biggest hit for one episode.<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-415\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Taylor-Cranston.jpg\" alt=\"taylor-cranston\" width=\"463\" height=\"280\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Dylan Penn</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Trying to make it big in New York City as a model, starting off with a million part time jobs. What ended up contributing to her fame is her causal relationship with Robert Pattison, which kick started her modeling career. Now 25 years old, Dylan has modeled for GQ and W magazines.</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-416\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Dylan-Penn.jpg\" alt=\"dylan-penn\" width=\"438\" height=\"292\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Frances Bean Cobain</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>She spent most of her life trying to shuffle between her family members so what she is now is all because of hard work. The 23 year old is worth $170 million and comes on the cover of the Elle magazine.</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-417\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Frances-Bean-Cobain.jpg\" alt=\"frances-bean-cobain\" width=\"434\" height=\"289\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Sistine Stallone</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Sylvester Stallone’s middle child, Sistine, has done everything in power to avoid the shadow of her infamous father. Sistine joined her friend Ireland Baldwinn in joining the IMG Models agency, where she displays her quirky sense of style. Sistine recently revealed she just doesn’t enjoy acting as much as modeling.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-418\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Sistine-Stallone.jpg\" alt=\"sistine-stallone\" width=\"457\" height=\"305\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h2> <strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Rafferty Law</span></strong></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Having a very harsh childhood in the sense that he was 18 when news broke out that his father was having a son with his ex-girlfriend. It was since that he decided to start a career in singing and acting.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-419\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Rafferty-Law.jpg\" alt=\"rafferty-law\" width=\"458\" height=\"305\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Connor Cruise</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">One of Hollywood’s most powerful and beautiful couples of the ’90s, Nicole Kidman and Tom Cruise adopted two children during their time together – Isabella and Connor Anthony. Connor is staying out of the Hollywood headlines, but the 21-year-old is known as a DJ.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-420\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Connor-Cruise.jpg\" alt=\"connor-cruise\" width=\"459\" height=\"306\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Sosie Bacon</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Daughter of Kevin Bacon and Kyra Sedgwick, she was kept away from the spotlight so that she would not come into the field of acting however she still managed to star in movies like Lost Boy and some others.</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-421\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Sosie-Bacon.jpg\" alt=\"sosie-bacon\" width=\"464\" height=\"309\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Dominik Cristina</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">She is the eldest of Andy Gracia’s four children. She always wanted a career in dancer since she was little however she was not able to follow that career in particular. She is 32 now and has appeared in Wild Card recently.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-422\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Dominik-Cristina.jpg\" alt=\"dominik-cristina\" width=\"455\" height=\"303\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Gia Mantegna</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Daughter of “Criminal Minds” superstar, Joe Mantegna, and restaurateur Arlene Vrhel, 26-year-old Gia looks better than ever. Gia trained to be a ballerina and a gymnast since she was a child, but has had more success on television in the recent years.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-423\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Gia-Mantegna.jpg\" alt=\"gia-mantegna\" width=\"441\" height=\"294\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h2> <strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Lily Mo Sheen</span></strong></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">A young girl who looks as gorgeous as her mother at the age of 17. She had to bare a very emotional breakup when her parents decided to part ways that too in front of the public however she still has a good relationship with her father.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-424\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Lily-Mo-Sheen.jpg\" alt=\"lily-mo-sheen\" width=\"433\" height=\"288\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Jack Scott Ramsay</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Known for his cooking and brutal honesty, Gordon Ramsay now runs every top of the line restaurant in the UK. The Scottish chef is also the father of Jack Scott, who recently joined his father in the spotlight and has made quite the impression on social media.</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-425\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Jack-Scott-Ramsay.jpg\" alt=\"jack-scott-ramsay\" width=\"423\" height=\"282\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Lucy Devito</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>DeVito’s and Perlman’s daughter Lucy, like many other celeb kids, followed her parents onto the stage. Lucy has made appearances in “DeadBeat” and her father’s star show “It’s Always Sunny In Philadelphia”. And yes, Lucy did inherit her father’s height!</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-426\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Lucy-DeVito.jpg\" alt=\"lucy-devito\" width=\"422\" height=\"281\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Joseph Baena</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Born in 1997, Joseph Baena was quite the secret for many years. Arnold Schwarznegger, who had an affair with his housekeeper Mildred Baena, had Joseph and his son Christopher (from wife Maria Shriver”) just days apart! Joseph was Arnie’s hidden son until recently, when the media got a hold of the information.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-427\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Joseph-Baena.jpg\" alt=\"joseph-baena\" width=\"426\" height=\"284\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Marcus Jordan</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Since he was the son of a famous basket ball player people had a lot of expectations from him. He was trying to follow his father since he was 13 and that’s why he got a basketball scholarship at the University of South Florida. Just this year he opened his own shoe shop since this career wasn’t right for him.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-428\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Marcus-Jordan.jpg\" alt=\"marcus-jordan\" width=\"428\" height=\"285\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Hayley Hasselhoff</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>She was younger to the two children her parents had. Before starring in the show Hasselhoffs she appeared in the famous show Baywatch in 1999.</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-429\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Hayley-Hasselhoff.jpg\" alt=\"hayley-hasselhoff\" width=\"386\" height=\"257\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h2><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Ireland Baldwin</span></strong></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">A stunning young model with a phenomenal height of 6’2” was an IMG model at the age of 18 and has been popular ever since. She is famous for her fashionable lifestyle and high-profile friendships.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-430\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Ireland-Baldwin.jpg\" alt=\"ireland-baldwin\" width=\"363\" height=\"242\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h2><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Cassidy Gifford</span></strong></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">She is yet another person in the spotlight. In 2005 she starred in the show Not So Raven and her latest works include Gods not dead and the Gallows.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-431\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Cassidy-Gifford.jpg\" alt=\"cassidy-gifford\" width=\"447\" height=\"298\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Zelda Williams</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">The world was in mourning when in 2014 the world’s most loved comedian, Robin Williams, took his own life. Luckily, Williams’ daughter Zelda is a little piece of the star that is still with us. The 26-year-old followed her father into the spotlight by voicing the animated series “Teenage Mutant Ninja”</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-432\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Zelda-Williams.jpg\" alt=\"zelda-williams\" width=\"413\" height=\"275\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Damian Charles Harley</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Since his mother could not have a daughter as beautiful looking as her he was seen with his mother most of the time. He is acting right now.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-433\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Damian-Charles-Hurley.jpg\" alt=\"damian-charles-hurley\" width=\"488\" height=\"325\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Lorraine Nicholson</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Although we love Jack Nicholson, whether he’s Randle McMurphy or Dr. Buddy, but do his daughter’s boyfriends think the same? Probably not; he’s pretty terrifying. Lorraine, one of Nicholson’s 6 children, is currently an actress, and even produced and directed her own film in 2011.</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-449\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Lorraine-Nicholson.jpg\" alt=\"lorraine-nicholson\" width=\"464\" height=\"309\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Brooklyn Beckham</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>The Beckham children were pretty much celebrities before they were even born. Victoria and David’s eldest son, Brooklyn, has been spotted with his parents in London quite frequently. Most recently, Brooklyn has shown interest to photography, as well as his recent romance with Chloe Grace Moretz.</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-450\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Brooklyn-Beckham.jpg\" alt=\"brooklyn-beckham\" width=\"431\" height=\"287\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Kate Hudson</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>You’ve definitely heard of Kate Hudson, but did you know she is the daughter of actress Goldie Hawn and comedian/actor Bill Hudson. She has carved out her own name in Hollywood, appearing in many films such as <em>Almost Famous</em> and <em>50 First Dates.</em></h2>\r\n<h2><em><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-451\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Kate-Hudson-Collage.jpg\" alt=\"kate-hudson-collage\" width=\"482\" height=\"208\" /><!--nextpage--></em></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Chance King</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>He is the child of famous Larry king. He was given the chance to host the first baseball show when he was 10 years old. He is living a regular life along with his infamous father.</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-452\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Chance-King.jpg\" alt=\"chance-king\" width=\"451\" height=\"301\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h2> <strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Isabella and Olivia Giannulli</span></strong></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Lori Loughlin, aka Aunt Becky on <em>Full House, </em>has two daughters that are all grown up and already are creating their own space in the world of fashion by appearing in magazines and having huge followings on Twitter.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-453\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Lori-Loughlin.jpg\" alt=\"lori-loughlin\" width=\"492\" height=\"205\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Rumer Willis</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Daughter of Bruce Willis she has appeared in several movies as well as shows like Pretty Little Liars and Workahoics. She is an amazing actor.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-454\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Rumer-Willis.jpg\" alt=\"rumer-willis\" width=\"495\" height=\"243\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Eva Amurri</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Eva Amurri is the daughter of film director Franco Amurri and Susan Sarandon. She has become an actress as well, appearing in many films and TV shows. She recently got married and has a daughter and son of her own.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-455\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Eva-Amurri-Collage.jpg\" alt=\"eva-amurri-collage\" width=\"509\" height=\"229\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Miles Robbins</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>The youngest child of his parents Susan Sarandon and Tims Robbins. He is currently working as a DJ and is totally eccentric.</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-456\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Miles-Robbins.jpg\" alt=\"miles-robbins\" width=\"413\" height=\"275\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Violet Afflick</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Violet, daughter of Ben Affleck and Jennifer Garner, is growing up and is looking more and more like her famous mother every day. She also has a brother and a sister, though her parents have recently called it quits.</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-457\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Violet-Affleck-.jpg\" alt=\"violet-affleck\" width=\"504\" height=\"252\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Rainey Qualley</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">One of Andie MacDowell’s three children, Rainey Qualley, made a name for herself in the music industry, creating country hits like “Me and Johnny Cash”. Rainey also appeared in the final season of TV series “Mad Men”.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-458\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Rainey-Qualley.jpg\" alt=\"rainey-qualley\" width=\"433\" height=\"288\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Colin Hanks</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Son of superstar actor Tom Hanks. Although he was recently seen in the series Fargo it not known to everyone that he forged the acting career on himself.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-459\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Hanks-Collage.jpg\" alt=\"hanks-collage\" width=\"358\" height=\"332\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Brielle Biermann</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">The star of ‘The Real Housewives of Atlanta’ and her husband Kroy Biermann adopted Brielle and her sister, Ariana, a while ago. Since then, the sisters took their stepfather’s name and managed to build quite the fan base on Twitter. Today, Brielle is practically engaged to her boyfriend, baseball superstar Michael Kopech.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-460\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Brielle-Biermann.jpg\" alt=\"brielle-biermann\" width=\"443\" height=\"295\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Annie Starke</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Daughter to one of the most praised actresses of her generation, Glenn Close, Annie, debuted into the industry at the age of 13 in the film “South Pacific”, and today, at the age of 28, is back on screen in “We Don’t Belong Here”.</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-461\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Annie-Starke.jpg\" alt=\"annie-starke\" width=\"443\" height=\"295\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Sailor Cook</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Already following her mother in the lime light, this girl landed some gigs with Teen Vogue and later expressed her interest in acting. She is also very active on social media.</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-479\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Sailor-Cook.jpg\" alt=\"sailor-cook\" width=\"446\" height=\"297\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Mamie Gummer</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Mamie picked up many skills from her famous mother, Meryl Streep. She even acted alongside her in, <em>Ricki and the Flash </em><em>as</em> her on screen daughter. She is following in her mother’s footsteps and continuing to act. She had a recurring role on <em>The Good Wife</em>. Gummer is now 33 years old.</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-480\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/mamie.jpg\" alt=\"mamie\" width=\"430\" height=\"332\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Sophie Von Haselberg</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>She is the only daughter of the legendary actress Bette Midler. At first she was not interested in acting but later she took courses from Yale. She made her debut in Irrational Man.</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-481\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Sophie-Von-Haselberg.jpg\" alt=\"sophie-von-haselberg\" width=\"434\" height=\"290\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Maya Hawke</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">She is young and hence not involved in the acting world as yet. Her parents are no longer together but she is an image of both and is a sign of their once happy marriage.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-482\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Maya-Hawke.jpg\" alt=\"maya-hawke\" width=\"405\" height=\"270\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h2> <strong>Maude Apatow</strong></h2>\r\n<h2>Appeared as Cleo in the TV series “Girls” in 2015. Since then, she has also earned the role of Alexandra in “Other People”. Aside from her on-screen career, Maude is just a regular teenager who helps Zooey Deschanel with her website, Hello Giggles.</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-487\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Maude-Apatow.jpg\" alt=\"maude-apatow\" width=\"425\" height=\"283\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Drana De Niro</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Daughter of Robert De Niro, she is an actor as well as a film producer. She was adopted. She currently lives in New York with her son.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-488\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/drena-de-niro.jpg\" alt=\"drena-de-niro\" width=\"333\" height=\"309\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h2> <strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Lily Costner</span></strong></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Daughter of Kevin Costner. In 2004 she was elected as the miss golden globe. She graduated from Wesleyan University in 2008. Her famous role is Lily in the Babysitters club. She currently lives in California.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-490\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/lily-costner.jpg\" alt=\"lily-costner\" width=\"467\" height=\"304\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Ella Travolta</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">With a father who is an amazing actor in the industry, the little girl is just 16 years old and made her first debut in 2001 on the set of “Not under my roof.”</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-491\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Ella-Travolta.jpg\" alt=\"ella-travolta\" width=\"477\" height=\"318\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Georgia Ford</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Georgia Ford is the daughter of highly acclaimed actor, Harrison Ford. Georgia is known for her roles in the films <em>True Story, American Milkshake,</em><em> </em>and<em> </em><em>The Visitor. </em>Georgia battles Epilepsy and her father has said she is “his hero”.</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-492\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/georgia-ford.jpg\" alt=\"georgia-ford\" width=\"440\" height=\"328\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Mia Honey Threapleton</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Daughter of Kate Winslet. She is already 16 years and is a copy of her mother regarding looks. She usually does not appear in front of people but appeared with her mum in the Wimbledon Championship last year.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-493\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Mia-Honey.png\" alt=\"mia-honey\" width=\"481\" height=\"198\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Simone Alexandra Johnson</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Daughter of Dwayne Johnson also known as Rock and his first wife. Her parents separated when she as ten years old, but they remain good friends. She is good friends wither father and accompanies him to red carpet events.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-489\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Simon-Alexandra.png\" alt=\"simon-alexandra\" width=\"429\" height=\"276\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1> <strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Shiloh Jolie-Pitt</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Already she is very young she has already made headlines because of the way she dresses. She likes to act like a boy, and rumours are caught that she might be transgender. Angelina Jolie recently said that she always wanted to be a boy, but this is not confirmed.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-486\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Shiloh-Jolie-Pitt.png\" alt=\"shiloh-jolie-pitt\" width=\"440\" height=\"319\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Julie Pacino</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Eldest daughter of Al Pacino she has followed her parent’s steps and is in the industry as a producer and writer. Her most recent work for which she is famous is ABRACADABRA.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-485\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Julie-Pacino.png\" alt=\"julie-pacino\" width=\"496\" height=\"298\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Chloe Rose</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">She was born 11 years before her parents decided to divorce. Her parents met on the set of “Grease”. She made her debut in Australian soap opera when she was only seven years old but since then decided to go into the music industry.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-484\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Chloe-Rose.jpg\" alt=\"chloe-rose\" width=\"485\" height=\"323\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Alexandra Hoffman</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Dustin Hoffman has two children from his first marriage, and she is one of them. She is 28 and was famous because of her “thing” with Jonah Hill but since it has ended the hype died down.</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-483\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Alexandra-Hoffman.jpg\" alt=\"alexandra-hoffman\" width=\"431\" height=\"287\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Syndey Brooke Simpson</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Daughter of the athlete who was jailed for murdering his wife. His son and daughter both stayed out of the spotlight for many years. She is 30, lives in Atlanta and works as an event planner. Her parents say she is kind and hardworking.</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-478\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Sydeny-Brooke-Simpson.jpg\" alt=\"sydeny-brooke-simpson\" width=\"365\" height=\"464\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Ronan Farrow</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>The son of Hollywood legend Woody Allen has an amazing personality on his own. At the age of 28, he is a journalist, activist and former US government advisor.</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-477\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Ronan-Farrow.png\" alt=\"ronan-farrow\" width=\"495\" height=\"232\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Michael Neeson</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Born in 1995 to Liam Neeson, his mother passed away eight years earlier because of a serious head injury. Lastly, he was known to be effected badly by a serious drug addiction, but that was him dealing with his mother\'s death. He is working as fashion gallery curator nowadays.</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-476\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Michael-Neeson.png\" alt=\"michael-neeson\" width=\"366\" height=\"258\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Hazel Moder</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">The son of Julia Roberts who is the “pretty women”. He has a twin whose name is Phinnaeus. They are just ten years old but growing up quickly and have started looking like their mother.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-475\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Hazel-Moder.jpg\" alt=\"Exclusive...Julia Roberts Makes The Most Of Her Afternoon With Hazel And Henry\" width=\"317\" height=\"436\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Dylan Brosnan</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">When your father is so handsome and popular among people you have to keep up. Not only is he the son of Brad Pitt but also the model for high-end brands like Saint Lauren. He also has relationship problems like other teenagers.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-474\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Dylan-Brosnan.jpg\" alt=\"dylan-brosnan\" width=\"300\" height=\"396\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1> <strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Honey Boo Boo</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Mama June’s daughter. She first made an appearance when she was six years old. She became so popular that she hosted her show which was cancelled two years ago. Recently she made an appearance in which she looks very different.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-473\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Honey-Boo-Boo.jpg\" alt=\"honey-boo-boo\" width=\"339\" height=\"496\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h2> <strong>Zoe Jackson</strong></h2>\r\n<h2>Daughter of Samuel Jackson. She is 34 years old and followed her father into the industry and directed a movie called Everything is Samuel Jackson\'s fault.</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-472\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Zoe-Jackson.jpg\" alt=\"zoe-jackson\" width=\"443\" height=\"277\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Christiana Barkley</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Daughter of famous basketball player Charles Barkley. She is a socialite and is well known in the modelling world. She posts racy photographs on her Instagram account under the name “Villanova.”<img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-471\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Christina-Barkley.jpg\" alt=\"christina-barkley\" width=\"351\" height=\"351\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h2> <strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Jordan Zain Weiner</span></strong></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">The two politicians stole the spotlight when they had a fight over a sexting scandal. They have been fighting over the custody of their son who is four years now and growing quickly.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-470\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Jordan-Zain.jpg\" alt=\"jordan-zain\" width=\"304\" height=\"416\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Cameron Douglas</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>He is the oldest son of Michael Douglas. He has appeared in some famous movies one of them was Jackie Chan’s Nice Guy. He has been arrested sometimes for serious drug offences and has spent up to seven years in jail.</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-469\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/cameron-douglas.jpg\" alt=\"cameron-douglas\" width=\"436\" height=\"273\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Carys Zeta Douglas</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>She is the daughter of Michael Douglas and looks like both of her parents. She is just 13 years old. She is very close to both of her parents. Shopping for her mum and travelling around with her dad are her favourite past times.</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-468\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/carys-zeta.jpg\" alt=\"carys-zeta\" width=\"415\" height=\"375\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Huma Abedin</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Daughter of educators in British India, she was Hillary Clintons Vice Chairwomen in this year\'s campaign. She was recently involved in a love scandal with her husband but got custody of her son.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-467\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Huma-Abedin.jpg\" alt=\"Huma Abedin\" width=\"491\" height=\"276\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Bristol Palin</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>A TV star and reality show personality she is the daughter of Todd and Sarah Palin. In 2010 she went to the show “Dancing with the Stars” and won third place. She also starred in a show in 2012 called “Bristol Palin: Life’s a Tripp.”</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-466\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/bristolpalin.jpg\" alt=\"bristolpalin\" width=\"441\" height=\"293\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Sasha Spielberg</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Daughter of director Steven Spielberg Kate Capshaw. She is an American actress and attended Brown University. She is part of a band with Theo Spielberg.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-465\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Sasha-Speilberg.png\" alt=\"sasha-speilberg\" width=\"452\" height=\"252\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Homer James Jigme Gere</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">After 41 years of their marriage his parents, Richard Gere and Cary Lowell, had a very bad divorce and parted their ways. Their divorce was all over the media. He is very close to his dad.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-464\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/homer-1024x913.jpg\" alt=\"homer-1024x913\" width=\"385\" height=\"343\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Suzanne Charlton</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Daughter of famous footballer Bobby Charlton, she is a British Weather Forecaster for BBC. She has one son and lives in Hertfordshire.</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-463\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Suzanne-Charlton.png\" alt=\"suzanne-charlton\" width=\"505\" height=\"214\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Emerson Tenney</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Daughter of Teri Hatcher, a famous actress in Desperate housewives. She is just 19 years old and says she has no plans to act yet.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-462\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Emerson-Tenney.jpg\" alt=\"emerson-tenney\" width=\"437\" height=\"291\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Willow Smith</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">She is the daughter of famous Will Smith. She decided to take the music part instead of the acting one. She released an album in 2015 and has some modelling plans.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-448\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Willow-Smith.png\" alt=\"willow-smith\" width=\"455\" height=\"318\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong> <span style=\"color: #000000\">Sophia Richie</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Born to Lionel Richie and his ex-wife. She is now 18 years old and is already a mode. Modelling for various magazines like Vogue China has made her famous, and she was recently involved in the Yeezy Fashion Show.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-447\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Sophia-Rochie.png\" alt=\"sophia-rochie\" width=\"455\" height=\"320\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Maddox Jolie Pit</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">He was adopted by Angeline Jolie in 2002 from Columbia, and then Brad Pitt adopted him in 2006. He used to help his parents on the set but has recently been upset because of their split.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-446\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Maddox-Jolie-Pitt.png\" alt=\"maddox-jolie-pitt\" width=\"404\" height=\"289\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Paris Michael</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Second daughter of the famous pop star Michael Jackson with Debbie Rowie. She was very depressed after her father’s death and attempted suicide in 2013. Just recently she declared she is attending Alcoholics Anonymous meetings.</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-445\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Paris-Michael.png\" alt=\"paris-michael\" width=\"428\" height=\"304\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Corinne Bishop</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Eldest daughter of Jamie Foxx is now 19 years old and is a real beauty. She accompanies her father in award shows. Just this year she stole the spotlight by becoming miss golden globe and is now becoming both a model and an actress.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-444\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Corinne-Bishop.jpg\" alt=\"corinne-bishop\" width=\"453\" height=\"302\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Kaia Gerber</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Daughter of an infamous model Cindy Crawford and Rande Gerber she is already in the spotlight because she was featured on the cover of Vogue Paris along with her mother. She has another sister Pressley.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-443\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Kaia-Gerber.jpg\" alt=\"kaia-gerber\" width=\"453\" height=\"302\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Justin Combs</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">He has been in and out of Hollywood’s spotlight for a couple of years. He appeared on the show “My Super Sweet Sixteen” where his father gifted him $360,000. He is the only member of his family to have studied and gotten a degree.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-442\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Justin-Combs.jpg\" alt=\"justin-combs\" width=\"443\" height=\"295\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Earvin Johnson</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">More commonly known as E.J, he is the oldest of his three siblings. He was very famous because of the Reality Tv series, Rich Kids of Beverly Hills.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-441\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Earvin-Collage.jpg\" alt=\"earvin-collage\" width=\"397\" height=\"368\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Lily Atkinson</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Born to the legendary actor Roan Atkinson in 1995, she recently performed in a pretty raunchy cabaret this year around and her father seemed very calm about it.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-440\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Lily-Atkinson.png\" alt=\"lily-atkinson\" width=\"494\" height=\"264\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Jaden Smith</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>He has won regarding genes. He first appeared with his father in Men in Black 2, and after that, he worked on projects independently. He also has his clothes line which goes by the name of MSFTSrep.</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-439\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Jaden-Smith.jpg\" alt=\"jaden-smith\" width=\"477\" height=\"318\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Lily Rose Depp</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Daughter of Jhonny Depp and Vanessa Paradis, she made her first acting debut in 2014 in the movie “Tusk” when she was only 15 years old. She is currently working on three projects at the same time.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-438\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Lily-Rose-Depp.jpg\" alt=\"lily-rose-depp\" width=\"483\" height=\"322\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Iris Law</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Born to actor Jude Law and Sadie Forest, she is only 15 years old and has signed her first modelling contract with Chanel which is a big achievement at her age.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-437\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Iris-Law.png\" alt=\"iris-law\" width=\"488\" height=\"272\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Jane Carrey</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Having a father who was named as one of the funniest men in the world life couldn’t have been boring for her at all. She was interested in singing and tried her luck in American Idol 4 years back but did not make it to the end.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-436\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Jane-Carrey.jpg\" alt=\"jane-carrey\" width=\"458\" height=\"305\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Pauline Gretzky</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Daughter of the famous Ice hockey player she isn’t a little girl. Inspired by her father, she married Dustin Johnson, a golfer. She also has some kids of her own.</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-435\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Paulina.jpg\" alt=\"paulina\" width=\"474\" height=\"237\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Lourdes Leon</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>She was born to Madonna and Carlos Leon. She is the eldest daughter in the family and is campaigning for Stella McCartney currently while studying performing arts simultaneously.</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-434\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Lourdes-Leon.jpg\" alt=\"lourdes-leon\" width=\"492\" height=\"328\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h2></h2>','Kids Of Famous Parents- Then and Now','','inherit','closed','closed','','397-revision-v1','','','2016-12-12 15:01:21','2016-12-12 15:01:21','',397,'http://theladypost.com/2016/12/12/397-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(495,2,'2016-12-12 15:42:52','2016-12-12 15:42:52','<h2> <span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>1. Blac Chyna and Rob Kardashian</strong></span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">The last born among the Kardashians, Rob is engaged to the sensational Blac Chyna. The two are currently engaged and expecting a bouncing baby girl ahead of their wedding next year.</span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-529\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/blac.jpg\" alt=\"blac\" width=\"558\" height=\"314\" /><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>2. Lilit Avagyan And Reggie Bush</strong></span></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Reggie Bush is a famous NFL player and Kim Kardashian’s ex-boyfriend. Bush got married to Lilit Avagyan and for the two years they have lived together they have made two bouncy babies. Lilit is Kim’s twin sister.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-500\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Reggie-Bush-And-Lilit.png\" alt=\"reggie-bush-and-lilit\" width=\"421\" height=\"480\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>3. Eddie Murphy And Paige Butcher</strong></span></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">The great Eddie too has feelings. Eddie Murphy and his Australian sweetheart have been partners since 2012. They have since had a baby and moved into together. The union is getting better by the day.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-501\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Eddie-Murphy-and-Paige.png\" alt=\"eddie-murphy-and-paige\" width=\"447\" height=\"516\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>4. Kimora Lee and Tim Leissner </strong></span></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Kimora and Leissner met and hit the road running. Their heated affair culminated into a blissful marriage in 2013 and nine months down the line they welcomed their first born; Wolfe.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-502\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Kimora-Lee-And-Tim.png\" alt=\"kimora-lee-and-tim\" width=\"523\" height=\"347\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>5. Zac Efron and Sami Niró</strong></span></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Sami Niro and Zac Efron got to know each other through a mutual friend who’s also into Hollywood. They dated for two years but their affair did not materialize into a marriage. They have since parted ways.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-503\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Zac-and-Sami.png\" alt=\"zac-and-sami\" width=\"355\" height=\"495\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>6. Mariah Carey &amp; Nick Cannon</strong></span></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Nick met Mariah while she was shooting one of her hits in 2008. They fell in love at first sight and got drowned in the passionate affair. They had fun and did crazy things together. With time, the passion died down and they divorced six years later.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-504\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Maria-Carey-and-Nick.png\" alt=\"maria-carey-and-nick\" width=\"422\" height=\"445\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>7. Naya Rivera &amp; Ryan Dorsey</strong></span></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Rivera Naya is the famous star of ‘’Glee’’. She sent chills through her fans when she announced that she’d be marrying Ryan Dorcey after a relatively short courtship. Shortly after the wedding she announced that she was pregnant. They still seem happy together.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-505\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Naya-And-Ryan.png\" alt=\"naya-and-ryan\" width=\"498\" height=\"408\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>8. Lisa Bonet and Jason Momoa</strong></span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">This two cute Hollywood bigwigs met through a mutual friend and though ‘’Why not give it a try?’’ They have been married since 2007 and have had two children together.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-506\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Lisa-And-Jason-Momoa.png\" alt=\"lisa-and-jason-momoa\" width=\"447\" height=\"469\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>9. Rutina Wesley And Jacob Fishel</strong></span></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Despite going to the  prestigious Juilliard School in New York school together, Rutina Wesley first caught Jacobs’ attention after she gained fame on the ‘’True Blood’’ series. The two later met at an event and got acquainted. The two later tied the knots but sadly ended their union in 2013 due to ‘’irreconcilable differences.’’</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-514\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Jacob-Fishel-And-Rutina-Wesley.png\" alt=\"jacob-fishel-and-rutina-wesley\" width=\"452\" height=\"453\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h2> <span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>10. Gelila Assefa And Wolfgang Puck</strong></span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Puck and Gelila surely have a unique exotic taste for sweethearts. Despite their deep affections, they took it slow. After getting to know one another for four years, the two opted to wed, and they did it big. Their marriage has since been blessed with two lovely kids.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-515\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Gelila-and-Wolfgang.png\" alt=\"gelila-and-wolfgang\" width=\"406\" height=\"507\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>11. Michael Jordan &amp; Yvette Prieto</strong></span></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Michael Jordan too has been to the rock bottom of marriage. His second marriabe is proving to be successful and a blessing. He met Yvette at a night club in Miami back in 2013. Three years later and see what we’ve got; a happy couple!</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-516\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Michael-Jordan.png\" alt=\"michael-jordan\" width=\"463\" height=\"446\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>12. Ellen Pompeo and Chris Ivery</strong></span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Ellen Pompeo, a star of the ‘Grey’s Anatomy’ met her now-husband, Chris Ivery in 2003. Guess where they met? At a grocery store! The couple has been together with children for over a decade now.</span></h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-528\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/ellen-pompeo.png\" alt=\"ellen-pompeo\" width=\"448\" height=\"366\" />\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>13. Tina Turne