ears’ marriage. Even though Patton ended the 9-year marriage to Thicke, she occasionally looks back fondly on the nice moments they spent together. Thicke still tries to win her back.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>29. Demi Lovato and Wilmer Valderrama</strong></span></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Hollywood star Wilmer Valderrama hit it off with Demi Lovato, a famous pop singer in 2010. Over the years they have had their ups and downs. The relationship has been on and off, whenever they are together, they look cute together.<!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>30. Grace Hightower And Robert De Niro</strong></span></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Grace and Robert are a testimony that every marriage needs some rejuvenation. Grace is the founder of a non-profit organization that supports genocide victims in Rwanda. The two met back in 1997 and made their union official the same year. However, due to the nature of her work, their marriage suffered major setbacks. After the turbulent affair, they later renewed their vows and have since lived happily.<!--nextpage--> </span></h2>\r\n<h2></h2>','30 Beautiful Interracial Celebrity Couples','','inherit','closed','closed','','495-revision-v1','','','2016-12-12 15:45:44','2016-12-12 15:45:44','',495,'http://theladypost.com/2016/12/12/495-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(500,2,'2016-12-12 15:48:33','2016-12-12 15:48:33','','reggie-bush-and-lilit','','inherit','open','closed','','reggie-bush-and-lilit','','','2016-12-12 15:48:33','2016-12-12 15:48:33','',495,'http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Reggie-Bush-And-Lilit.png',0,'attachment','image/png',0),(501,2,'2016-12-12 15:49:13','2016-12-12 15:49:13','','eddie-murphy-and-paige','','inherit','open','closed','','eddie-murphy-and-paige','','','2016-12-12 15:49:13','2016-12-12 15:49:13','',495,'http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Eddie-Murphy-and-Paige.p