ver Kylie hAshlee Simpson &amp; Evan Rossave been dating on and off for many years. Despite the trend, they have stayed at it and none is willing to let the other go. Seeing them together is always a sight worth beholding.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-512\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Kylie-and-Tyga.png\" alt=\"kylie-and-tyga\" width=\"418\" height=\"311\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>26. Iman &amp; David Bowie</strong></span></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">The late David Bowie was quite a lover-boy. Despite being a womanizer, he never once cheated on his lovely wife Iman over the decades two decades they shared in marriage. They both had children from previous affairs with whom they merged into one admirable family that people still adores today. May his soul rest in eternal peace.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-511\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/David-Bowie-And-Iman.png\" alt=\"david-bowie-and-iman\" width=\"451\" height=\"302\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>27. Olivier Martinez And Halle Berry</strong></span></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Oliver and Halle started dating in 2010. Oliver is a renowned French actor while Halle Maria Berry is an American actress, a fashion model and film producer. The lovely couple met in while shooting ‘’The Dark Tide’’ and got engaged in 2012. Unfortunately, their marriage lasted only a few years as they divorced in 2015.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-510\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Halle-Berry-and-Oliver-Martinez.png\" alt=\"halle-berry-and-oliver-martinez\" width=\"380\" height=\"341\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>28. Paula Patt