ong>Roman Abramovich’s $1 Billion Yacht, Eclipse</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Yes, the Russian business mogul enjoys a lot of what many can only imagine of. The Chelsea Football Club owner is also a majority owner of one of Russia’s prominent holding companies. His 553-foot yacht, nicknamed ‘Eclipse’ costs a whooping $1 billion. This pricey toy is a true fantasy for most people across the globe, but not for the Russian billionaire.</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-607\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/roman-yatch.jpg\" alt=\"roman-yatch\" width=\"575\" height=\"373\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Maybach Exelero for Birdman</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Just recently, the celebrated pop star, Birdman, brought his $8 million Maybach Exelero to his fans on Twitter. The Cash Money C.E.O is truly balling regardless of the theories surrounding his Maybach’s ownership. This is a truly fancy whip, isn’t it?</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-615\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/birdman.jpg\" alt=\"birdman\" width=\"573\" height=\"322\" />\r\n<!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>Donald Trump’s Multi-million Boeing 757</strong></span></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">This Trump-branded Boeing 757 is one of its kind. Leave it to Donald to roll in this style. The $100 million private aircraft is designed to accommodate 43 passengers and comes with a VIP room. It has a gold and suede finish. Many can only fantasize about this level of luxury.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-616\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/trump.jpg\" alt=\"trump\" width=\"586\" height=\"333\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Jay Z’s $8 million Maybach Exelero</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>This posh toy, Maybach Exelero, is a dream for many but Jay Z knows best how it feels to roll in one. The exceptional celebrity first rocked the Maybach during his “Lost Ones” video. This was followed by a fleet of world’s expensive autos. If you love cars and music, then Jay Z is exactly what you love!</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-620\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Jaz-maybach.jpg\" alt=\"jaz-maybach\" width=\"586\" height=\"378\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>Roberto Cavalli with His $40 Million Yacht</strong></span></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">The Cavali cost Roberto a cool $40 million and the fancy yacht was truly one from the movies. It is best known for the parties hosted in the sea.  You won’t believe the models that would come your way thanks to such a posh toy.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-622\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/cavalli.jpg\" alt=\"cavalli\" width=\"584\" height=\"412\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>Bugatti Veyron for Birdman</strong></span></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">By now, you must be wondering who follows who between Jay Z and Birdman. When it comes to automobiles, the duo seems to be reading from the same page. This classy car saw Birdman part with a staggering $2 million.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-614\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Birdman-veyron.jpg\" alt=\"birdman-veyron\" width=\"604\" height=\"368\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Fighter Jet for Paul Allen</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>From marine collection to a fleet of expensive cars, Allen’s taste has never disappointed. While the transfer fee for this Russian Army fighter jet was undisclosed, we can bet on something mind-boggling. Just when fantasy met reality – Paul Allen is truly living the dream!</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-623\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/paul-allen-jet.jpg\" alt=\"paul-allen-jet\" width=\"583\" height=\"388\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>Jobs’ G5 for $40 Million</strong></span></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">If you are such a celebrity like Steve Jobs, you would want to fly so high. His $40 Million high-flying G5 aircraft is a testimony to his taste of life.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-621\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/steve-jobs.jpg\" alt=\"steve-jobs\" width=\"572\" height=\"284\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>Larry Page and His $43 Million Yacht</strong></span></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">The Google co-founder owns this floating toy for a staggering $43 million. Once owned by Phillipe Starck, the 193-foot luxury yacht is one of the great yacht reviews featuring here. The inside is way too hot than the outside. You can trust the job done by Phillipe.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-619\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/larry-page-yatch.jpg\" alt=\"larry-page-yatch\" width=\"577\" height=\"369\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>$2 Million Bugatti Veyron for Katie Price</strong></span></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">The former British singer turned a star on reality TV, Katie Price, rolls on this $2 million toy. Her Bugatti Veyron car is her latest addition. Rumor has it that she plans to paint in her signature color, pink. Before you can imagine, this toy is another one for Katie’s fleet of pink customized flashy automobiles.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-618\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/katie-price.jpg\" alt=\"katie-price\" width=\"568\" height=\"365\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>$33 Million Johnny Depp Yacht</strong></span></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">During his time on the <em>Pirates of the Caribbean </em>set, Johnny must have been influenced more than we ever thought. His $33 million yacht is not anything simple. His VAJORLIROJA name given to his toy is an acronym of his wife, daughter, son and himself. The adorable toy is available for weekly trip rent for around $130,000.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-617\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Johnny-Depp.jpg\" alt=\"johnny-depp\" width=\"568\" height=\"378\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>David Beckham $400,000 Rolls Royce Phantom</strong></span></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">If you are as great as Becks, you cannot worry about custom-making your machine into greatness. His superb Roll Royce Phantom cost him a cool $400,000. With all the fame around this guy and his wife Victoria, what could he not do anyway?</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-613\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/beckam-rolls.jpg\" alt=\"beckam-rolls\" width=\"569\" height=\"368\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>$14 Million Pharrell Yacht</strong></span></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">If you are looking for a brilliant ride in the sea, then Pharrell’s $14 million yacht should be your outright choice. It comes with its own music studio making it stand out from the rest of the art in the sea. It is a brilliant toy for P!</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-612\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/pharell.jpg\" alt=\"pharell\" width=\"569\" height=\"341\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>Lamborghini Gallardo for Chris Brown</strong></span></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">This $219,000 dope Lambo is a toy for the Pop star. It’s custom painted into a U.S fighter plane. If you own one like this, then the world would have to stand and watch you cruise around. Come on CB, a calm Lamborghini Gallardo?</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-611\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/chris-brown.jpg\" alt=\"chris-brown\" width=\"590\" height=\"311\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Richard Branson Necker Nymph submarine</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Branson enjoy his time on a fleet of fancy toys. Well, our pick on the $671,511 Necker Nymph is just but one of the many choices we had. This submarine is one of the coolest stuff you will ever come across. The business mogul knows how to enjoy his life and his fleet of posh toys says it all. This is a true meaning of balling really well!</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-610\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/richard-necker-nymph.jpg\" alt=\"richard-necker-nymph\" width=\"591\" height=\"373\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Jay Leno with His $500,000 Mercedes SLR McLaren</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Being one of Jay’s proud collections, this $0.5 million McLaren automobile is the most expensive in its pedigree in the market. Jay Leno knows what value he draws from his toys and he never jokes around them.</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-609\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/maclaren.jpg\" alt=\"maclaren\" width=\"575\" height=\"402\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Tiger Woods’ $25 Million Yacht</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>This is one toy that Tiger Woods really values. He named it Privacy for a reason: it’s one of the few things this celebrity has been able to enjoy lately. From his cheating scandal and public divorce saga, things have turned out great for this world figure. This toy is, however, on sale for $25 million.</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-608\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/tiger-woods.jpg\" alt=\"tiger-woods\" width=\"585\" height=\"352\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1></h1>','Expensive Toys for Celebrities and Famous People','','inherit','closed','closed','','596-revision-v1','','','2016-12-18 17:26:07','2016-12-18 17:26:07','',596,'http://theladypost.com/2016/12/18/596-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(628,2,'2016-12-18 17:33:24','2016-12-18 17:33:24','<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">They were once our favorite stars and were the most familiar faces on TV. Those who were children during the 80’s, still allot a special place to these stars. We, however, don’t see them as frequently as before. What happened to them? Some of them left the world of showbiz and now, spend their time in retirement. </span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Emilio Estevez</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>You might not know but Emilio is actor Charlie Sheen’s elder brother. He worked with stars like Sean Penn, during the 80’s.</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-571\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Emilio-Estevez.jpg\" alt=\"emilio-estevez\" width=\"478\" height=\"478\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Judd Nelson</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Judd set his mark with “The Breakfast Club”. Prior to that, he acted in Nikita.</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-572\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Judd-Nelson.jpg\" alt=\"judd-nelson\" width=\"482\" height=\"482\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Madonna</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>If you ask an 80’s kid about his or her music preference, they are most likely to answer: Madonna.</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-573\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Madonna.jpg\" alt=\"madonna\" width=\"470\" height=\"470\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1> <span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>Ally Sheedy</strong></span></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">The Brat Pack star began her journey with the 1983 hit: Bad Boys.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-574\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Ally-Sheedy.jpg\" alt=\"ally-sheedy\" width=\"477\" height=\"477\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong> </strong><strong>Molly Ringwald</strong></span></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">The charming redhead gained fame for her role in “Sixteen Candles”.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-575\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Molly-Ringwald.jpg\" alt=\"molly-ringwald\" width=\"475\" height=\"475\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Andrew McCarthy</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Andrew got himself another contract with hit <em>Brat Pack</em> lineup in “Pretty in Pink”.</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-576\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Andrew-McCarthy.jpg\" alt=\"andrew-mccarthy\" width=\"467\" height=\"467\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Demi Moore</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Leaving behind her disappointment in school, Moore established herself as one of the most desirable actresses in Hollywood.</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-577\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Demi-Moore.jpg\" alt=\"demi-moore\" width=\"462\" height=\"462\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Ricky Schroder</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>When he was just 12, he played the lead role in the famous TV show Silver Spoons.</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-585\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Ricky-Schroder.jpg\" alt=\"ricky-schroder\" width=\"462\" height=\"462\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1> <span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>Anthony Michael Hall</strong></span></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Anthony got spotlight after appearing in hit comedy “National Lampoon’s Vacation”.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-586\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Anthony-Michael-Hall.jpg\" alt=\"anthony-michael-hall\" width=\"464\" height=\"464\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>George Michael</strong></span></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">People still remember the English singer for hit tracks like Careless Whisper and Last Christmas.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-594\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/George-Michael.jpg\" alt=\"george-michael\" width=\"466\" height=\"466\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1> <span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>Alyssa Milano</strong></span></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Alyssa got breakthrough with her performance in ABC sitcom “Who\'s the Boss?”.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-593\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Alyssa-Milano.jpg\" alt=\"alyssa-milano\" width=\"473\" height=\"473\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>Tom Cruise</strong></span></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Cruise is still one of the big shots in Hollywood. Many of us don’t know that Cruise began his career with a minor role in the movie “The Outsiders”.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-591\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Tom-Cruise.jpg\" alt=\"tom-cruise\" width=\"463\" height=\"463\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>John Cusack</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Cusack entered the world of showbiz with his enthralling performance in “Better Off Dead”.</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-592\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/John-Cusack.jpg\" alt=\"john-cusack\" width=\"467\" height=\"467\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Michael J. Fox</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Canadian Michael J. Fox became known for his acting skills with his role in “Family Ties”.</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-590\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Michael-J.-Fox.jpg\" alt=\"michael-j-fox\" width=\"466\" height=\"466\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Mr. T</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Anyone who grew up during the 80’s will go WOW if you asked them about “The A-Team”. Indeed the name <strong>Mr. T</strong> became synonymous with the hit show.</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-589\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Mr.-T.jpg\" alt=\"mr-t\" width=\"478\" height=\"478\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Matthew Broderick</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Matthew set his footprint with his acting in “Ferris Bueller\'s Day Off”. He eventually made it to some of the biggest hits in Hollywood.</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-588\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Matthew-Broderick.jpg\" alt=\"matthew-broderick\" width=\"468\" height=\"468\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>Rob Lowe</strong></span></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Rob was also a part of “The Outsiders” cast along with Tom Cruise. He also appeared in <em>Brat Pack</em>.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-587\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Rob-Lowe.jpg\" alt=\"rob-lowe\" width=\"471\" height=\"471\" /> <!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>Kevin Bacon</strong></span></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">He became a household name after playing the character of Ren McCormack. Even today he is a regular face in Hollywood movies.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-584\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Kevin-Bacon.jpg\" alt=\"kevin-bacon\" width=\"465\" height=\"465\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>Patrick Dempsey</strong></span></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">The actor became audience favorite after playing a nerdy character in “Can’t Buy Me Love”.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-583\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Patrick-Dempsey.jpg\" alt=\"patrick-dempsey\" width=\"467\" height=\"467\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Cyndi Lauper</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Her first album “She\'s So Unusual” was released in 1983. She eventually established herself as the pop sensation of the decade.</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-582\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Cyndi-Lauper.jpg\" alt=\"cyndi-lauper\" width=\"468\" height=\"468\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1> <strong>Matt Dillon</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Bad boy Matt Dillon took part in many 80’s flicks. He was one of the heartthrobs of the decade.</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-581\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Matt-Dillon.jpg\" alt=\"matt-dillon\" width=\"462\" height=\"462\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>Drew Barrymore</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Successful Hollywood actress Drew Barrymore appeared on television when she was just 11! Her first breakthrough came with <em>E.T. the Extra-Terrestrial.</em></h2>\r\n<h2><em><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-580\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Drew-Barrymore.jpg\" alt=\"drew-barrymore\" width=\"470\" height=\"470\" /><!--nextpage--></em></h2>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>Corey Feldman</strong></span></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Corey commenced his acting career when he was just 3. He became popular for his performance in “The Goonies”.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-579\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Corey-Feldman.jpg\" alt=\"corey-feldman\" width=\"462\" height=\"462\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>Debbie Gibson</strong></span></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Her hit single <em>Foolish Beat </em>hit the top of the Billboard soon after it was released; making her one of the youngest artists to achieve that feat.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-578\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Debbie-Gibson.jpg\" alt=\"debbie-gibson\" width=\"470\" height=\"470\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>','See How These Stars From The 80’s Aged UP','','inherit','closed','closed','','568-revision-v1','','','2016-12-18 17:33:24','2016-12-18 17:33:24','',568,'http://theladypost.com/2016/12/18/568-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(629,2,'2016-12-18 17:38:22','2016-12-18 17:38:22','<h1><strong>1. Julia Roberts – $170m</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Her smile can light up the world, literally. Julia has that cute smile that keeps eyes glued to the screens. At one point she was the best paid actress in Hollywood. Today she has come of age and is whiling away her sunset days with $170m to her name.</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-537\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Julia-Roberts.png\" alt=\"julia-roberts\" width=\"460\" height=\"458\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">2. Angelina Jolie – Over $160m</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Angelina Jolie is definitely one of the world’s most glamorous actresses alive. The successful Hollywood star has accumulated with a personal fortune worth over $160 million and she’s not yet done!</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-538\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Angelina-Jolie.png\" alt=\"angelina-jolie\" width=\"325\" height=\"455\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">3. Robert De Niro – $350m</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Old is gold, so they say. Robert is a mentor to many upcoming actors. It’s arguable that he is the greatest actor of all times. In recent time his career has slowed down due to old age. In his long career he has built a fortune worth $350m.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-539\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Robert-De-Niro.png\" alt=\"robert-de-niro\" width=\"539\" height=\"333\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">4. George Clooney – $250m</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Mr Clooney has had a very glittering career both as an actor and as a director Hollywood. His hard work has made him one of the most-after professionals in Hollywood. He has since amassed over $250m.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-566\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/George.jpg\" alt=\"george\" width=\"514\" height=\"367\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>5. Jessica Alba – $350m</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Jessica is a definition of beauty and brains. She’s talented without a shadow of doubt. Her stellar acting career has made her an envy of many. Besides acting, she is an entrepreneur with a business empire worth over $350m.</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-540\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Jessica-Alba.png\" alt=\"jessica-alba\" width=\"460\" height=\"464\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>6. John Travolta – $170m</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>John Travolta was a big deal back in the 70s. He was a phenomenal Hollywood star before his career dropped for a while before a rejuvenation that catapulted him back to the top. Over the years he has made a whopping $170m for himself.</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-541\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/John-Travolta.png\" alt=\"john-travolta\" width=\"446\" height=\"532\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>7. Leonardo DiCaprio – $245m</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Leonardo is quite an academy darling. After many years’ struggle he finally landed the much sought after academy award. Forbes value him at $245m.</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-542\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Leonardo-Di-Caprio.png\" alt=\"leonardo-di-caprio\" width=\"570\" height=\"300\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">8. Robert De Niro – $350m</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Often cited as one of the greatest actors of all time, De Niro’s career has slowed a lot in recent years. However, he is still a big draw, and he’s amassed a fortune of $350m in his career.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-543\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Robert-De-Niro-1.png\" alt=\"robert-de-niro\" width=\"581\" height=\"359\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1> <strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">9. Taylor Swift – $360m</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Taylor Swift has a powerful voice and very seductive body. Taylor has created a world and is doing running it as its queen. She has featured in many romantic scenes and her bank account grows with every hit. Her net worth as 2016 is $360m.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-553\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Taylor-Swift.png\" alt=\"taylor-swift\" width=\"582\" height=\"325\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">10. Christopher Nolan – $180m</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">I guess you’ve watched or at least heard of Batman. Chris is the guy behind the marvelous piece of work put into reviving Batman and making Tom Hardy what he is along the way. As a renowned director, Chris Nolan has made a $180m fortune.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-554\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Christopher-Norlan.png\" alt=\"christopher-norlan\" width=\"565\" height=\"375\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>11. Will Smith – $260m</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Will smith one of the most famous personalities in the world. Since his breakthrough in ‘’Prince of Bel Air’’ he has never looked back. He has been soaring with a sensation after a sensation. He is currently valued at $260m.</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-555\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Will-Smith.png\" alt=\"will-smith\" width=\"567\" height=\"318\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">12. Sean Connery – $300m</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">There have been many James Bonds but Sean Connery was the most outstanding. Thanks to his hard work he won an academy award for the most all-round legend. Sean net worth is roughly $300.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-556\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Sean-Connery.png\" alt=\"sean-connery\" width=\"393\" height=\"488\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">13. Denzel Washington – $200m</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Denzel Washington is a man with a big presence and an equally fat bank account. The fact that he became the first black-American ever to win Academy Awards explains it better. To-date he’s still starling. $200m and counting.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-561\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Denzel-Washington.png\" alt=\"denzel-washington\" width=\"556\" height=\"416\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>14. Jay-Z – $700m</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Also known as Mr Beyoncé Knowles, Jaz-Z definitely has the bragging rights in the hip-hop industry. The rap god’s career has thrived over the last 30 years. His net worth is estimated to be around $700m.</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-562\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Jayz.png\" alt=\"jayz\" width=\"543\" height=\"383\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">15. Clint Eastwood – $375m</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">After a fantastic career in Hollywood as an actor, Clint graduated from an award-winning actor to an award winning director with a whopping worth of $375m.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-560\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Clint-Eastwood.png\" alt=\"clint-eastwood\" width=\"569\" height=\"356\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1> <strong>16. <span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>Sylv</strong>ester Stallone – $400m</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">‘’John Rambo’’ is one sensation the world is not about to get over. In his lifetime he has been a script-writer, an actor, and eventually a Hollywood Legend. With search passion and versatility amassing $400m is no big deal.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-565\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Sylvester.jpg\" alt=\"sylvester\" width=\"532\" height=\"385\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">17. Sandra Bullock – $200m</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">MS Bullock has been working in Hollywood for over twenty years. Along the way she has won numerous awards and has earn more than $200m.</span></h2>