. With an exponentially growing expire, she is currently valued at $450m.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-551\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Victoria-Beckhamp.png\" alt=\"victoria-beckhamp\" width=\"438\" height=\"437\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">22. Robert Downey Jr. – $220m</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Robert Downey is known for Iron Man. He is eminent for giving zest to the movie and marking it a hit. Overall, he has amassed about $220m for himself.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-550\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Robert-Downey.png\" alt=\"robert-downey\" width=\"431\" height=\"432\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>23. Mel Gibson – $425m</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Known for his exceptional skills and weapon flicks, Mel is one of the founding stars of modern-day Hollywood. Mel Gibson quite a wealthy man; $425m.</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-549\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Mel-Gibson.png\" alt=\"mel-gibson\" width=\"548\" height=\"405\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong> 24. <span style=\"color: #000000\">Beyoncé Knowles – $450m</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">She started out as part of the famous destiny kids. No-one saw it coming but nonetheless Beyonce the songstress has surprised many with a superb career. Her fame got a great boost from her marriage to Jay-Z. Today, she’s valued at $450m.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-548\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Beyonce-Knowless.png\" alt=\"beyonce-knowless\" width=\"573\" height=\"347\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong> 25. <span style=\"color: #000000\">Keanu Reeves – $350m</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Nice guys finish too. Keanu is a man of honor and a kind heart. Riches come with arrogance but the reverse is true for Keanu. His goodness has pursued him with a $350m reward.  </span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-547\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Keanu.png\" alt=\"keanu\" width=\"580\" height=\"398\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>26. Mark Wahlberg – $225m</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Mark is was formerly known for his role on ‘’New Kids on the Block.” Besides acting, he is a renowned Calvin Klein brand model. Mark has a net worth of around $225m.</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone  wp-image-546\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Mark-Wahlberg.png\" alt=\"mark-wahlberg\" width=\"524\" height=\"439\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>27. Shahrukh Khan – $600m</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>No doubt Shahrukh Khan is the king of Bollywood. He goes unrivaled in the Indian film industry. With a great potential to explore, he is currently valued at $600m.</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-545\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Shahrukh-Khan.png\" alt=\"shahrukh-khan\" width=\"541\" height=\"401\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>28. Tom Cruise – $500m</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>Tom Cruise alias Mr. Reliable is a big name in Hollywood. Building his brand did not happen overnight. It took him a decade of hard work before the results showed. In the last ten years he has made over $100 from box office alone. Is cumulative worth is well over $500m.</h2>\r\n<h2><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-544\" src=\"http://theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Tom-Cruise.png\" alt=\"tom-cruise\" width=\"438\" height=\"524\" /><!--nextpage--></h2>\r\n<h1><strong>29. K. Rowling – $1bn</strong></h1>\r\n<h2>You’ve certainly heard of the book or the series Harry Potter. J.K Rowling is the brain behind the books. She may not have the younger Hollyw