d him $360 million.</span></h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-368\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Kobe-Bryant.png\" alt=\"kobe-bryant\" width=\"407\" height=\"403\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">29. Fernando Alonso $200 Million</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Fernando Alonso was a formula one driver with impressive track records. He knew what he wanted to be in life by age 3. With a career spanning that long, $200 million is not too much the ace driver.</span></h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-367\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Fernando-Alonso.png\" alt=\"fernando-alonso\" width=\"571\" height=\"323\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">30. Bob Arum $250 Million</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"> Bob promotes boxing. He was the guy behind the fight of the century. His marketing skills have made his a net worth of $250 million.</span></h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-366\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Bob-Arum.png\" alt=\"bob-arum\" width=\"541\" height=\"375\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">31. Lionel Messi $280 Million</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"> Arguably the greatest footballer of all times, Messi makes over $16 every year. His net worth of $280 grows by the days.</span></h2>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-365\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Lionel-Messi-300x166.png\" alt=\"lionel-messi\" width=\"587\" height=\"325\" />\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000\"><!--nextpage--></span>','30 Richest Athletes In The World','','inherit','closed','closed','','361-revision-v1','','','2016-12-19 09:38:28','2016-12-19 09:38:28','',361,'http://www.theladypost.com/2016/12/19/361-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(637,2,'2016-12-19 09:54:13','2016-12-19 09:54:13','<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">A wedding venue is vital for every bride, book a honeymoon suite, and enjoy these unending dresses. Have a look at these truthfully unique brides.</span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Bridal Balloon</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">A wedding cannot be complete minus balloons, and what this bride did is to take a step further by having a dress that uniquely resembles small balloons!</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-325\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Bridal-Balloon-201x300.jpg\" alt=\"bridal-balloon\" width=\"314\" height=\"469\" /></span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Wedding Photos</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Well, this wedding photo is certainly a craft. This moment ca never be forgotten by the couple.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-326 \" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Wedding-Photos-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"wedding-photos\" width=\"344\" height=\"344\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">DIY Dress</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">A wedding is an expensive undertaking, and coming up with cost-cutting ideas is a nice idea. This bride decided to go for a DIY wedding dress.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-327\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/DIY-Dress-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"diy-dress\" width=\"322\" height=\"429\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Sassy Bride In Rented Limousine</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">When you give a bride freedom to come up with dress ideas, she will total take it to another level. We’re happy that this wedding dress fit into the rented limousine…otherwise, it would have turned disastrous.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-328\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Sassy-Bride-202x300.jpg\" alt=\"sassy-bride\" width=\"335\" height=\"498\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Bridal Gown</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">As you can note from the previous list of our wedding dresses, some brides have taken it to the next level. They end to insist on something unique for their special day really, but this lady took it to the extreme.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-329\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Bridal-Gown-218x300.jpg\" alt=\"bridal-gown\" width=\"331\" height=\"456\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Have Your Special Day Cake and Eat It</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">This bride disagrees with everything.  She went for a tailor-made dress that is also unique and edible. You can imagine the amount of time spent in creating this tasty wedding dress.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-330\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Have-Your-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"have-your\" width=\"393\" height=\"393\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>Crazy Cat Lady</strong></span></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Ever wondered how an animal themed wedding dress will look like, well this lady did exactly that by going for a cat themed tailor-made dress.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-331\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Crazy-Cat-210x300.jpg\" alt=\"crazy-cat\" width=\"326\" height=\"466\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Donut Be Nuts!</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Well, if you think you have seen enough of edible wedding dresses, then the next thing is a bride coming up with something more unique and original. I won’t lie; I would be attempted to take a bite out of her beautifully crafted wedding dress.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-332\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Donut-Be-Nuts-300x236.jpg\" alt=\"donut-be-nuts\" width=\"453\" height=\"356\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Disney Comes to Life</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">This bubblegum pink number executed the Disney idea perfectly. It is one of the unique and original wedding gowns we have seen so far.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-333\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Disney-Comes-188x300.jpg\" alt=\"disney-comes\" width=\"301\" height=\"480\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Cost Cutting</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">One way of cutting your wedding dress costs is to forget the suit and wedding dress entirely and just go with some decorative body art.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-334\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Cost-Cutting-300x260.jpg\" alt=\"cost-cutting\" width=\"416\" height=\"360\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">The Sweetest Bride</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Heard of the expression, “you can have your cake and eat it too”? That is that what this couple is living this quote. After all, it was a special day for them.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-335\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/The-Sweetest-Bride-208x300.jpg\" alt=\"the-sweetest-bride\" width=\"316\" height=\"455\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Double-Click</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Nothing will be romantic than geeking out on your special day. This bride took it to the next level with a tailor-made wedding gown, though it’s made of computer mice and not real mice. That would have turned weird.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-336\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Double-Click-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"double-click\" width=\"327\" height=\"436\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Katniss?</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">It looks like Katniss Everdeen from ‘The Hunger Games’ would have worn for her big day, a beauty made out of sunset shades and flames. Worry no more about grabbing the fire extinguisher, though in this case, you will surely get worried; they are not real flames.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-337\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Katniss-237x300.jpg\" alt=\"katniss\" width=\"323\" height=\"409\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">You’ve Been Tangoed</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Everyone wants to stand out during his/her wedding day. But this bride took it to the next level, don’t you think? She opted for a nice shade of tangerine on her wedding day.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-343\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/You-ve-Been-237x300.jpg\" alt=\"you-ve-been\" width=\"344\" height=\"436\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">White Chocolate Wonder</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Edible and original wedding dresses are coming right up. This one is another luscious wonder, made entirely of white chocolate. Hope it will not be too sunny on the bride’s special day otherwise she might start melting!</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-344\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/White-Chocolate-Wonder-219x300.jpg\" alt=\"white-chocolate-wonder\" width=\"328\" height=\"449\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Customer Wedding Dress</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">If you are thinking of a custom tailor-made dress for your wedding day, you should know that a blue color symbolizes stability, loyalty, and security. So blue is a no go zone!</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-345\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Custom-Wedding-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"custom-wedding\" width=\"389\" height=\"389\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Glittery Wedding Limo Service</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Nothing says “I love you” quite like a dress made up of lots of bright pink hearts with some glitter for added effect. Since this bride looks everything but traditional, we wonder if the rented wedding limo was covered in pink glitter, too.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-348\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Glittery-Wedding-263x300.jpg\" alt=\"glittery-wedding\" width=\"369\" height=\"421\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">No Regular Wedding Dress Rental</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Who doesn’t love a leopard print, don’t get me wrong, though? Let’s us just say this custom pink and leopard print wedding dress is not a normal wedding dress you can get from a regular dress rental store.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-349\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/No-Regular-Wedding-300x249.jpg\" alt=\"no-regular-wedding\" width=\"420\" height=\"348\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Where’s The Dress?</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Just trying to figure out what really going on in this picture. This bride decided to look like a tree. Did you notice the bride? You may need to take a closer look.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-352\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Wheres-The-Dress-239x300.jpg\" alt=\"wheres-the-dress\" width=\"363\" height=\"456\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Neon Bright</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Giving our bridesmaid freedom to choose their dresses for the special day is a nice way to keep everyone happy. Cost can be kept low, and your favorite people get the freedom to choose a dress of their choice. However, you might end up with something colorful as this neon themed dress.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-353\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Neon-Bright-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"neon-bright\" width=\"424\" height=\"282\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Origami Wedding Dress</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">To be honest, it is not the wedding day that is vital – It is the fact that you and your other half will be exchanging vows and promise to commit to each other for the remaining days of your lives. You would love to be with you bride even before picking such a dramatic gown like this.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-354\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Origami-Wedding-200x300.jpg\" alt=\"origami-wedding\" width=\"321\" height=\"482\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">All of The Lights</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Every bride wants to show off on the wedding day. She wants a hammered limousine and extravagant venue. She wants the perfect honeymoon suite in the most amazing seven-star hotel. And more than that, she wants to be perfectly dressed and look beautiful.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-356\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/All-Of-The-Lights-236x300.png\" alt=\"all-of-the-lights\" width=\"355\" height=\"451\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Custom Wedding Dress Or Wigs?</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Consider your special day and think of the “hair” or “wig” that can be right for the occasion. On the centrally the bride decided to get a dress made fully out of human hair at a price of $78,000 is a perfect match for the bride.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-357\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Custom-Wedding-Dress-262x300.jpg\" alt=\"custom-wedding-dress\" width=\"347\" height=\"397\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Go Green</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">What a better way to create a scene that to have a dress made out of recycled materials. Food papers, sweet wrappers, it does not matter but ensures that it is the right color. We love this wedding dress!</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-359\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Go-Green-244x300.jpg\" alt=\"go-green\" width=\"338\" height=\"415\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Balloon Gown</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">This balloon wedding dress is an art. The second piece of art that we have seen, but to be honest, we really love it! Sometime it is good to mix things up and change the style of the wedding dress. And this balloon wedding dress should be the first one on your mind.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-358\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Balloon-Gown-221x300.jpg\" alt=\"balloon-gown\" width=\"363\" height=\"492\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Camo Camp Out</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">This camo-wedding dress is something only Honey Boo Boo’s mamma could go for on her special day. For an avid hunter, this is a perfect match but not for us; we would prefer something more of ivory.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-355\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Camo-Camp-Out-286x300.jpg\" alt=\"camo-camp-out\" width=\"379\" height=\"398\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Toilet Roll Creation</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Well, when you get the right toilet paper, you buy enough to ensure that you never run out of stock shortly, this bride went an extra step and designed a wedding dress from tissue papers. She knows what she loves and hopes she gets a matching pair of shoe.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-351\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Toilet-Roll-Creation-300x261.png\" alt=\"toilet-roll-creation\" width=\"425\" height=\"370\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Terrifically Tentacled</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Just like “The Little Mermaid” this tentacle-inspired wedding dress is definitely up to our alley. Irrespective of our dislike of seafood, we highly love this wedding dress.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-350\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Terrifically-Tentacled-271x300.jpg\" alt=\"terrifically-tentacled\" width=\"380\" height=\"421\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Bright Like A Diamond</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">The bride chose the custom-made wedding dress for her special day. A good match in case there would be an electricity blackout.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-347\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Bright-Like-A-Diamond-300x232.jpg\" alt=\"bright-like-a-diamond\" width=\"449\" height=\"347\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Double Wedding</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">As a matter of fact, no good can come from having a joint wedding with your best friend, especially when your tastes are this similar. On the contrary, this special day for the couple was brightened by the magenta.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-346\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Double-Wedding-300x213.jpg\" alt=\"double-wedding\" width=\"443\" height=\"315\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Wifey $ Lifey</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">There is nothing that shows your commitment more than having ‘Wifey’ emblazoned across your bottom wedding dress for the special day. At least this bride won’t forget what she’s up to. Turns in a mirror and Oh yes!</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-342\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Wifey-4-Lifey-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"wifey-4-lifey\" width=\"469\" height=\"352\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">The Royal Dress</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">It is clear and self-explanatory – the wedding was “The Royal Wedding” themed. The dress looks amazingly royal to us!</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-341\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/The-Royal-Dress-253x300.jpg\" alt=\"the-royal-dress\" width=\"399\" height=\"474\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Honeymoon Suite Ready</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">In case you had not noticed, the bride chose a dress made out of more than one thousand rubbers. A clear indication of her preparedness once they get to the honeymoon.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-340\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Honeymoon-Suite-234x300.jpg\" alt=\"honeymoon-suite\" width=\"329\" height=\"422\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Peek-A-Bump</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">It is hard work when you try to find a nice looking dress for your special day if you happen to be pregnant. Most brides want to cover their baby bump but not this bride here. She had her custom-made dress created to show off her bump, allowing her baby to watch the ceremony.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-339\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Peek-A-Bump-240x300.jpg\" alt=\"peek-a-bump\" width=\"342\" height=\"428\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Wedding Limo, Please!</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">It is said that the average wedding in the US costs not less than $20,000. Well, how much of the budget do you think this bride spent on her wedding hummer limo?</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-338\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Wedding-Limo-300x190.jpg\" alt=\"wedding-limo\" width=\"471\" height=\"298\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>','Epic Brides You Can’t Unsee','','inherit','closed','closed','','322-revision-v1','','','2016-12-19 09:54:13','2016-12-19 09:54:13','',322,'http://www.theladypost.com/2016/12/19/322-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(638,2,'2016-12-19 09:57:14','2016-12-19 09:57:14','<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Before marrying Prince William, Kate Middleton was one of those girls who attend university to pursue a degree. But back in 2002, a wild night on ramp changed everything when she took part in a fashion show held at her university. That was the exact night when the Prince settled his mind that this is the girl of his dream, she is the ONE.</span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-293\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/2-236x300.png\" alt=\"2\" width=\"354\" height=\"450\" /></span>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">At first look it seems like she is being chased by some paparazzis. No wonder she is known as more of a ‘commoner’ than a princess.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-292\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/1-226x300.jpg\" alt=\"1\" width=\"358\" height=\"475\" /></span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Even in a silly hat she looks great. This is perhaps the best thing about the princess of people – she looks smoking hot even in the dullest dresses.</span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-305\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/14-2-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"14\" width=\"338\" height=\"450\" /></span>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Perhaps she doesn’t have an agreement with the wind, like Marilyn Monroe did! This happened back in 2014 in Australia.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-295\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/4-248x300.png\" alt=\"4\" width=\"327\" height=\"395\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">It is believed that Kate is so strong willed that she won’t even bow to the Queen. Paparazzis nevertheless have no regard for that.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-296\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/5-1-239x300.png\" alt=\"5\" width=\"340\" height=\"426\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">It had not been more than three months that Kate hit the court after giving birth to George, to show her volleyball prowess. She was seen wearing a casual top and skin-tight jeggings.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-297\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/6-209x300.jpg\" alt=\"6\" width=\"318\" height=\"457\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">There are very few photos of Kate’s baby bump. This one picture more or less makes up for that.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-301\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/10-1-300x166.png\" alt=\"10\" width=\"509\" height=\"282\" /></span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Prince William of course fell in love with Kate by being mesmerized by her natural beauty. This dress however blew away the last doubt from the prince’s mind.<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-299\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/8-1-241x300.png\" alt=\"8\" width=\"347\" height=\"432\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">We don’t know whether the queen was outraged seeing this photo. It discloses the human side of the royal family.<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-300\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/9-1-300x166.png\" alt=\"9\" width=\"456\" height=\"253\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">In spite of being a Princess, she never shies away from enjoying life to the fullest. Wearing revealing clothes is apparently is not a big deal to her.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-298\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/7-1-244x300.png\" alt=\"7\" width=\"349\" height=\"429\" /></span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">There are very few photos of Kate’s baby bump. This one picture more or less makes up for that.<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-302\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/11-234x300.png\" alt=\"11\" width=\"356\" height=\"457\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">In this ‘Blue Wonder’ shot, Kate looks gorgeous and smart. She looks like a princess in one of those Disney princess movies.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-303\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/12-2-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"12\" width=\"404\" height=\"539\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Another picture showing how rarely the Princess cares about those camera clicks. Could it be that she knows people enjoy getting those glimpse?<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-309\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/18-2-300x185.jpg\" alt=\"18\" width=\"469\" height=\"289\" /></span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Kate doesn’t let go a chance to do justice to her fame as ‘princess of the people’. Here, she is attending a children’s fundraiser in a not too revealing but appealing dress.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\" wp-image-294 alignnone\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/3-238x300.png\" alt=\"3\" width=\"386\" height=\"486\" /></span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">The Duchess of Cambridge (Kate Middleton) attended a special screening of the Recovery Street Film Festival before heading to the red carpet premiere of A Street Cat Named Bob at the Curzon Mayfair Cinema Theatre in London.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-315\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/24-152x300.jpg\" alt=\"24\" width=\"284\" height=\"560\" /></span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">The Princess enjoys a game of cricket wearing a red velvet dress. We however could not know whether she managed to hit a few boundaries.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-307\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/16-2-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"16\" width=\"319\" height=\"426\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Kate never falls short of fulfilling her fans’ wishes. In the meantime, she is also giving the crowd a show.<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-308\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/17-2-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"17\" width=\"310\" height=\"414\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Kate wore this sweet blue while attending a red carpet, back in 2012.Anyone would admit that that body-hugging gown rocks.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-312\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/21-2-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"21\" width=\"332\" height=\"443\" /></span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">The Princess never loses her composure. She knows how to make quick comebacks even when caught off-guard.<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-306\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/15-2-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"15\" width=\"331\" height=\"441\" /></span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">During the Australia tour in 2014, the Princess saw her skirt scooting up while she was holding Prince George. She just smiled and continued her steps, confidently.<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-311\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/20-2-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"20\" width=\"317\" height=\"423\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Who could be a better choice than the royal pair to improve ties between Great Britain and Australia? Here she is in a wonderful floral design dress.<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-304\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/13-2-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"13\" width=\"342\" height=\"456\" /></span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">This cocktail dress matched Kate so good that there is no way to tell that she is pregnant. She knows very well just how much revealing you can be, without being slutty.<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-313\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/22-2-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"22\" width=\"334\" height=\"446\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Kate has always been known for her demure choices. This dress justifies that even more.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-314\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/23-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"23\" width=\"321\" height=\"428\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Just like a supermodel, she is moving forward with a never dull expression in her face. Trademark Kate!<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-310\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/19-2-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"19\" width=\"337\" height=\"449\" /></span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">When she gave this impressively regal side-eye to a photographer during a ceremony at Westminster Abbey.</span></h2>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-289\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/27-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"27\" width=\"472\" height=\"314\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">That time she was literally so perfect that a random photograph was more beautiful than any elaborately staged magazine cover.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-290\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/26-195x300.jpg\" alt=\"26\" width=\"320\" height=\"492\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Kate can’t seem to take her eyes off her prince – she’s been shooting William several sweet looks of love throughout the tour.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-291\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/25-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"25\" width=\"439\" height=\"329\" /></span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><!--nextpage--></span></h2>','27 Photos that Prove Kate Middleton is Too Hot and the Prince is a Lucky Man','','inherit','closed','closed','','288-revision-v1','','','2016-12-19 09:57:14','2016-12-19 09:57:14','',288,'http://www.theladypost.com/2016/12/19/288-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(639,2,'2016-12-19 09:58:51','2016-12-19 09:58:51','<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">A wedding venue is vital for every bride, book a honeymoon suite, and enjoy these unending dresses. Have a look at these truthfully unique brides.</span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Bridal Balloon</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">A wedding cannot be complete minus balloons, and what this bride did is to take a step further by having a dress that uniquely resembles small balloons!</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-325\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Bridal-Balloon-201x300.jpg\" alt=\"bridal-balloon\" width=\"314\" height=\"469\" /></span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Wedding Photos</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Well, this wedding photo is certainly a craft. This moment ca never be forgotten by the couple.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-326 \" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Wedding-Photos-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"wedding-photos\" width=\"404\" height=\"404\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">DIY Dress</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">A wedding is an expensive undertaking, and coming up with cost-cutting ideas is a nice idea. This bride decided to go for a DIY wedding dress.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-327\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/DIY-Dress-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"diy-dress\" width=\"356\" height=\"474\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Sassy Bride In Rented Limousine</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">When you give a bride freedom to come up with dress ideas, she will total take it to another level. We’re happy that this wedding dress fit into the rented limousine…otherwise, it would have turned disastrous.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-328\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Sassy-Bride-202x300.jpg\" alt=\"sassy-bride\" width=\"335\" height=\"498\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Bridal Gown</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">As you can note from the previous list of our wedding dresses, some brides have taken it to the next level. They end to insist on something unique for their special day really, but this lady took it to the extreme.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-329\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Bridal-Gown-218x300.jpg\" alt=\"bridal-gown\" width=\"331\" height=\"456\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Have Your Special Day Cake and Eat It</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">This bride disagrees with everything.  She went for a tailor-made dress that is also unique and edible. You can imagine the amount of time spent in creating this tasty wedding dress.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-330\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Have-Your-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"have-your\" width=\"393\" height=\"393\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000\"><strong>Crazy Cat Lady</strong></span></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Ever wondered how an animal themed wedding dress will look like, well this lady did exactly that by going for a cat themed tailor-made dress.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-331\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Crazy-Cat-210x300.jpg\" alt=\"crazy-cat\" width=\"326\" height=\"466\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Donut Be Nuts!</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Well, if you think you have seen enough of edible wedding dresses, then the next thing is a bride coming up with something more unique and original. I won’t lie; I would be attempted to take a bite out of her beautifully crafted wedding dress.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-332\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Donut-Be-Nuts-300x236.jpg\" alt=\"donut-be-nuts\" width=\"453\" height=\"356\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Disney Comes to Life</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">This bubblegum pink number executed the Disney idea perfectly. It is one of the unique and original wedding gowns we have seen so far.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-333\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Disney-Comes-188x300.jpg\" alt=\"disney-comes\" width=\"301\" height=\"480\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Cost Cutting</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">One way of cutting your wedding dress costs is to forget the suit and wedding dress entirely and just go with some decorative body art.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-334\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Cost-Cutting-300x260.jpg\" alt=\"cost-cutting\" width=\"416\" height=\"360\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">The Sweetest Bride</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Heard of the expression, “you can have your cake and eat it too”? That is that what this couple is living this quote. After all, it was a special day for them.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-335\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/The-Sweetest-Bride-208x300.jpg\" alt=\"the-sweetest-bride\" width=\"316\" height=\"455\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Double-Click</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Nothing will be romantic than geeking out on your special day. This bride took it to the next level with a tailor-made wedding gown, though it’s made of computer mice and not real mice. That would have turned weird.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-336\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Double-Click-225x300.jpg\" alt=\"double-click\" width=\"327\" height=\"436\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Katniss?</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">It looks like Katniss Everdeen from ‘The Hunger Games’ would have worn for her big day, a beauty made out of sunset shades and flames. Worry no more about grabbing the fire extinguisher, though in this case, you will surely get worried; they are not real flames.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-337\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Katniss-237x300.jpg\" alt=\"katniss\" width=\"323\" height=\"409\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">You’ve Been Tangoed</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Everyone wants to stand out during his/her wedding day. But this bride took it to the next level, don’t you think? She opted for a nice shade of tangerine on her wedding day.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-343\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/You-ve-Been-237x300.jpg\" alt=\"you-ve-been\" width=\"344\" height=\"436\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">White Chocolate Wonder</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Edible and original wedding dresses are coming right up. This one is another luscious wonder, made entirely of white chocolate. Hope it will not be too sunny on the bride’s special day otherwise she might start melting!</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-344\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/White-Chocolate-Wonder-219x300.jpg\" alt=\"white-chocolate-wonder\" width=\"328\" height=\"449\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Customer Wedding Dress</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">If you are thinking of a custom tailor-made dress for your wedding day, you should know that a blue color symbolizes stability, loyalty, and security. So blue is a no go zone!</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-345\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Custom-Wedding-300x300.jpg\" alt=\"custom-wedding\" width=\"389\" height=\"389\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Glittery Wedding Limo Service</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Nothing says “I love you” quite like a dress made up of lots of bright pink hearts with some glitter for added effect. Since this bride looks everything but traditional, we wonder if the rented wedding limo was covered in pink glitter, too.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-348\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Glittery-Wedding-263x300.jpg\" alt=\"glittery-wedding\" width=\"369\" height=\"421\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">No Regular Wedding Dress Rental</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Who doesn’t love a leopard print, don’t get me wrong, though? Let’s us just say this custom pink and leopard print wedding dress is not a normal wedding dress you can get from a regular dress rental store.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-349\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/No-Regular-Wedding-300x249.jpg\" alt=\"no-regular-wedding\" width=\"420\" height=\"348\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Where’s The Dress?</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Just trying to figure out what really going on in this picture. This bride decided to look like a tree. Did you notice the bride? You may need to take a closer look.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-352\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Wheres-The-Dress-239x300.jpg\" alt=\"wheres-the-dress\" width=\"363\" height=\"456\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Neon Bright</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Giving our bridesmaid freedom to choose their dresses for the special day is a nice way to keep everyone happy. Cost can be kept low, and your favorite people get the freedom to choose a dress of their choice. However, you might end up with something colorful as this neon themed dress.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-353\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Neon-Bright-300x200.jpg\" alt=\"neon-bright\" width=\"424\" height=\"282\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Origami Wedding Dress</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">To be honest, it is not the wedding day that is vital – It is the fact that you and your other half will be exchanging vows and promise to commit to each other for the remaining days of your lives. You would love to be with you bride even before picking such a dramatic gown like this.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-354\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Origami-Wedding-200x300.jpg\" alt=\"origami-wedding\" width=\"321\" height=\"482\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">All of The Lights</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Every bride wants to show off on the wedding day. She wants a hammered limousine and extravagant venue. She wants the perfect honeymoon suite in the most amazing seven-star hotel. And more than that, she wants to be perfectly dressed and look beautiful.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-356\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/All-Of-The-Lights-236x300.png\" alt=\"all-of-the-lights\" width=\"355\" height=\"451\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Custom Wedding Dress Or Wigs?</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Consider your special day and think of the “hair” or “wig” that can be right for the occasion. On the centrally the bride decided to get a dress made fully out of human hair at a price of $78,000 is a perfect match for the bride.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-357\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Custom-Wedding-Dress-262x300.jpg\" alt=\"custom-wedding-dress\" width=\"347\" height=\"397\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Go Green</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">What a better way to create a scene that to have a dress made out of recycled materials. Food papers, sweet wrappers, it does not matter but ensures that it is the right color. We love this wedding dress!</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-359\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Go-Green-244x300.jpg\" alt=\"go-green\" width=\"338\" height=\"415\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Balloon Gown</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">This balloon wedding dress is an art. The second piece of art that we have seen, but to be honest, we really love it! Sometime it is good to mix things up and change the style of the wedding dress. And this balloon wedding dress should be the first one on your mind.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-358\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Balloon-Gown-221x300.jpg\" alt=\"balloon-gown\" width=\"363\" height=\"492\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Camo Camp Out</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">This camo-wedding dress is something only Honey Boo Boo’s mamma could go for on her special day. For an avid hunter, this is a perfect match but not for us; we would prefer something more of ivory.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-355\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Camo-Camp-Out-286x300.jpg\" alt=\"camo-camp-out\" width=\"379\" height=\"398\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Toilet Roll Creation</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Well, when you get the right toilet paper, you buy enough to ensure that you never run out of stock shortly, this bride went an extra step and designed a wedding dress from tissue papers. She knows what she loves and hopes she gets a matching pair of shoe.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-351\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Toilet-Roll-Creation-300x261.png\" alt=\"toilet-roll-creation\" width=\"425\" height=\"370\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Terrifically Tentacled</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">Just like “The Little Mermaid” this tentacle-inspired wedding dress is definitely up to our alley. Irrespective of our dislike of seafood, we highly love this wedding dress.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-350\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Terrifically-Tentacled-271x300.jpg\" alt=\"terrifically-tentacled\" width=\"380\" height=\"421\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Bright Like A Diamond</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">The bride chose the custom-made wedding dress for her special day. A good match in case there would be an electricity blackout.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-347\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Bright-Like-A-Diamond-300x232.jpg\" alt=\"bright-like-a-diamond\" width=\"449\" height=\"347\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Double Wedding</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">As a matter of fact, no good can come from having a joint wedding with your best friend, especially when your tastes are this similar. On the contrary, this special day for the couple was brightened by the magenta.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-346\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Double-Wedding-300x213.jpg\" alt=\"double-wedding\" width=\"443\" height=\"315\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Wifey $ Lifey</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">There is nothing that shows your commitment more than having ‘Wifey’ emblazoned across your bottom wedding dress for the special day. At least this bride won’t forget what she’s up to. Turns in a mirror and Oh yes!</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-342\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Wifey-4-Lifey-300x225.jpg\" alt=\"wifey-4-lifey\" width=\"469\" height=\"352\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">The Royal Dress</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">It is clear and self-explanatory – the wedding was “The Royal Wedding” themed. The dress looks amazingly royal to us!</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-341\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/The-Royal-Dress-253x300.jpg\" alt=\"the-royal-dress\" width=\"399\" height=\"474\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Honeymoon Suite Ready</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">In case you had not noticed, the bride chose a dress made out of more than one thousand rubbers. A clear indication of her preparedness once they get to the honeymoon.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-340\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Honeymoon-Suite-234x300.jpg\" alt=\"honeymoon-suite\" width=\"329\" height=\"422\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Peek-A-Bump</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">It is hard work when you try to find a nice looking dress for your special day if you happen to be pregnant. Most brides want to cover their baby bump but not this bride here. She had her custom-made dress created to show off her bump, allowing her baby to watch the ceremony.</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-339\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Peek-A-Bump-240x300.jpg\" alt=\"peek-a-bump\" width=\"342\" height=\"428\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>\r\n<h1><strong><span style=\"color: #000000\">Wedding Limo, Please!</span></strong></h1>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\">It is said that the average wedding in the US costs not less than $20,000. Well, how much of the budget do you think this bride spent on her wedding hummer limo?</span></h2>\r\n<h2><span style=\"color: #000000\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-338\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/Wedding-Limo-300x190.jpg\" alt=\"wedding-limo\" width=\"471\" height=\"298\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h2>','Epic Brides You Can’t Unsee','','inherit','closed','closed','','322-revision-v1','','','2016-12-19 09:58:51','2016-12-19 09:58:51','',322,'http://www.theladypost.com/2016/12/19/322-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(640,2,'2016-12-22 15:47:03','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Auto Draft','','auto-draft','open','open','','','','','2016-12-22 15:47:03','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'http://www.theladypost.com/?p=640',0,'post','',0),(641,2,'2017-01-08 16:30:45','2017-01-08 16:30:45','<h2><strong>$100 Million Eric Clapton Yacht</strong></h2>\r\n<h2>The 157-foot fancy yacht cost the balling Eric Clapton over a staggering $100 million. To match his class, Clapton has a guest entertainment space in his Va Bene yacht as he sails around the Mediterranean at a speed of 14 kn