11\" width=\"551\" height=\"551\" /></h3>\r\n<h3><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Gabrielle Union</h1>\r\n<h3>Gabrielle Union joins this lists\' list of people that were already beautiful, to begin with. She has been gorgeous from the start, but it\'s truly amazing to witness how she just keeps looking better and better as time goes by; by all accounts, she looks even better today than she ever did.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1444\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/24.png\" alt=\"24\" width=\"549\" height=\"439\" /></h3>\r\n<h3><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Nicole Richie</h1>\r\n<h3>Tuning down her troubled lifestyle has certainly helped Nicole Richie with her looks. Her early years were surrounded by controversy and some very brave fashion choices. Nowadays Nicole is just breathtaking, her beauty more balanced, her style more defined than ever before.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1440\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/204.jpg\" alt=\"20\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /></h3>\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<h3><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Blair Underwood</h1>\r\n<h3>Blair Underwood had a very boyish, round look back in his 20\'s. This look always gave away the impression that Blair is actually younger than he really was. Today he is 47 years old and looks simply fantastic – He could certainly pass for a 30-something-year-old.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1441\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/216.jpg\" alt=\"21\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /></h3>\r\n<h3><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Ryan Gosling</h1>\r\n<h3>Ryan Gosling got his major breakthrough in Hollywood when he starred in the 2004 film the notebook. The film\'s director Nick Cassavetes actually chose Gosling for the role because he thought he wasn\'t good looking. Gosling, of course, has gotten better and better looking as time went by and is widely considered to be one of the hottest men in Hollywood today.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1450\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/304.jpg\" alt=\"30\" width=\"550\" height=\"550\" />\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Kate Beckinsale</h1>\r\n<h3>Kate Beckinsale started acting at a very young age. She was a pretty teenager-turned-gorgeous young woman, but as the years go by it seems like she\'s just getting more and more beautiful. Her face has lost its roundness and has a more refined chiseled look nowadays, which aids Kate\'s undeniable elegance.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1446\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/263.jpg\" alt=\"26\" width=\"497\" height=\"497\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Bradley Cooper</h1>\r\n<h3>Bradley Cooper is consistently featured in every respectful magazine\'s list of the best looking men in Hollywood, and with good reason. Now in his early 40\'s, he looks undoubtedly better than he did even a decade before. He has perfected his rough yet stylish look and developed a sense of fashion like no other actor in Hollywood.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1449\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/294.jpg\" alt=\"29\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /></h3>\r\n<h3><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Johnny Depp</h1>\r\n<h3>Johnny Depp is a case very similar to Robert Downey Jr. He\'s one of Hollywood\'s most appreciated and sought-after actors today, and while he was certainly a good looking young man back in his early boyish days, there\'s no denying today\'s Johnny is one of the hottest and sexiest men in the world. He\'s also approaching his mid-50s, mind you. Not that it shows.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1426\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/6.png\" alt=\"6\" width=\"550\" height=\"311\" /></h3>','30 Stars Who Look Better With Age','','inherit','closed','closed','','650-revision-v1','','','2017-01-30 14:34:41','2017-01-30 14:34:41','',650,'http://www.theladypost.com/2017/01/30/650-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(652,2,'2017-01-30 14:35:17','2017-01-30 14:35:17','','featured1','','inherit','open','closed','','featured1','','','2017-01-30 14:35:17','2017-01-30 14:35:17','',650,'http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/featured1.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(653,2,'2017-02-26 19:33:26','2017-02-26 19:33:26','<h2>Celebs tend to date amongst themselves. But sometimes, the choice of their hearts can be quite surprising. Here are 30 celebrity couples that you might be surprised as to how they ended up together.</h2>\r\n<h1>Chris Pratt and Anna Faris</h1>\r\n<h3>Chris Pratt is currently at the height of his career. His films are extremely successful and he seems to be loved by all. Pratt has been married to Anna Farris, of \"Scary Movie\" fame, since 2009.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1149\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/chris-pratt.jpg\" alt=\"chris-pratt\" width=\"550\" height=\"483\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Jennifer Lawrence and Darren Aronofsky</h1>\r\n<h3>One of Hollywood\'s hottest names, Jennifer Lawrence is enjoying incredible success on the big screen – and off it. She is currently dating \"Requiem for a Dream\" director Darren Aronofsky.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1156\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/jen.jpg\" alt=\"jen\" width=\"362\" height=\"496\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Scarlett Johansson and Romain Dauriac</h1>\r\n<h3>Previously married to Ryan Reynolds, the gorgeous actress has been married to French journalist Romain Dauriac since 2014.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1170\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/scarlett-johansson-and-romain-dauriac.jpg\" alt=\"scarlett-johansson-and-romain-dauriac\" width=\"388\" height=\"483\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Dave Franco and Alison Brie</h1>\r\n<h3>Often considered to be even prettier than his older brother James, Dave Franco has been dating beautiful actress Alison Brie since 2012, with the two becoming engaged in 2015.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1152\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/dave-franco.jpg\" alt=\"dave-franco\" width=\"360\" height=\"480\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Emma Watson and William Knight</h1>\r\n<h3>With the Harry Potter saga behind her, Emma Watson has moved on to new and different projects. Meanwhile, she has been dating tech entrepreneur and businessman William \"Mack\" Knight.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1155\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/emma-watson.jpg\" alt=\"emma-watson\" width=\"549\" height=\"384\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>David Cross and Amber Tamblyn</h1>\r\n<h3>Actor, stand-up comedian and director David Cross, of \"Arrested Development\" fame, has been married to actress Amber Tamblyn – who most recently appeared on \"Two and a Half Men\" – since 2012.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1153\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/david-cross.jpg\" alt=\"david-cross\" width=\"551\" height=\"414\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Billie Lourd and Taylor Lautner</h1>\r\n<h3>Billie Lourd is a prime example of true Hollywood royalty: The daughter of the late Carrie Fisher and the granddaughter of the late Debbie Reynolds is currently dating former \"Twilight\" star, Taylor Lautner.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1146\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/billie.jpg\" alt=\"billie\" width=\"551\" height=\"297\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Sophie Turner and Joe Jonas</h1>\r\n<h3>The British star, known to audiences for her ongoing role on \"Game of Thrones\", has been dating \"DNCE\" lead man and former \"Jonas Brothers\" singer Joe Jonas.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1172\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/sophie.jpg\" alt=\"sophie\" width=\"298\" height=\"481\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Marcus Mumford and Carey Mulligan</h1>\r\n<h3>The \"Mumford and Sons\" lead singer broke into the limelight in 2012 with his band\'s Grammy Award winning album \"Babel\". He and his BAFTA award-winning wife Carey Mulligan have actually been childhood pen pals.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1166\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/mumford.jpg\" alt=\"mumford\" width=\"480\" height=\"430\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Maya Rudolph and Paul Thomas Anderson</h1>\r\n<h3>Comedian and former SNL cast member Maya Rudolph has been in a relationship with respected film director and screenwriter Paul Thomas Anderson since 2001. They have three children together.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1164\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/maya-rudolph.jpg\" alt=\"maya-rudolph\" width=\"359\" height=\"479\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Jeffrey Dean Morgan and Hilarie Burton</h1>\r\n<h3>The versatile actor, currently appearing on TV screens all over the world on \"The Walking Dead\" as the menacing Negan, has been together with former \"One Tree Hill\" star Hilarie Burton since 2009.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1167\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/negan.jpg\" alt=\"negan\" width=\"551\" height=\"414\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Jesse Eisenberg and Anna Strout</h1>\r\n<h3>The \"Social Network\" and \"Now You See Me\" star has been dating Anna Strout since 2002, with the couple experiencing a short breakup between 2013 and 2015. They are currently expecting their first child together.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1158\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/jesse.jpg\" alt=\"jesse\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Kate Mara and Jamie Bell</h1>\r\n<h3>After making her breakthrough on \"House of Cards\", Kate Mara went on to appear on the critically panned \"Fantastic Four\", where she met actor Jamie Bell. The two started dating in 2015 and got married in January 2017.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1159\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/kate-mara.jpg\" alt=\"kate-mara\" width=\"550\" height=\"429\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Chris Evans and Jenny Slate</h1>\r\n<h3>The \"Captain America\" star, who has enjoyed incredible success in recent years, began dating the former Saturday Night Live actress in early 2016.</h3>\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-1148\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/chris-evans.jpg\" alt=\"Mandatory Credit: Photo by Dave Allocca/Starpix/REX/Shutterstock (5736897aa) Jenny Slate, Chris Evans Universal Pictures and Illumination Entertainment Present The Premiere of \'The Secret Life of Pets\', New York, USA - 25 Jun 2016\" width=\"333\" height=\"500\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Daniel Radcliff and Erin Darke</h1>\r\n<h3>The child star, recognized by most people all over the world as Harry Potter, has been dating American actress Erin Darke since meeting her on the set of \"Kill Your Darlings\".</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1151\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/dan.jpg\" alt=\"dan\" width=\"549\" height=\"409\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Sofia Vergara and Joe Manganiello</h1>\r\n<h3>Named as the highest paid actress in television in 2016 by Forbes, Sofia Vergara has been married to \"True Blood\" star Joe Manganiello since November 2015.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1171\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/sofia.jpg\" alt=\"sofia\" width=\"309\" height=\"499\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Jennifer Aniston and Justin Theroux</h1>\r\n<h3>It took her some time to get over the over-publicized breakup from Brad Pitt, but Jennifer Aniston has finally found her soulmate in \"Mulholland Drive\" and \"Inland Empire\" actor Justin Theroux. The couple has been married since 2015.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1157\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/jennifer-aniston1-a.jpg\" alt=\"jennifer-aniston1-a\" width=\"352\" height=\"479\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Kit Harington and Rose Leslie</h1>\r\n<h3>Known to all as Jon Snow from the hit TV series \"Game of Thrones\", British actor Kit Harrington is actually dating his former co-star Rose Leslie, who played Ygritte on the show. They have been together since 2012.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1161\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/kit.jpg\" alt=\"kit\" width=\"551\" height=\"367\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Anna Kendrick and Ben Richardson</h1>\r\n<h3>Previously attached to some big names as Jake Gyllenhaal and Edgar Wright, the \"Pitch Perfect\" and \"Up in the Air\" actress has been seeing cinematographer Ben Richardson since 2014.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1145\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/anna-kendrick.jpg\" alt=\"anna-kendrick\" width=\"297\" height=\"480\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Leonardo DiCaprio and Nina Agdal</h1>\r\n<h3>Finally winning the Academy Award for best actor he worked so hard for, Leonardo DiCaprio has been with a fair share of girlfriends over his career. His latest girlfriend is Danish model Nina Agdal, with whom he has been dating since May 2016.</h3>\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-1162\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/leo.jpg\" alt=\"*PREMIUM EXCLUSIVE* New York, NY - Leonardo DiCaprio and Nina Agdal are spotted after dinner with a friend. The couple looks smitten and in love as they cuddle up while walking in the Big Apple. Leo and Nina keep it casual as they grab a smoke outside the restaurant. The actor is seen holding hands with the supermodel while talking to a friend. **Shot on August 18, 2016* AKM-GSI August 21, 2016 To License These Photos, Please Contact : Maria Buda (917) 242-1505 mbuda@akmgsi.com sales@akmgsi.com or Mark Satter (317) 691-9592 msatter@akmgsi.com sales@akmgsi.com www.akmgsi.com\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Bradley Cooper and Irina Shayk</h1>\r\n<h3>Widely and consistently considered to be one of Hollywood\'s hottest men, Bradley Cooper is currently dating Russian supermodel Irina Shayk. They have been together since early 2015.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1147\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/bradley.jpg\" alt=\"bradley\" width=\"550\" height=\"309\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Ed Sheeran and Cherry Seaborn</h1>\r\n<h3>English folk singer Ed Sheeran gained respectable fame over the past few years, releasing a number of critically acclaimed records. He first met his girlfriend Cherry Seaborn in high school, and the two started dating in 2016.</h3>\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-1154\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/ed.jpeg\" alt=\"Singer Ed Sheeran again out with his mystery lady this time at the Philadelphia Phillies Vs New York Mets at Citi Field on September 2, 2015 in the Flushing neighborhood of the Queens borough of New York City. Pictured: Ed Sheeran Ref: SPL1115780 030915 Picture by: Splash News Splash News and Pictures Los Angeles: 310-821-2666 New York: 212-619-2666 London: 870-934-2666 photodesk@splashnews.com \" width=\"551\" height=\"342\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Margot Robbie and Tom Ackerley</h1>\r\n<h3>Young Australian actress Margot Robbie has found notable success in recent years, appearing in blockbusters such as \"The Wolf of Wall Street\" and \"Suicide Squad\". The gorgeous Robbie and British assistant director Tom Ackerley tied the knot in December 2016.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1163\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/margot.jpg\" alt=\"margot\" width=\"550\" height=\"329\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Chris Hemsworth and Elsa Pataky</h1>\r\n<h3>The \"Thor\" actor has been married to Spanish model and actress Elsa Pataky since 2010. The couple are still going strong, and they have three children together.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1173\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/thor.jpg\" alt=\"thor\" width=\"407\" height=\"480\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Tom Hardy and Charlotte Riley</h1>\r\n<h3>Rising star and British heartthrob Tom Hardy and actress Charlotte Riley have been together since meeting on the set of the 2009 TV film \"Wuthering Heights\". They have been married since 2014.</h3>\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-1174\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/tom-hardy.jpg\" alt=\"LONDON, ENGLAND - SEPTEMBER 03: Tom Hardy and Charlotte Riley attend the UK Premiere of &quot;Legend&quot; at Odeon Leicester Square on September 3, 2015 in London, England. (Photo by John Phillips/Getty Images)\" width=\"328\" height=\"480\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Michael Fassbender and Alicia Vikander</h1>\r\n<h3>The Irish-German esteemed actor Michael Fassbender first met Swedish actress Alicia Vikander on the set of the film \"The Light Between Oceans\" in 2014, and the two have been together ever since.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1165\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/michael-fassbender.jpg\" alt=\"michael-fassbender\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Cobie Smulders and Taran Killam</h1>\r\n<h3>Canadian actress Cobie Smulders, of \"How I Met Your Mother\" fame, has been married to comedian and SNL cast member Taran Killam since 2012. Smulders and Killam have two daughters together.</h3>\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-1150\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/cobie.jpg\" alt=\"13 Mar 2014 --- Hollywood, CA - March 13: Cobie Smulders, Taran Killam Attending &quot;Captain America: The Winter Soldier&quot; - Los Angeles Premiere Held at El Capitan Theatre California on March 13, 2014. Photo Credit: Faye Sadou / UPA . --- Image by © Faye Sadou / UPA ./Retna Ltd./Corbis\" width=\"329\" height=\"480\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Sacha Baron Cohen and Isla Fischer</h1>\r\n<h3>Comical mastermind Sacha Baron Cohen and his wife, Australian actress Isla Fischer, have been married since 2010. They have three children together: two daughters and a son.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1169\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/sacha.jpg\" alt=\"sacha\" width=\"549\" height=\"412\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Jason Sudeikis and Olivia Wilde</h1>\r\n<h3>A true Hollywood power couple, versatile comedy actor Jason Sudeikis and the former \"House M.D.\" Star Olivia Wilde have been engaged since 2013. The have two children together – a son and a daughter.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1168\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/olivia.jpg\" alt=\"olivia\" width=\"550\" height=\"344\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Katy Perry and Orlando Bloom</h1>\r\n<h3>Katy Perry was previously famously married to controversial comedian and actor Russell Brand. She is currently dating English versatile actor Orlando Bloom, of \"The Lord of the Rings\" and \"The Pirates of the Caribbean\" fame.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1160\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/katy.jpg\" alt=\"katy\" width=\"549\" height=\"288\" />','30 Surprising Celebrity Couples','','publish','open','open','','30-surprising-celebrity-couples','','','2017-02-26 19:33:26','2017-02-26 19:33:26','',0,'http://www.theladypost.com/?p=653',0,'post','',0),(654,2,'2017-01-30 14:41:58','2017-01-30 14:41:58','','margot','','inherit','open','closed','','margot','','','2017-01-30 14:41:58','2017-01-30 14:41:58','',653,'http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/margot.jpg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),(655,2,'2017-01-30 14:42:10','2017-01-30 14:42:10','<h2>Celebs tend to date amongst themselves. But sometimes, the choice of their hearts can be quite surprising. Here are 30 celebrity couples that you might be surprised as to how they ended up together.</h2>\r\n<h1>Chris Pratt and Anna Faris</h1>\r\n<h3>Chris Pratt is currently at the height of his career. His films are extremely successful and he seems to be loved by all. Pratt has been married to Anna Farris, of \"Scary Movie\" fame, since 2009.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1149\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/chris-pratt.jpg\" alt=\"chris-pratt\" width=\"550\" height=\"483\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Jennifer Lawrence and Darren Aronofsky</h1>\r\n<h3>One of Hollywood\'s hottest names, Jennifer Lawrence is enjoying incredible success on the big screen – and off it. She is currently dating \"Requiem for a Dream\" director Darren Aronofsky.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1156\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/jen.jpg\" alt=\"jen\" width=\"362\" height=\"496\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Scarlett Johansson and Romain Dauriac</h1>\r\n<h3>Previously married to Ryan Reynolds, the gorgeous actress has been married to French journalist Romain Dauriac since 2014.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1170\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/scarlett-johansson-and-romain-dauriac.jpg\" alt=\"scarlett-johansson-and-romain-dauriac\" width=\"388\" height=\"483\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Dave Franco and Alison Brie</h1>\r\n<h3>Often considered to be even prettier than his older brother James, Dave Franco has been dating beautiful actress Alison Brie since 2012, with the two becoming engaged in 2015.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1152\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/dave-franco.jpg\" alt=\"dave-franco\" width=\"360\" height=\"480\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Emma Watson and William Knight</h1>\r\n<h3>With the Harry Potter saga behind her, Emma Watson has moved on to new and different projects. Meanwhile, she has been dating tech entrepreneur and businessman William \"Mack\" Knight.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1155\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/emma-watson.jpg\" alt=\"emma-watson\" width=\"549\" height=\"384\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>David Cross and Amber Tamblyn</h1>\r\n<h3>Actor, stand-up comedian and director David Cross, of \"Arrested Development\" fame, has been married to actress Amber Tamblyn – who most recently appeared on \"Two and a Half Men\" – since 2012.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1153\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/david-cross.jpg\" alt=\"david-cross\" width=\"551\" height=\"414\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Billie Lourd and Taylor Lautner</h1>\r\n<h3>Billie Lourd is a prime example of true Hollywood royalty: The daughter of the late Carrie Fisher and the granddaughter of the late Debbie Reynolds is currently dating former \"Twilight\" star, Taylor Lautner.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1146\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/billie.jpg\" alt=\"billie\" width=\"551\" height=\"297\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Sophie Turner and Joe Jonas</h1>\r\n<h3>The British star, known to audiences for her ongoing role on \"Game of Thrones\", has been dating \"DNCE\" lead man and former \"Jonas Brothers\" singer Joe Jonas.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1172\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/sophie.jpg\" alt=\"sophie\" width=\"298\" height=\"481\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Marcus Mumford and Carey Mulligan</h1>\r\n<h3>The \"Mumford and Sons\" lead singer broke into the limelight in 2012 with his band\'s Grammy Award winning album \"Babel\". He and his BAFTA award-winning wife Carey Mulligan have actually been childhood pen pals.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1166\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/mumford.jpg\" alt=\"mumford\" width=\"480\" height=\"430\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Maya Rudolph and Paul Thomas Anderson</h1>\r\n<h3>Comedian and former SNL cast member Maya Rudolph has been in a relationship with respected film director and screenwriter Paul Thomas Anderson since 2001. They have three children together.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1164\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/maya-rudolph.jpg\" alt=\"maya-rudolph\" width=\"359\" height=\"479\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Jeffrey Dean Morgan and Hilarie Burton</h1>\r\n<h3>The versatile actor, currently appearing on TV screens all over the world on \"The Walking Dead\" as the menacing Negan, has been together with former \"One Tree Hill\" star Hilarie Burton since 2009.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1167\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/negan.jpg\" alt=\"negan\" width=\"551\" height=\"414\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Jesse Eisenberg and Anna Strout</h1>\r\n<h3>The \"Social Network\" and \"Now You See Me\" star has been dating Anna Strout since 2002, with the couple experiencing a short breakup between 2013 and 2015. They are currently expecting their first child together.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1158\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/jesse.jpg\" alt=\"jesse\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Kate Mara and Jamie Bell</h1>\r\n<h3>After making her breakthrough on \"House of Cards\", Kate Mara went on to appear on the critically panned \"Fantastic Four\", where she met actor Jamie Bell. The two started dating in 2015 and got married in January 2017.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1159\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/kate-mara.jpg\" alt=\"kate-mara\" width=\"550\" height=\"429\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Chris Evans and Jenny Slate</h1>\r\n<h3>The \"Captain America\" star, who has enjoyed incredible success in recent years, began dating the former Saturday Night Live actress in early 2016.</h3>\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-1148\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/chris-evans.jpg\" alt=\"Mandatory Credit: Photo by Dave Allocca/Starpix/REX/Shutterstock (5736897aa) Jenny Slate, Chris Evans Universal Pictures and Illumination Entertainment Present The Premiere of \'The Secret Life of Pets\', New York, USA - 25 Jun 2016\" width=\"333\" height=\"500\" /><!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Daniel Radcliff and Erin Darke</h1>\r\n<h3>The child star, recognized by most people all over the world as Harry Potter, has been dating American actress Erin Darke since meeting her on the set of \"Kill Your Darlings\".</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1151\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/dan.jpg\" alt=\"dan\" width=\"549\" height=\"409\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Sofia Vergara and Joe Manganiello</h1>\r\n<h3>Named as the highest paid actress in television in 2016 by Forbes, Sofia Vergara has been married to \"True Blood\" star Joe Manganiello since November 2015.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1171\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/sofia.jpg\" alt=\"sofia\" width=\"309\" height=\"499\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Jennifer Aniston and Justin Theroux</h1>\r\n<h3>It took her some time to get over the over-publicized breakup from Brad Pitt, but Jennifer Aniston has finally found her soulmate in \"Mulholland Drive\" and \"Inland Empire\" actor Justin Theroux. The couple has been married since 2015.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1157\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/jennifer-aniston1-a.jpg\" alt=\"jennifer-aniston1-a\" width=\"352\" height=\"479\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Kit Harington and Rose Leslie</h1>\r\n<h3>Known to all as Jon Snow from the hit TV series \"Game of Thrones\", British actor Kit Harrington is actually dating his former co-star Rose Leslie, who played Ygritte on the show. They have been together since 2012.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1161\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/kit.jpg\" alt=\"kit\" width=\"551\" height=\"367\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Anna Kendrick and Ben Richardson</h1>\r\n<h3>Previously attached to some big names as Jake Gyllenhaal and Edgar Wright, the \"Pitch Perfect\" and \"Up in the Air\" actress has been seeing cinematographer Ben Richardson since 2014.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1145\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/anna-kendrick.jpg\" alt=\"anna-kendrick\" width=\"297\" height=\"480\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Leonardo DiCaprio and Nina Agdal</h1>\r\n<h3>Finally winning the Academy Award for best actor he worked so hard for, Leonardo DiCaprio has been with a fair share of girlfriends over his career. His latest girlfriend is Danish model Nina Agdal, with whom he has been dating since May 2016.</h3>\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-1162\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/leo.jpg\" alt=\"*PREMIUM EXCLUSIVE* New York, NY - Leonardo DiCaprio and Nina Agdal are spotted after dinner with a friend. The couple looks smitten and in love as they cuddle up while walking in the Big Apple. Leo and Nina keep it casual as they grab a smoke outside the restaurant. The actor is seen holding hands with the supermodel while talking to a friend. **Shot on August 18, 2016* AKM-GSI August 21, 2016 To License These Photos, Please Contact : Maria Buda (917) 242-1505 mbuda@akmgsi.com sales@akmgsi.com or Mark Satter (317) 691-9592 msatter@akmgsi.com sales@akmgsi.com www.akmgsi.com\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Bradley Cooper and Irina Shayk</h1>\r\n<h3>Widely and consistently considered to be one of Hollywood\'s hottest men, Bradley Cooper is currently dating Russian supermodel Irina Shayk. They have been together since early 2015.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1147\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/bradley.jpg\" alt=\"bradley\" width=\"550\" height=\"309\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Ed Sheeran and Cherry Seaborn</h1>\r\n<h3>English folk singer Ed Sheeran gained respectable fame over the past few years, releasing a number of critically acclaimed records. He first met his girlfriend Cherry Seaborn in high school, and the two started dating in 2016.</h3>\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-1154\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/ed.jpeg\" alt=\"Singer Ed Sheeran again out with his mystery lady this time at the Philadelphia Phillies Vs New York Mets at Citi Field on September 2, 2015 in the Flushing neighborhood of the Queens borough of New York City. Pictured: Ed Sheeran Ref: SPL1115780 030915 Picture by: Splash News Splash News and Pictures Los Angeles: 310-821-2666 New York: 212-619-2666 London: 870-934-2666 photodesk@splashnews.com \" width=\"551\" height=\"342\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Margot Robbie and Tom Ackerley</h1>\r\n<h3>Young Australian actress Margot Robbie has found notable success in recent years, appearing in blockbusters such as \"The Wolf of Wall Street\" and \"Suicide Squad\". The gorgeous Robbie and British assistant director Tom Ackerley tied the knot in December 2016.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1163\" src=\"http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/margot.jpg\" alt=\"margot\" width=\"550\" height=\"329\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Chris Hemsworth and Elsa Pataky</h1>\r\n<h3>The \"Thor\" actor has been married to Spanish model and actress Elsa Pataky since 2010. The couple are still going strong, and they have three children together.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1173\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/thor.jpg\" alt=\"thor\" width=\"407\" height=\"480\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Tom Hardy and Charlotte Riley</h1>\r\n<h3>Rising star and British heartthrob Tom Hardy and actress Charlotte Riley have been together since meeting on the set of the 2009 TV film \"Wuthering Heights\". They have been married since 2014.</h3>\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-1174\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/tom-hardy.jpg\" alt=\"LONDON, ENGLAND - SEPTEMBER 03: Tom Hardy and Charlotte Riley attend the UK Premiere of &quot;Legend&quot; at Odeon Leicester Square on September 3, 2015 in London, England. (Photo by John Phillips/Getty Images)\" width=\"328\" height=\"480\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Michael Fassbender and Alicia Vikander</h1>\r\n<h3>The Irish-German esteemed actor Michael Fassbender first met Swedish actress Alicia Vikander on the set of the film \"The Light Between Oceans\" in 2014, and the two have been together ever since.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1165\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/michael-fassbender.jpg\" alt=\"michael-fassbender\" width=\"550\" height=\"366\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Cobie Smulders and Taran Killam</h1>\r\n<h3>Canadian actress Cobie Smulders, of \"How I Met Your Mother\" fame, has been married to comedian and SNL cast member Taran Killam since 2012. Smulders and Killam have two daughters together.</h3>\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-1150\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/cobie.jpg\" alt=\"13 Mar 2014 --- Hollywood, CA - March 13: Cobie Smulders, Taran Killam Attending &quot;Captain America: The Winter Soldier&quot; - Los Angeles Premiere Held at El Capitan Theatre California on March 13, 2014. Photo Credit: Faye Sadou / UPA . --- Image by © Faye Sadou / UPA ./Retna Ltd./Corbis\" width=\"329\" height=\"480\" />\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Sacha Baron Cohen and Isla Fischer</h1>\r\n<h3>Comical mastermind Sacha Baron Cohen and his wife, Australian actress Isla Fischer, have been married since 2010. They have three children together: two daughters and a son.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1169\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/sacha.jpg\" alt=\"sacha\" width=\"549\" height=\"412\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Jason Sudeikis and Olivia Wilde</h1>\r\n<h3>A true Hollywood power couple, versatile comedy actor Jason Sudeikis and the former \"House M.D.\" Star Olivia Wilde have been engaged since 2013. The have two children together – a son and a daughter.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1168\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/olivia.jpg\" alt=\"olivia\" width=\"550\" height=\"344\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Katy Perry and Orlando Bloom</h1>\r\n<h3>Katy Perry was previously famously married to controversial comedian and actor Russell Brand. She is currently dating English versatile actor Orlando Bloom, of \"The Lord of the Rings\" and \"The Pirates of the Caribbean\" fame.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1160\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/katy.jpg\" alt=\"katy\" width=\"549\" height=\"288\" />','30 Surprising Celebrity Couples','','inherit','closed','closed','','653-revision-v1','','','2017-01-30 14:42:10','2017-01-30 14:42:10','',653,'http://www.theladypost.com/2017/01/30/653-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(656,2,'2017-02-26 19:32:31','2017-02-26 19:32:31','<h1><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">We all love pets, and celebrities are no different. Whether they show them to the world or not, these celebs have the cutest pets you can find.</span></h1>\r\n<h1>Taylor Swift and Her Cats</h1>\r\n<h3>Taylor Swift, besides being a pop sensation, is a known cat enthusiast. Her cats are named Dr. Meredith Grey and Detective Olivia Benson. Both cats have flourishing Instagram accounts.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1199\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Taylor.png\" alt=\"taylor\" width=\"480\" height=\"475\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Jennifer Lawrence and Pippi</h1>\r\n<h3>Jennifer Lawrence can\'t seem to do anything wrong, as the young talented actress enjoys incredible success over the past few years. She has a cute puppy called Pippi Lawrence who is very close to her heart.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1187\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/jen1.jpg\" alt=\"jen\" width=\"549\" height=\"549\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Cara Delevigne and Cecil The Bunny</h1>\r\n<h3>Cara Delevigne is a very successful young actor and model, but her bunny Cecil is successful in his own right. Cecil has a Twitter account as well as an Instagram account with thousands of followers on each one.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1206\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/cara.png\" alt=\"cara\" width=\"480\" height=\"480\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Miley Cyrus\' Cats and Dogs</h1>\r\n<h3>Miley Cyrus is a wonderful pet owner. She has been known to adopt many pets – dogs, cats, rabbits and even a pig, once. Her current pet resume includes 6 dogs and 3 cats (that we know of).</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1193\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/miley.png\" alt=\"miley\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Ariana Grande and Sirius Black</h1>\r\n<h3>Ariana Grande is apparently a Harry Potter fan, as she named her newest puppy Sirius Black, after a character in the Harry Potter series.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1183\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/grande-black.jpg\" alt=\"grande-black\" width=\"538\" height=\"538\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Orlando Bloom and Sidi</h1>\r\n<h3>The other half of the Perry-Bloom couple, Orlando Bloom is known for his affection for dogs. He has a rescue Saluki mix named Sidi, of whom he takes great care.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1196\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/orlando-bloom.jpg\" alt=\"orlando-bloom\" width=\"550\" height=\"447\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Justin Bieber and Esther</h1>\r\n<h3>Justin Bieber, the teen pop sensation and heartthrob, has a cute puppy named Esther Bieber. He also owns another pup named Phil.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1204\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Bieber.jpg\" alt=\"bieber\" width=\"520\" height=\"515\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Iggy Azalea</h1>\r\n<h3>Iggy Azalea has been in the spotlight for the past few years, releasing some hit singles. She owns a French bulldog who goes by the very long name of Shrinkabull Jam Don\'t Shake Like That Jelli Azalea.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1185\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/iggy.jpg\" alt=\"iggy\" width=\"359\" height=\"479\" /></h3>\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Liam Hemsworth and Dora</h1>\r\n<h3>Known for his role in \"The Hunger Games\" trilogy, Liam Hemsworth is a known dog lover, and has adopted a pet dog called Dora.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1192\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/liam-hem.jpg\" alt=\"liam-hem\" width=\"388\" height=\"479\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Emmy Rossum and Cinnamon</h1>\r\n<h3>Emmy Rossum of the TV series \"Shameless\" has a cute puppy named Cinnamon. She shares pictures of Cinnamon and her frequently on Instagram.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1182\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/emmy-rossum.jpg\" alt=\"emmy-rossum\" width=\"550\" height=\"550\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Ariana Grande and Toulouse</h1>\r\n<h3>Before adopting Sirius Black, Grande has adopted Toulouse from an animal shelter. Toulouse has since modeled for Coach.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1184\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/grande-toulouse.jpg\" alt=\"grande-toulouse\" width=\"540\" height=\"540\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Paris Hilton and Peter Pan</h1>\r\n<h3>Paris Hilton\'s pets were always famous, and she is known to keep them by her side at all times. Her most famous current pooch, the Chihuahua Peter Pan Hilton, has over 39 thousand followers on Instagram.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1197\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/paris.jpg\" alt=\"paris\" width=\"353\" height=\"480\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Demi Lovato\'s Buddy</h1>\r\n<h3>Demi Lovato\'s pup named Buddy has his own Twitter following, with over 61 thousand followers on his account.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1180\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/demi.jpg\" alt=\"demi\" width=\"297\" height=\"480\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Nikki Reed and Ian Somerhalder\'s dogs</h1>\r\n<h3>The successful couple owns two dogs, and they make sure to post as many pictures of them on Instagram as they can. The dogs are named Enzo Reed and Nietzsche Somerhalder.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1209\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/nikki-reed1.jpg\" alt=\"nikki-reed\" width=\"548\" height=\"517\