ophia.png\" alt=\"annasophia\" width=\"549\" height=\"550\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Katy Perry and Kitty Purry</h1>\r\n<h3>Katy Perry is an avid cat lover and has gone on record announcing it on various occasions. Her most famous cat is Kitty Purry, who made a cameo in Perry\'s \"I Kissed a Girl\" video.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1189\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Katy_perry_and_kitty_purry.jpg\" alt=\"katy_perry_and_kitty_purry\" width=\"472\" height=\"461\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Jessica Chastain and Chaplin</h1>\r\n<h3>Jessica Chaplain sure has a kind heart. She has adopted a three-legged pooch named Chaplin. The two appeared together on the TV show \"The View\".</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1188\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/jessica.jpg\" alt=\"jessica\" width=\"550\" height=\"540\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Kaley Cuoco and Ruby</h1>\r\n<h3>Kaley Cuoco is known for playing the character of Penny in \"The Big Bang Theory\". She also owns a cute little pup she has adopted from an animal shelter, named Ruby.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1205\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/caley.jpg\" alt=\"caley\" width=\"551\" height=\"367\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Diana Agron and Freddie</h1>\r\n<h3>The former \"Glee\" star also owns a cute French bulldog, who she named Freddie. She regularly posts pictures of Freddie on Instagram.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1200\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/agron.jpg\" alt=\"agron\" width=\"549\" height=\"548\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Chloe Grace Moretz and Missy</h1>\r\n<h3>Chloe Grace Moretz is a dog enthusiast, and currently owns two dogs, one of which she named Missy. She even took Missy with her to the set of her film \"Carrie\".</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1208\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/chloe.jpg\" alt=\"chloe\" width=\"351\" height=\"501\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Chelsea Handler</h1>\r\n<h3>American actress, television host and producer Chelsea Handler has a cute pup named Tammy.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1207\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/chelsea.jpeg\" alt=\"chelsea\" width=\"377\" height=\"502\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Lena Dunham and Lamby</h1>\r\n<h3>Lena Dunham gained fame for writing and starring in the hit TV show \"Girls\". She has a dog named Lamby whom she takes with her everywhere.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1191\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/lena.jpg\" alt=\"lena\" width=\"550\" height=\"550\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Ed Sheeran and Graham</h1>\r\n<h3>Ed Sheeran is known for writing and singing heartfelt songs. The English singer has a big heart himself, and he has adopted a cute little kitten who goes by the name of Graham.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1181\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Ed-sheeran.jpg\" alt=\"ed-sheeran\" width=\"541\" height=\"541\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Ariel Winter and Chloe</h1>\r\n<h3>Ariel Winter of \"Modern Family\" fame has recently adopted a beautiful German Shepard and named her Chloe. Besides Chloe, Winter has 2 other dogs.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1203\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/ariel.jpg\" alt=\"ariel\" width=\"539\" height=\"540\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Jake Gyllenhaal and Atticus</h1>\r\n<h3>Jake Gyllenhaal is a respected and versatile American actor, known for his Academy Award-nominated performance in \"Brokeback Mountain\". He has a beloved dog named Atticus.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1186\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Jake.jpg\" alt=\"jake\" width=\"368\" height=\"502\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Chrissy Teigen and Pippa</h1>\r\n<h3>Chrissy Teigen and her husband, singer-songwriter John Legend, own a handful of dogs. One of which is the cute Pippa, who is a French bulldog.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1179\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/chrissy.jpg\" alt=\"chrissy\" width=\"550\" height=\"550\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Sarah Hyland and Barkley</h1>\r\n<h3>Another \"Modern Family\" star who is a famous pet owner is Sarah Hyland who plays the role of Haley on the show. She owns a cute puppy called Barkley whom she trained all on her own.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1198\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Sarah-Hyland-1.jpg\" alt=\"sarah-hyland-1\" width=\"351\" height=\"501\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Miranda Kerr and Frankie</h1>\r\n<h3>Miranda Kerr is an international supermodel. When she has some time off from modeling, though, she enjoys cuddling with her cute puppy Frankie.</h3>\r\n<img class=\" wp-image-1194\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Miranda-Kerrr.jpg\" alt=\"Australian model Miranda Kerr looking beautiful in blue as she poses with her pet dog while on the set of a commercial in Santa Monica, Ca Pictured: Miranda Kerr Ref: SPL943776 050215 Picture by: London Entertainment /Splash Splash News and Pictures Los Angeles: 310-821-2666 New York: 212-619-2666 London: 870-934-2666 photodesk@splashnews.com \" width=\"404\" height=\"499\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Lady Gaga and Miss Asia Kinney</h1>\r\n<h3>Famous and successful singer and performer Lady Gaga has a black French Bulldog named Miss Asia Kinney. Miss Kinney is a pet model and has also appeared on television.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1190\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/lady-gaga1.jpg\" alt=\"lady-gaga\" width=\"519\" height=\"518\" />','30 Celebrities And Their Cute Pets','','inherit','closed','closed','','656-revision-v1','','','2017-01-30 14:48:09','2017-01-30 14:48:09','',656,'http://www.theladypost.com/2017/01/30/656-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(659,2,'2017-03-09 14:19:42','2017-03-09 14:19:42','<h2>Celebrity couples are nothing new – stars have been known to date amongst themselves for decades. But the nature of the glamor of Hollywood makes it difficult to sustain relationships for long times, as evidenced time and time again with some of Hollywood\'s most iconic couples splitting up. Where did the wives of those Hollywood stars end up after their relationships ended? Which of those memorable couples are still together to this day?</h2>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">John Travolta &amp; Kelly Preston – Then</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">John Travolta met Kelly Preston on the set of the film \"The Experts\" in which they were both starring. Kelly was in a relationship with Charlie Sheen, but the two broke up and she married Travolta in 1991. The two had two separate weddings – one legal ceremonial wedding and one wedding in accordance with the rules of Scientology.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2995\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/33.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"345\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">John Travolta &amp; Kelly Preston – Now</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Travolta and Preston are still married today, and had three children together, although one of their children, Jett, has sadly passed away at the age of 16.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2996\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/34.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"434\" /></span>\r\n<h1></h1>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Elvis Presley &amp; Priscilla Presley - Then</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Priscilla Presley was only 14 when Elvis and she met for the first time. Regardless of her young age, Elvis and Priscilla dated for seven years before tying the knot in 1967. The couple had one daughter together, Lisa Marie.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\" wp-image-2965\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"550\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Elvis Presley &amp; Priscilla Presley - Now</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Elvis, as we all know, tragically died in 1977. By the time of his death, the two were divorced for a couple of years, mainly due to Elvis\' drug habit. Priscilla remained in the limelight, although not as much as she had been before.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2966\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Sylvester Stallone &amp; Brigitte Nielson - Then</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Stallone is known worldwide as the face of both Rocky Balboa and Rambo and is considered a legend in Hollywood. He married actress-model Brigitte Nielson in 1985.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\" wp-image-3003\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/41.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"367\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Sylvester Stallone &amp; Brigitte Nielson - Now</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Unfortunately, the marriage didn\'t last long at all, and the two separated after just two years as husband and wife.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3004\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/42.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span>\r\n<h1></h1>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Anthony Hopkins &amp; Jennifer Leyton - Then</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Anthony Hopkins is a true Hollywood giant. He married Jennifer Leyton in 1973, after being briefly married before to Petronella Barker.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2969\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/7.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"338\" height=\"500\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Anthony Hopkins &amp; Jennifer Leyton - Now</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Hopkins and Leyton remained together for almost 30 years until thy separated in 2002. Hopkins has remarried since, to Stella Arroyave.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2970\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/8.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"326\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Harrison Ford &amp; Calista Flockhart – Then</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Harrison was already one of Hollywood\'s biggest stars when Calista made her breakthrough. The two met at the 2002 Golden Globe Awards and dated for years before getting married in 2010.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3049\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/87.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"548\" height=\"443\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Harrison Ford &amp; Calista Flockhart – Now</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Harrison Ford is still going strong with his acting. He famously appeared reprised his role as Han Solo in \"Star Wars: The Force Awakens\" and is scheduled to reprise his role in the \"Blade Runner\" sequel as well. Ford and Flockhart are still </span>married,<span style=\"color: #000000;\"> and make sure to appear together everywhere they go.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3050\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/88.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"409\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Sean Connery &amp; Micheline Roquebrune - Then</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Sean Connery is, without a doubt, one of the most respected and valued actors of all time, most prominently remembered for portraying James Bond. He married Morrocan-French painter Micheline Roquebrune in 1975.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2971\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/9.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"330\" height=\"490\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Sean Connery &amp; Micheline Roquebrune - Now</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Sean and Micheline are still happily married today after all those years, and maintain a healthy and admirable family life with their grandchildren.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\" wp-image-2972\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/10.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"333\" height=\"490\" /><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Clint Eastwood &amp; Maggie Johnson - Then</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">One of the most beautiful men of his time, and undoubtedly one of the most talented, Clint Eastwood was sought after by countless women. He married Maggie Johnson in 1958, but their marriage turned out to be a difficult one.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\" wp-image-2963\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"505\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Clint Eastwood &amp; Maggie Johnson - Now</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">The couple managed to stay together for 31 years before ending the marriage. During this time the couple had two children together, although Eastwood had fathered another child from a different woman while he was still married to Johnson.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2964\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Sean Penn &amp; Madonna – Then</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Sean Penn and Madonna were a real power couple during their four years of marriage, from 1985 to 1989. The two stars couldn’t keep their marriage intact for any longer and ended their marriage with a bang.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2973\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/11.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"412\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Sean Penn &amp; Madonna – Now</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">The two went on to have even bigger careers than anyone would have imagined back then. They both got remarried – Sean to Robin Wright and Madonna to Guy Ritchie – and both re-divorced only recently.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2974\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/12.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"445\" /><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Dustin Hoffman &amp; Lisa Hoffman – Then</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">One of Hollywood\'s most versatile and respected actors, Dustin Hoffman has won two Academy Awards for Best Actor in his long, prosperous career. Lisa Hoffman became his second wife when the two married in 1980.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\" wp-image-2967\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"442\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Dustin Hoffman &amp; Lisa Hoffman – Now</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">The Hoffmans have managed to maintain their marriage ever since and there\'s no indication that they won\'t continue that way. They have four children together.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2968\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/6.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"357\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Jack Nicholson &amp; Sandra Knight – Then</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Talented actor Jack Nicholson and Sandra Knight\'s 1962 marriage was a short one, as it only lasted for four years. Even though it was short, the couple managed to have a child together, named Jennifer.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2977\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/15.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"548\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Jack Nicholson &amp; Sandra Knight – Now</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Nicholson has dated many women since his marriage with Knight fell apart. He, of course, went on with his career in acting, while Knight maintains a career as a writer.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2978\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/16.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Pierce Brosnan &amp; Keely Shaye Smith - Then</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Brosnan\'s first wife, Cassandra Harris, sadly passed away in 1991, after the two had been married for 11 years. Brosnan met the journalist Smith in 1994, and the two got married in 2001.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2979\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/17.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"327\" height=\"489\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Pierce Brosnan &amp; Keely Shaye Smith - Now</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">These two are together to this day. They have two sons together, in addition to Brosnan\'s children with his first wife, which they raised as well.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2980\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/18.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"366\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Warren Beatty &amp; Annette Bening – Then</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Warren Beatty, the respected actor-filmmaker, has been quite the ladies\' man in his time. He finally settled down with Annette Bening in 1992.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2981\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/19.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"484\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Warren Beatty &amp; Annette Bening – Now</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">The two are still happily married to this day and have four children together.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2982\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/20.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"309\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Robert Redford &amp; Lola Van Wagenen - Then</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Robert Redford was not only a respected actor and filmmaker but one of the biggest heartthrobs of the 20<sup>th</sup> century. He married the environmental activist Lola Van Wagenen in 1958.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2975\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/13.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"368\" height=\"450\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Robert Redford &amp; Lola Van Wagenen - Now</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Redford and Van Wagenen had four children together during their 30 years of marriage, which ended in 1985. Although they have both remarried other people, the two seem to have remained on good terms with each other.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2976\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/14.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">William Shatner &amp; Elizabeth Shatner – Then</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Known to generations of fans all over the world for his role as Captain Kirk in \"Star Trek\", William Shatner has been married for four different women in his life. He married his last wife, Elizabeth, in 2001.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2987\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/25.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"306\" height=\"490\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">William Shatner &amp; Elizabeth Shatner – Now</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">The Shatners are still married and appear together in public quite often.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2988\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/26.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"476\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Jeff Bridges &amp; Susan Geston - Then</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Jeff Bridges was a true heartthrob back in the day, and he met his future wife Susan Geston while working on \"Rancho Deluxe\" in 1976. The two started dating very quickly after meeting and got married in 1977.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\" wp-image-2997\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/35.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"321\" height=\"480\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Jeff Bridges &amp; Susan Geston - Now</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">This is another happy story, as Bridges and </span>Geston<span style=\"color: #000000;\"> are still married today. They have three daughters together, one of which has blessed them with a granddaughter. Bridges famously thanked his wife and family during his Academy Award acceptance speech.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2998\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/36.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"320\" height=\"480\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Bruce Springsteen &amp; Julianne Phillips - Then</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">One of the greatest musical artists of our time, Bruce Springsteen is one of rock &amp; roll\'s gods. He married successful actress Julianne Phillips in 1985.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2989\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/27.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"550\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Bruce Springsteen &amp; Julianna Phillips - Now</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">The marriage only lasted for four years, though, and in 1989 the couple split up, without having any children together.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2990\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/28.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Howard Stern &amp; Alison Berns - Then</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Howard Stern is a true radio star, and he met Alison Berns while still attending university. The couple got married in 1978; They have three daughters together: Emily, Debra, and Ashley.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2991\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/29.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"532\" height=\"314\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Howard Stern &amp; Alison Berns - Now</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">After 23 years together, Stern and Berns got divorced in 2001. Stern remained the radio star that he is while Berns quickly stepped out of the limelight.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2992\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/30.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Bruce Willis &amp; Demi Moore - Then</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Bruce Willis is one of Hollywood\'s top action heroes. His marriage to Demi Moore in 1987 made waves as they formed a true celebrity power couple. During their marriage, they had three daughters together – Rumer, Scout, and Tallulah.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2993\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/31.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"458\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Bruce Willis &amp; Demi Moore - Now</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Willis and Moore got divorced in 2000, but remain on good terms, and they have even attended each other\'s next weddings.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2994\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/32.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"309\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Dennis Quaid &amp; Meg Ryan - Then</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Dennis Quaid and Meg Ryan met on the set of their film \"D.O.A.\" and fell in love instantly. They married in 1991 and had a son together.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2999\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/37.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"309\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Dennis Quaid &amp; Meg Ryan - Now</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">The two enjoyed great success in their professional lives during the 90\'s, but that came at the cost of their private lives, as the couple got divorced in 2001.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3000\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/38.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Paul Newman &amp; Joanne Woodward – Then</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Paul Newman was considered to be one of the best looking men in the world in his prime. He was married to Jackie Witt for 11 years before the two broke up and he wound up marrying Joanna Woodward in 1958.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3001\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/39.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"533\" height=\"420\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Paul Newman &amp; Joanne Woodward – Now</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Sadly, Paul died in 2008, after 50 years of marriage with Joanne. The couple had three children together during their long, prosperous marriage.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3002\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/40.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"480\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Michael J. Fox &amp; Tracy Pollan - Then</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Michael J. Fox\'s career in the 80\'s was really hot stuff. He met Tracy Pollan on the set of the film \"Family Ties\", but the two started dating only two years later. Michael and Tracy finally tied the knot in 1988.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2985\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/23.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"521\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Michael J. Fox &amp; Tracy Pollan - Now</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">This story has a happy ending, as Michael and Tracy are still together today. Michael was diagnosed with Parkinson\'s disease, and Tracy has remained by his side to support him at all times in a show of true love.  They have four children together.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2986\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/24.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"412\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Kelsey Grammer &amp; Camille Grammer - Then</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Kelsey Grammer married the former Playboy model Camille in 1997. They had two children together who were born via surrogacy.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3005\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/43.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"501\" height=\"322\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Kelsey Grammer &amp; Camille Grammer - Now</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Kelsey and Camille had a very public breakup and divorce in 2011 and went on their separate ways. Kelsey still acts in films and has appeared in \"The Expendables 3\" and \"Transformers: Age of Extinction\".</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3006\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/44.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Jeff Goldblum &amp; Gina Davis - Then</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Jeff Goldblum and Gina Davis met at the height of their success and gave Hollywood a reason cheer. They starred together in 3 films – \"Transylvania 6-5000\", \"The Fly\" and \"Earth Girls Are Easy\" – and got married in 1987.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3011\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/49.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"365\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Jeff Goldblum &amp; Gina Davis - Now</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Unfortunately, the two got divorced three years later in 1990. Goldblum later remarried Emilie Livingston, with whom he is still together today. Davis is married to Reza Jarrahy since 2001.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3012\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/50.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Michael Douglas &amp; Diandra Luker – Then</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Academy Award-winning actor Michael Douglas married Diandra Luker in 1977, and the two remained married until 1995. They had one son together during this time.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3007\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/45.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"421\" height=\"491\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Michael Douglas &amp; Diandra Luker – Now</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Since their breakup, Michael Douglas found his true love in Catherine Zeta-Jones, whom he married in 2000. Douglas and Zeta-Jones have two children together. Luker, meanwhile, has pretty much vanished off the radar after her marriage to Douglas fell apart.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3008\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/46.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Kevin Costner &amp; Cindy Silva - Then</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Kevin Costner and Cindy Silva met each other back in university. They started dating in 1975 and tied the knot officially three years later in 1978.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3009\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/47.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"551\" height=\"413\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Kevin Costner &amp; Cindy Silva - Now</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Costner and Silva\'s love story didn\'t last forever, though, as they got divorced in 1994 after having three children together. Costner went on to become one of Hollywood\'s top actors, while Silva vanished into obscurity.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3010\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/48.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Gene Hackman &amp; Betsy Arakawa – Then</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Gene Hackman was married for Fay Maltese before he got remarried to Betsy Arakawa in 1991. After their marriage, the two wanted to step out of the public eye, and so they left Hollywood and moved to Santa Fe together.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3013\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/51.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"452\" height=\"365\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Gene Hackman &amp; Betsy Arakawa – Now</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Staying out of the limelight worked only to some extent, as Gene is still acting today. But doing so clearly worked for their marriage, as they are still happily married.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3014\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/52.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"417\" height=\"489\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Michael York &amp; Patricia McCallum - Then</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Patricia McCallum was a photographer, and that\'s how she met Michael York – she photographed him at a photo shoot. The two fell in love immediately and got married a year after their initial meeting, in 1968.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3015\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/53.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"551\" height=\"428\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Michael York &amp; Patricia McCallum - Now</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">This is a true love story indeed, as the two are still together today, almost 50 years later.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3016\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/54.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"391\" height=\"489\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Colin Firth &amp; Livia Giuggioli - Then</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">The handsome British heartthrob Colin Firth was married to Meg Tilly, but after their divorce fell into the arms of the beautiful Livia, whom he married in 1997. They have two sons together.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-3017\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/55.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"476\" height=\"480\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Colin Firth &amp; Livia Giuggioli - Now</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Colin and Livia\'s marriage still holds strong even with the considerable success they both enjoy in their professional lives.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3018\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/56.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"366\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Gary Oldman &amp; Uma Thurman - Then</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Another one of Britain\'s greatest actors, Gary Oldman married four times during his life, with beautiful actress Uma Thurman being the second in number. The two married in 1990.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3019\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/57.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"408\" height=\"480\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Gary Oldman &amp; Uma Thurman - Now</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Oldman and Thurman broke their marriage just a couple of years later, in 1992, without having any children together. Uma Thurman is currently married to Ethan Hawke, while Gary Oldman has remarried with Alexandra Edenborough; their marriage lasted until 2015.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3020\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/58.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"478\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Jeremy Irons &amp; Sinead </span>Cusck<span style=\"color: #000000;\"> - Then</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">One of the most talented and versatile actors to come out of England, Jeremy Irons married the Irish-born Sinead </span>Cusck<span style=\"color: #000000;\"> in 1978. This was Irons\' second marriage.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3035\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/73.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"349\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Jeremy Irons &amp; Sinead </span>Cusck<span style=\"color: #000000;\"> - Now</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">It takes true strength for couples to stay together for long in Hollywood, and the Irons-</span>Cusck<span style=\"color: #000000;\"> couple seems to have that strength. They are still married to this day, going on strong for almost 40 years.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3036\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/74.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"326\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Hank Azaria &amp; Helen Hunt - Then</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Hank Azaria and Helen Hunt\'s love story began in 1994, and the two dated for five whole years before finally getting married in 1999.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3021\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/59.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"320\" height=\"480\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Hank Azaria &amp; Helen Hunt - Now</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Sadly, things took a turn for the worst after their marriage and the two just couldn\'t keep the relationship going. They split and got divorced just one year later, in 2000.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3022\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/60.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Johnny Depp &amp; Lori Anne Allison - Then</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Johnny Depp\'s first wife, Lori Anne Allison, was a make- up artist whom he met in the early 80\'s. The two got married in 1983 but got divorced soon after, in 1985.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3023\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/61.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"344\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Johnny Depp &amp; Lori Anne Allison - Now</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Depp has been married twice since then, with both marriages ending in divorce. Johnny and Lori seem to have remained on good terms, though, as Lori has been testifying on Depp\'s behalf in the domestic violence case he was involved in due to the accusations of his last ex-wife, Amber Heard.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3024\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/62.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Mel Gibson &amp; Robyn Moore - Then</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Mel Gibson is a versatile actor and director with quite a controversial repertoire. He met Robyn Moore on the set of Mad Max, and the two got married in 1980.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3025\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/63.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"300\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Mel Gibson &amp; Robyn Moore - Now</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">After having seven children together – six sons and one daughter – and being married for 33 years, Gibson called it time on the marriage. He has gone on to remarry and had one more child.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3026\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/64.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Tim Allen &amp; Laura Deibel - Then</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Tim Allen is a respected and valued actor all across Hollywood. He married Laura Deibel in 1984; Laura gave birth to their daughter Katherine five years later, in 1989.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3043\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/81.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"311\" height=\"491\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Tim Allen &amp; Laura Deibel - Now</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Tim and Laura remained married until 2003, although they already separated four years earlier. Tim got remarried and had one more child, and Laura chose to step out of the limelight for good.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3044\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/82.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Antonio Banderas &amp; Melanie Griffith - Then</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Antonio and Melanie met on the set of the film \"Too Much\", in which they starred together, and got married a year later, in 1996.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3027\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/65.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"414\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Antonio Banderas &amp; Melanie Griffith - Now</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Not all things last, though, and the two finally got divorced in 2015 after having one daughter together.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3028\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/66.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"391\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Robert Downey Jr. &amp; Deborah Falconer - Then</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Robert Downey Jr. and Deborah Falconer were only dating for 42 days before tying the knot in 1992. They later had one son together, named Indio.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2983\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/21.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"317\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Robert Downey Jr. &amp; Deborah Falconer - Now</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">The couple got divorced in 2004, mainly due to Robert\'s drug abuse related issues. Downey Jr. married his current wife, Susan Downey, a mere one year later. He has managed to get rid of his bad habits and has been one of Hollywood\'s top paid and most sought after actors of the past decade.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2984\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/22.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Burt Reynolds &amp; Lori Anderson – Then</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Burt Reynolds is truly one of Hollywood\'s greats. He was married twice in his lifetime, and the marriage to his second wife, Lori Anderson, came in 1988.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3031\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/69.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"552\" height=\"375\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Burt Reynolds &amp; Lori Anderson – Now</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">They eventually broke up five years later, in 1993, after having adopted one child together. Burt Reynolds is still very active in the movie industry and continues to appear in films.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3032\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/70.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Robert De Niro &amp; </span>Diahnne<span style=\"color: #000000;\"> Abbot - Then</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Robert De Niro is one of Hollywood\'s most recognizable faces, and with good reason. The actor has been in the industry for </span>decades,<span style=\"color: #000000;\"> and has credits in dozens of films. He married Diahnne Abbot in 1976.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3051\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/89.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"388\" height=\"480\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Robert De Niro &amp; </span>Diahnne<span style=\"color: #000000;\"> Abbot - Now</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">The couple managed to sustain their marriage until 1988. De Niro is currently married to Grace Hightower, while </span>Diahnne<span style=\"color: #000000;\"> has stepped out of the limelight – little is known about her whereabouts.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3052\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/90.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Russell Crowe &amp; Danielle Spencer - Then</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Danielle Spencer co-starred alongside Russell Crowe in the 1989 film \"The Crossing\" – and that\'s how the two had met. They were involved in a rollercoaster of a relationship, breaking up just to get back together a while later, until finally tying the knot in 2003.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3033\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/71.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"551\" height=\"310\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Russell Crowe &amp; Danielle Spencer - Now</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">The two finally separated for good in 2012, although they are still technically married as they have not gotten officially divorced. They have two sons together.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\" wp-image-3034\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/72.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"338\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Tommy Lee &amp; Heather Locklear - Then</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Rockstar Tommy Lee and beautiful actress Heather Locklear got married in 1986 and formed a true rock-star couple.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3029\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/67.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"416\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Tommy Lee &amp; Heather Locklear - Now</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Their marriage didn\'t last too long, and in 1993, Lee and Locklear finally got divorced, after 7 years of a rollercoaster of a relationship.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3030\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/68.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Mark Hamill &amp; Marilou York - Then</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Mark Hamill met Marilou York at what seemed to be the prime of his life – in the year 1978, just a year after Star Wars: A New Hope was released worldwide and became a cultural phenomenon. The couple got married that same year.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3037\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/75.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"359\" height=\"480\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Mark Hamill &amp; Marilou York - Now</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Although not living in a galaxy far, far away, the two are living happily ever after, and are still married, going strong for almost 40 years. They have three children together – Nathan, Griffin, and Elizabeth.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3038\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/76.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"309\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Alec Baldwin &amp; Kim Basinger - Then</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Alec and Kim were another couple to meet on a shared set, in their case on the set of \"The Marrying Man\" in 1990. They married in 1993 and had one daughter together in 1995.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3039\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/77.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"548\" height=\"355\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Alec Baldwin &amp; Kim Basinger - Now</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">They ultimately divorced in 2002. Baldwin remarried Hilaria Thomas and has three more children with her.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3040\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/78.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"408\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Andre Agassi &amp; Brooke Shields - Then</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">The (now retired) professional tennis player married the gorgeous Brooke Shields in 1997 in what turned out to be a very publicized and public relationship.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3041\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/79.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"417\" height=\"480\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Andre Agassi &amp; Brooke Shields - Now</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Agassi and Shields broke up only two years later, in 1999, without bringing any children to the world together. Sometimes, things just don\'t work out.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3042\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/80.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"266\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">George Clooney &amp; Talia Balsam - Then</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Every man dreams of looking like him, and every woman dreams of being with him – that is how you best describe George Clooney. He married his first wife Talia Balsam before his big breakthrough, in 1989.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3045\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/83.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"339\" height=\"480\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">George Clooney &amp; Talia Balsam - Now</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Clooney and Balsam eventually called it quits in 1993, and Clooney became known as the man who just can\'t keep his relationships going. He is now happily married to Amal Clooney, though, and things are looking differently good for him.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3046\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/84.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Michael Caine &amp; Shakira Caine - Then</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Michael Caine has been a household name in Hollywood for decades, over which he has amassed an honorable reputation as a versatile actor. He married Shakira Caine in 1973.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3047\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/85.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"359\" height=\"480\" /></span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span>\r\n<h1><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Michael Caine &amp; Shakira Caine - Now</span></h1>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Michael and Shakira are still happily married to this day, with their marriage now spanning over 40 years. They have one daughter together, named Natasha Haleema.</span></h3>\r\n<span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3048\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/86.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"361\" height=\"480\" /></span>','Wives Of The Stars – Then & Now','','inherit','closed','closed','','643-revision-v1','','','2017-03-09 14:19:42','2017-03-09 14:19:42','',643,'http://www.theladypost.com/2017/03/09/643-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(660,2,'2017-03-09 15:15:14','2017-03-09 15:15:14','','prebid','','inherit','open','closed','','prebid','','','2017-03-09 15:15:14','2017-03-09 15:15:14','',0,'http://www.theladypost.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/03/prebid.js',0,'attachment','application/javascript',0),(661,2,'2017-03-09 16:16:13','2017-03-09 16:16:13','<h2>Most people look better when they\'re young, that\'s no secret. The skin is smoother, the eyes sharper, and the hair fuller. Celebrities are just the same – their looks degrade as they get older. But not these stars. These stars get better looking with age: the older they become, the better they look. Check out the list and see if you agree!</h2>\r\n<h1>Joseph Gordon-Levitt</h1>\r\n<h3>Moviegoers got their first look of the then-teenager Joseph Gordon-Levitt when he appeared on \"10 Things I Hate About You\" in 1999. Back then he looked like the skinnier, less successful version of his co-star Heath Ledger. Today Joseph has gained some muscle weight, and has grown overall, and looks finer than he did in his early days.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1422\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/215.jpg\" alt=\"2\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /></h3>\r\n<h3><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Justin Timberlake</h1>\r\n<h3>Something about Justin Timberlake\'s looks early in his career just feels off. Maybe it\'s the way he used to style his hair. Today, though, it\'s a completely different story, as Justin has turned into a stunning young man, whose good looks assured that his transition from music to the big screen would go as smoothly as can be.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1447\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/271.png\" alt=\"27\" width=\"549\" height=\"449\" /></h3>\r\n<h3><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Jennifer Lopez</h1>\r\n<h3>Jennifer Lopez has been around for a long, long time. She was always adored by men and women alike all around the world for her beauty, as well as for her singing and dancing skills. It\'s unbelievable to think that J-Lo is nearing her 50\'s – as she looks better than ever, and keeps showing that at every opportunity.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1424\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/412.jpg\" alt=\"4\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" />\r\n<h3><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>George Clooney</h1>\r\n<h3>To be honest, Clooney has always been good looking. But today he is the prime example of what every man wishes he would look like, no matter his age. There\'s no arguing that Clooney is one of the best looking men in the world. For him, age is not only not an issue, but a blessing.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1427\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/74.jpg\" alt=\"7\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /></h3>\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Jennifer Aniston</h1>\r\n<h3>OK, Jennifer Aniston was always stunning. From her early days on \"Friends\", Jennifer has always been considered as one of Hollywood\'s prettiest actresses. But recent appearances in films such as \"Horrible Bosses\" (1&amp;2) and \"We\'re The Millers\" prove that her looks just keep getting better with age, even at 47. If you have any doubts, consider this: She was named the \"Most Beautiful Woman\" of 2016 by People Magazine.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1425\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/513.jpg\" alt=\"5\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /></h3>\r\n<h3><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Charlize Theron</h1>\r\n<h3>It truly speaks volumes when you\'re having trouble identifying which picture is from the past and which picture is from the present. Charlize Theron\'s unique, stunning beauty is undeniable, but she manages to look better with each passing year. It\'s mind-boggling to think that these pictures were taken years apart.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1430\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/104.jpg\" alt=\"10\" width=\"551\" height=\"413\" /></h3>\r\n<h3><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Dwayne Johnson</h1>\r\n<h3>Dwayne \"The Rock\" Johnson started his career in wrestling, and wrestlers don\'t necessarily need to be beautiful and presentable. The Rock certainly wasn\'t, as this picture here from his early 20\'s shows. The move to Hollywood did well for old Dwayne, as he is one of the finest looking actors around, with an impeccable style and handsome looks that just keep getting better with time.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1423\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/316.jpg\" alt=\"3\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /></h3>\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<h3><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Beyonce</h1>\r\n<h3>Beyonce was beautiful when she was younger too, sure, but today the pop star is absolutely gorgeous and serves as an example and as a role model for millions of women worldwide. Although she is fast approaching her 40\'s, Beyonce is looking better and prettier than ever.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1448\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/284.jpg\" alt=\"28\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /></h3>\r\n<h3><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Nicole Kidman</h1>\r\n<h3>The amazingly talented Australian actress Nicole Kidman has been considered a rare and true beauty since her early days. But today, even though she is nearing the age of 50, the beautiful blonde looks even more stunning, her looks stand in complete contrast with her age.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1428\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/8.png\" alt=\"8\" width=\"550\" height=\"353\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Tom Cruise</h1>\r\n<h3>Tom Cruise is easily one of the most recognizable faces in Hollywood. With a prosperous career spanning over 20 years behind him, it\'s truly a wonder how that man has managed to maintain his good looks and to look even better than he did when he was younger. He\'s been named by People magazine as one of the 50 most beautiful men in the world for three times, and you can obviously understand why.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1429\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/9.png\" alt=\"9\" width=\"549\" height=\"349\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Robert Downey Jr.</h1>\r\n<h3>Robert Downey Jr. spent his early Hollywood days in a battle with various drug addictions, which clearly didn\'t help his boyish looks back in the day. Now he is considered one of Hollywood\'s hottest men while being the top-earning actor in the business for the past few years.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1421\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/116.jpg\" alt=\"1\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /></h3>\r\n<h3><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Ryan Phillippe</h1>\r\n<h3>Ryan Phillippe has been around Hollywood since the 90\'s and has been consistently considered one of the industry\'s biggest heartthrobs. Age doesn\'t seem to affect dear old Ryan as well – on the contrary, he looks just as good today as he did back then. Maybe even better…</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1432\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/121.png\" alt=\"12\" width=\"551\" height=\"375\" /></h3>\r\n<h3><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Julia Louis-Dreyfus</h1>\r\n<h3>There\'s something about Julia Louis-Dreyfus that just looks much better today than she did back in her \"Seinfeld\" days. Not that she didn\'t look great back then – but the \"Veep\" star has managed to keep her charm while becoming even better looking than before.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1434\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/14.png\" alt=\"14\" width=\"550\" height=\"289\" /></h3>\r\n<h3><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Halle Berry</h1>\r\n<h3>Halle Berry was always a beauty, and while it certainly is true that it doesn\'t seem like she aged that much since the beginning of her career way back in the 90\'s, you could argue that the Academy Award-winning actress looks even better today. Her style and elegance just keep getting better and better. She is in top shape indeed – could you guess she is already 50 years old?</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1433\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/134.jpg\" alt=\"13\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /></h3>\r\n<h3><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Kevin Bacon</h1>\r\n<h3>Being one of the most respected and loved actors in Hollywood must be doing wonders for your look, as Kevin Bacon proves once again that he just keeps getting better and better looking as the years go by. He looks nowhere near his true age of 58 years old and has managed to maintain his wonderful youthful look.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1445\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/25.png\" alt=\"25\" width=\"550\" height=\"377\" />\r\n<h3><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Victoria Beckham</h1>\r\n<h3>Yes, Victoria Beckham was always famous for her good looks. But she is well in her forties now, and still looks just as gorgeous – if not more – as she was in her twenties. And this alone speaks volumes, doesn\'t it?</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1437\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/17.png\" alt=\"17\" width=\"550\" height=\"440\" /></h3>\r\n<h3><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Gwyneth Paltrow</h1>\r\n<h3>The veteran actress has been around for many years and was always considered a true beauty. What\'s truly astonishing about her is that she is in her mid-40s, but doesn’t look a day over 30. Gwyneth is as beautiful as ever no matter her age.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1435\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/15.png\" alt=\"15\" width=\"550\" height=\"350\" /></h3>\r\n<h3><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Gabrielle Union</h1>\r\n<h3>Gabrielle Union joins this lists\' list of people that were already beautiful, to begin with. She has been gorgeous from the start, but it\'s truly amazing to witness how she just keeps looking better and better as time goes by; by all accounts, she looks even better today than she ever did.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1444\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/24.png\" alt=\"24\" width=\"549\" height=\"439\" /></h3>\r\n<h3><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Julianna Margulies</h1>\r\n<h3>Julianna Margulies undoubtedly looks more beautiful today than she did in her early years, but what\'s so amazing about that is that she does it without looking any older. She is as classy, elegant and sophisticated as they come, but never looks a day over 30 at worst.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1436\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/16.png\" alt=\"16\" width=\"550\" height=\"473\" /></h3>\r\n<h3><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Malcolm-Jamal Warner</h1>\r\n<h3>Back in the 90\'s, Malcolm was a cute, good boy looking kind of guy. Today he\'s looking much manlier and is a handsome young man by all accounts.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1442\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/224.jpg\" alt=\"22\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /></h3>\r\n<h3><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Demi Moore</h1>\r\n<h3>Demi Moore has blossomed with every passing year. Time has turned this once beautiful young lady into a matured, stunningly gorgeous woman, and she still turns heads around wherever she goes.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1438\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/18.png\" alt=\"18\" width=\"550\" height=\"418\" /></h3>\r\n<h3><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Uma Thurman</h1>\r\n<h3>While her eyes will never change and will stay as stunning as they are forever, Uma Thurman is still one of Hollywood\'s sexiest and most beautiful actresses at the age of 46. Wrinkles and other signs of old age just seem to stay away from her.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1443\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/23.png\" alt=\"23\" width=\"550\" height=\"363\" /></h3>\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<h3><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Sean Connery</h1>\r\n<h3>Connery was a gorgeous young man when he played Bond, there\'s absolutely no doubt about that. But even at old age, the Scottish actor looks terrific, showing that for him looks don\'t fade – they improve.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1431\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/117.jpg\" alt=\"11\" width=\"551\" height=\"551\" /></h3>\r\n<h3><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Gabrielle Union</h1>\r\n<h3>Gabrielle Union joins this lists\' list of people that were already beautiful, to begin with. She has been gorgeous from the start, but it\'s truly amazing to witness how she just keeps looking better and better as time goes by; by all accounts, she looks even better today than she ever did.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1444\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/24.png\" alt=\"24\" width=\"549\" height=\"439\" /></h3>\r\n<h3><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Nicole Richie</h1>\r\n<h3>Tuning down her troubled lifestyle has certainly helped Nicole Richie with her looks. Her early years were surrounded by controversy and some very brave fashion choices. Nowadays Nicole is just breathtaking, her beauty more balanced, her style more defined than ever before.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1440\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/204.jpg\" alt=\"20\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /></h3>\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<h3><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Blair Underwood</h1>\r\n<h3>Blair Underwood had a very boyish, round look back in his 20\'s. This look always gave away the impression that Blair is actually younger than he really was. Today he is 47 years old and looks simply fantastic – He could certainly pass for a 30-something-year-old.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1441\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/216.jpg\" alt=\"21\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /></h3>\r\n<h3><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Ryan Gosling</h1>\r\n<h3>Ryan Gosling got his major breakthrough in Hollywood when he starred in the 2004 film the notebook. The film\'s director Nick Cassavetes actually chose Gosling for the role because he thought he wasn\'t good looking. Gosling, of course, has gotten better and better looking as time went by and is widely considered to be one of the hottest men in Hollywood today.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1450\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/304.jpg\" alt=\"30\" width=\"550\" height=\"550\" />\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Kate Beckinsale</h1>\r\n<h3>Kate Beckinsale started acting at a very young age. She was a pretty teenager-turned-gorgeous young woman, but as the years go by it seems like she\'s just getting more and more beautiful. Her face has lost its roundness and has a more refined chiseled look nowadays, which aids Kate\'s undeniable elegance.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1446\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/263.jpg\" alt=\"26\" width=\"497\" height=\"497\" /><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Bradley Cooper</h1>\r\n<h3>Bradley Cooper is consistently featured in every respectful magazine\'s list of the best looking men in Hollywood, and with good reason. Now in his early 40\'s, he looks undoubtedly better than he did even a decade before. He has perfected his rough yet stylish look and developed a sense of fashion like no other actor in Hollywood.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1449\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/294.jpg\" alt=\"29\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" /></h3>\r\n<h3><!--nextpage--></h3>\r\n<h1>Johnny Depp</h1>\r\n<h3>Johnny Depp is a case very similar to Robert Downey Jr. He\'s one of Hollywood\'s most appreciated and sought-after actors today, and while he was certainly a good looking young man back in his early boyish days, there\'s no denying today\'s Johnny is one of the hottest and sexiest men in the world. He\'s also approaching his mid-50s, mind you. Not that it shows.</h3>\r\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1426\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/6.png\" alt=\"6\" width=\"550\" height=\"311\" /></h3>','30 Stars Who Look Better With Age','','inherit','closed','closed','','650-revision-v1','','','2017-03-09 16:16:13','2017-03-09 16:16:13','',650,'http://www.theladypost.com/2017/03/09/650-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(662,2,'2017-03-12 09:03:15','2017-03-12 09:03:15','<h3>Celebrity couples are nothing new – stars have been known to date amongst themselves for decades. But the nature of the glamor of Hollywood makes it difficult to sustain relationships for long times, as evidenced time and time again with some of Hollywood\'s most iconic couples splitting up. Where did the wives of those Hollywood stars end up after their relationships ended? Which of those memorable couples are still together to this day?</h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">John Travolta &amp; Kelly Preston – Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">John Travolta met Kelly Preston on the set of the film \"The Experts\" in which they were both starring. Kelly was in a relationship with Charlie Sheen, but the two broke up and she married Travolta in 1991. The two had two separate weddings – one legal ceremonial wedding and one wedding in accordance with the rules of Scientology.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2995\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/33.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"345\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">John Travolta &amp; Kelly Preston – Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Travolta and Preston are still married today, and had three children together, although one of their children, Jett, has sadly passed away at the age of 16.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2996\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/34.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"434\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Elvis Presley &amp; Priscilla Presley - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Priscilla Presley was only 14 when Elvis and she met for the first time. Regardless of her young age, Elvis and Priscilla dated for seven years before tying the knot in 1967. The couple had one daughter together, Lisa Marie.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\" wp-image-2965\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"550\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Elvis Presley &amp; Priscilla Presley - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Elvis, as we all know, tragically died in 1977. By the time of his death, the two were divorced for a couple of years, mainly due to Elvis\' drug habit. Priscilla remained in the limelight, although not as much as she had been before.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2966\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Sylvester Stallone &amp; Brigitte Nielson - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Stallone is known worldwide as the face of both Rocky Balboa and Rambo and is considered a legend in Hollywood. He married actress-model Brigitte Nielson in 1985.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\" wp-image-3003\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/41.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"367\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Sylvester Stallone &amp; Brigitte Nielson - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Unfortunately, the marriage didn\'t last long at all, and the two separated after just two years as husband and wife.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3004\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/42.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Anthony Hopkins &amp; Jennifer Leyton - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Anthony Hopkins is a true Hollywood giant. He married Jennifer Leyton in 1973, after being briefly married before to Petronella Barker.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2969\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/7.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"338\" height=\"500\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Anthony Hopkins &amp; Jennifer Leyton - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Hopkins and Leyton remained together for almost 30 years until thy separated in 2002. Hopkins has remarried since, to Stella Arroyave.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2970\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/8.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"326\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Harrison Ford &amp; Calista Flockhart – Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Harrison was already one of Hollywood\'s biggest stars when Calista made her breakthrough. The two met at the 2002 Golden Globe Awards and dated for years before getting married in 2010.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3049\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/87.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"548\" height=\"443\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Harrison Ford &amp; Calista Flockhart – Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Harrison Ford is still going strong with his acting. He famously appeared reprised his role as Han Solo in \"Star Wars: The Force Awakens\" and is scheduled to reprise his role in the \"Blade Runner\" sequel as well. Ford and Flockhart are still </span>married,<span style=\"color: #000000;\"> and make sure to appear together everywhere they go.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3050\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/88.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"409\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Sean Connery &amp; Micheline Roquebrune - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Sean Connery is, without a doubt, one of the most respected and valued actors of all time, most prominently remembered for portraying James Bond. He married Morrocan-French painter Micheline Roquebrune in 1975.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2971\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/9.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"330\" height=\"490\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Sean Connery &amp; Micheline Roquebrune - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Sean and Micheline are still happily married today after all those years, and maintain a healthy and admirable family life with their grandchildren.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\" wp-image-2972\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/10.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"333\" height=\"490\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Clint Eastwood &amp; Maggie Johnson - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">One of the most beautiful men of his time, and undoubtedly one of the most talented, Clint Eastwood was sought after by countless women. He married Maggie Johnson in 1958, but their marriage turned out to be a difficult one.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\" wp-image-2963\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"505\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Clint Eastwood &amp; Maggie Johnson - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">The couple managed to stay together for 31 years before ending the marriage. During this time the couple had two children together, although Eastwood had fathered another child from a different woman while he was still married to Johnson.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2964\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Sean Penn &amp; Madonna – Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Sean Penn and Madonna were a real power couple during their four years of marriage, from 1985 to 1989. The two stars couldn’t keep their marriage intact for any longer and ended their marriage with a bang.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2973\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/11.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"412\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Sean Penn &amp; Madonna – Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">The two went on to have even bigger careers than anyone would have imagined back then. They both got remarried – Sean to Robin Wright and Madonna to Guy Ritchie – and both re-divorced only recently.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2974\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/12.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"445\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Dustin Hoffman &amp; Lisa Hoffman – Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">One of Hollywood\'s most versatile and respected actors, Dustin Hoffman has won two Academy Awards for Best Actor in his long, prosperous career. Lisa Hoffman became his second wife when the two married in 1980.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\" wp-image-2967\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"442\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Dustin Hoffman &amp; Lisa Hoffman – Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">The Hoffmans have managed to maintain their marriage ever since and there\'s no indication that they won\'t continue that way. They have four children together.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2968\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/6.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"357\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Jack Nicholson &amp; Sandra Knight – Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Talented actor Jack Nicholson and Sandra Knight\'s 1962 marriage was a short one, as it only lasted for four years. Even though it was short, the couple managed to have a child together, named Jennifer.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2977\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/15.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"548\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Jack Nicholson &amp; Sandra Knight – Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Nicholson has dated many women since his marriage with Knight fell apart. He, of course, went on with his career in acting, while Knight maintains a career as a writer.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2978\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/16.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Pierce Brosnan &amp; Keely Shaye Smith - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Brosnan\'s first wife, Cassandra Harris, sadly passed away in 1991, after the two had been married for 11 years. Brosnan met the journalist Smith in 1994, and the two got married in 2001.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2979\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/17.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"327\" height=\"489\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Pierce Brosnan &amp; Keely Shaye Smith - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">These two are together to this day. They have two sons together, in addition to Brosnan\'s children with his first wife, which they raised as well.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2980\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/18.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"366\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Warren Beatty &amp; Annette Bening – Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Warren Beatty, the respected actor-filmmaker, has been quite the ladies\' man in his time. He finally settled down with Annette Bening in 1992.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2981\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/19.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"484\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Warren Beatty &amp; Annette Bening – Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">The two are still happily married to this day and have four children together.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2982\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/20.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"309\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Robert Redford &amp; Lola Van Wagenen - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Robert Redford was not only a respected actor and filmmaker but one of the biggest heartthrobs of the 20<sup>th</sup> century. He married the environmental activist Lola Van Wagenen in 1958.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2975\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/13.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"368\" height=\"450\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Robert Redford &amp; Lola Van Wagenen - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Redford and Van Wagenen had four children together during their 30 years of marriage, which ended in 1985. Although they have both remarried other people, the two seem to have remained on good terms with each other.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2976\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/14.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">William Shatner &amp; Elizabeth Shatner – Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Known to generations of fans all over the world for his role as Captain Kirk in \"Star Trek\", William Shatner has been married for four different women in his life. He married his last wife, Elizabeth, in 2001.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2987\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/25.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"306\" height=\"490\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">William Shatner &amp; Elizabeth Shatner – Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">The Shatners are still married and appear together in public quite often.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2988\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/26.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"476\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Jeff Bridges &amp; Susan Geston - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Jeff Bridges was a true heartthrob back in the day, and he met his future wife Susan Geston while working on \"Rancho Deluxe\" in 1976. The two started dating very quickly after meeting and got married in 1977.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\" wp-image-2997\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/35.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"321\" height=\"480\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Jeff Bridges &amp; Susan Geston - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">This is another happy story, as Bridges and </span>Geston are<span style=\"color: #000000;\"> still married today. They have three daughters together, one of which has blessed them with a granddaughter. Bridges famously thanked his wife and family during his Academy Award acceptance speech.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2998\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/36.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"320\" height=\"480\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Bruce Springsteen &amp; Julianne Phillips - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">One of the greatest musical artists of our time, Bruce Springsteen is one of rock &amp; roll\'s gods. He married successful actress Julianne Phillips in 1985.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2989\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/27.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"550\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Bruce Springsteen &amp; Julianna Phillips - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">The marriage only lasted for four years, though, and in 1989 the couple split up, without having any children together.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2990\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/28.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Howard Stern &amp; Alison Berns - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Howard Stern is a true radio star, and he met Alison Berns while still attending university. The couple got married in 1978; They have three daughters together: Emily, Debra, and Ashley.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2991\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/29.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"532\" height=\"314\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Howard Stern &amp; Alison Berns - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">After 23 years together, Stern and Berns got divorced in 2001. Stern remained the radio star that he is while Berns quickly stepped out of the limelight.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2992\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/30.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Bruce Willis &amp; Demi Moore - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Bruce Willis is one of Hollywood\'s top action heroes. His marriage to Demi Moore in 1987 made waves as they formed a true celebrity power couple. During their marriage, they had three daughters together – Rumer, Scout, and Tallulah.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2993\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/31.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"458\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Bruce Willis &amp; Demi Moore - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Willis and Moore got divorced in 2000, but remain on good terms, and they have even attended each other\'s next weddings.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2994\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/32.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"309\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Dennis Quaid &amp; Meg Ryan - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Dennis Quaid and Meg Ryan met on the set of their film \"D.O.A.\" and fell in love instantly. They married in 1991 and had a son together.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2999\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/37.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"309\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Dennis Quaid &amp; Meg Ryan - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">The two enjoyed great success in their professional lives during the 90\'s, but that came at the cost of their private lives, as the couple got divorced in 2001.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3000\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/38.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Paul Newman &amp; Joanne Woodward – Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Paul Newman was considered to be one of the best looking men in the world in his prime. He was married to Jackie Witt for 11 years before the two broke up and he wound up marrying Joanna Woodward in 1958.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3001\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/39.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"533\" height=\"420\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Paul Newman &amp; Joanne Woodward – Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Sadly, Paul died in 2008, after 50 years of marriage with Joanne. The couple had three children together during their long, prosperous marriage.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3002\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/40.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"480\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Michael J. Fox &amp; Tracy Pollan - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Michael J. Fox\'s career in the 80\'s was really hot stuff. He met Tracy Pollan on the set of the film \"Family Ties\", but the two started dating only two years later. Michael and Tracy finally tied the knot in 1988.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2985\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/23.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"521\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Michael J. Fox &amp; Tracy Pollan - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">This story has a happy ending, as Michael and Tracy are still together today. Michael was diagnosed with Parkinson\'s disease, and Tracy has remained by his side to support him at all times in a show of true love.  They have four children together.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2986\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/24.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"412\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Kelsey Grammer &amp; Camille Grammer - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Kelsey Grammer married the former Playboy model Camille in 1997. They had two children together who were born via surrogacy.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3005\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/43.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"501\" height=\"322\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Kelsey Grammer &amp; Camille Grammer - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Kelsey and Camille had a very public breakup and divorce in 2011 and went on their separate ways. Kelsey still acts in films and has appeared in \"The Expendables 3\" and \"Transformers: Age of Extinction\".</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3006\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/44.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Jeff Goldblum &amp; Gina Davis - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Jeff Goldblum and Gina Davis met at the height of their success and gave Hollywood a reason cheer. They starred together in 3 films – \"Transylvania 6-5000\", \"The Fly\" and \"Earth Girls Are Easy\" – and got married in 1987.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3011\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/49.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"365\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Jeff Goldblum &amp; Gina Davis - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Unfortunately, the two got divorced three years later in 1990. Goldblum later remarried Emilie Livingston, with whom he is still together today. Davis is married to Reza Jarrahy since 2001.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3012\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/50.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Michael Douglas &amp; Diandra Luker – Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Academy Award-winning actor Michael Douglas married Diandra Luker in 1977, and the two remained married until 1995. They had one son together during this time.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3007\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/45.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"421\" height=\"491\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Michael Douglas &amp; Diandra Luker – Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Since their breakup, Michael Douglas found his true love in Catherine Zeta-Jones, whom he married in 2000. Douglas and Zeta-Jones have two children together. Luker, meanwhile, has pretty much vanished off the radar after her marriage to Douglas fell apart.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3008\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/46.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Kevin Costner &amp; Cindy Silva - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Kevin Costner and Cindy Silva met each other back in university. They started dating in 1975 and tied the knot officially three years later in 1978.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3009\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/47.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"551\" height=\"413\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Kevin Costner &amp; Cindy Silva - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Costner and Silva\'s love story didn\'t last forever, though, as they got divorced in 1994 after having three children together. Costner went on to become one of Hollywood\'s top actors, while Silva vanished into obscurity.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3010\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/48.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Gene Hackman &amp; Betsy Arakawa – Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Gene Hackman was married for Fay Maltese before he got remarried to Betsy Arakawa in 1991. After their marriage, the two wanted to step out of the public eye, and so they left Hollywood and moved to Santa Fe together.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3013\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/51.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"452\" height=\"365\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Gene Hackman &amp; Betsy Arakawa – Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Staying out of the limelight worked only to some extent, as Gene is still acting today. But doing so clearly worked for their marriage, as they are still happily married.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3014\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/52.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"417\" height=\"489\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Michael York &amp; Patricia McCallum - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Patricia McCallum was a photographer, and that\'s how she met Michael York – she photographed him at a photo shoot. The two fell in love immediately and got married a year after their initial meeting, in 1968.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3015\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/53.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"551\" height=\"428\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Michael York &amp; Patricia McCallum - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">This is a true love story indeed, as the two are still together today, almost 50 years later.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3016\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/54.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"391\" height=\"489\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Colin Firth &amp; Livia Giuggioli - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">The handsome British heartthrob Colin Firth was married to Meg Tilly, but after their divorce fell into the arms of the beautiful Livia, whom he married in 1997. They have two sons together.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-3017\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/55.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"476\" height=\"480\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Colin Firth &amp; Livia Giuggioli - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Colin and Livia\'s marriage still holds strong even with the considerable success they both enjoy in their professional lives.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3018\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/56.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"366\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Gary Oldman &amp; Uma Thurman - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Another one of Britain\'s greatest actors, Gary Oldman married four times during his life, with beautiful actress Uma Thurman being the second in number. The two married in 1990.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3019\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/57.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"408\" height=\"480\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Gary Oldman &amp; Uma Thurman - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Oldman and Thurman broke their marriage just a couple of years later, in 1992, without having any children together. Uma Thurman is currently married to Ethan Hawke, while Gary Oldman has remarried with Alexandra Edenborough; their marriage lasted until 2015.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3020\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/58.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"478\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Jeremy Irons &amp; Sinead </span>Cusck<span style=\"color: #000000;\"> - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">One of the most talented and versatile actors to come out of England, Jeremy Irons married the Irish-born Sinead </span></h3>\r\nCusck\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"> in 1978. This was Irons\' second marriage.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3035\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/73.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"349\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Jeremy Irons &amp; Sinead </span>Cusck<span style=\"color: #000000;\"> - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">It takes true strength for couples to stay together for long in Hollywood, and the Irons-</span></h3>\r\nCusck\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"> couple seems to have that strength. They are still married to this day, going on strong for almost 40 years.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3036\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/74.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"326\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Hank Azaria &amp; Helen Hunt - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Hank Azaria and Helen Hunt\'s love story began in 1994, and the two dated for five whole years before finally getting married in 1999.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3021\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/59.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"320\" height=\"480\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Hank Azaria &amp; Helen Hunt - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Sadly, things took a turn for the worst after their marriage and the two just couldn\'t keep the relationship going. They split and got divorced just one year later, in 2000.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3022\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/60.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Johnny Depp &amp; Lori Anne Allison - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Johnny Depp\'s first wife, Lori Anne Allison, was a make- up artist whom he met in the early 80\'s. The two got married in 1983 but got divorced soon after, in 1985.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3023\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/61.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"344\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Johnny Depp &amp; Lori Anne Allison - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Depp has been married twice since then, with both marriages ending in divorce. Johnny and Lori seem to have remained on good terms, though, as Lori has been testifying on Depp\'s behalf in the domestic violence case he was involved in due to the accusations of his last ex-wife, Amber Heard.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3024\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/62.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Mel Gibson &amp; Robyn Moore - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Mel Gibson is a versatile actor and director with quite a controversial repertoire. He met Robyn Moore on the set of Mad Max, and the two got married in 1980.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3025\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/63.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"300\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Mel Gibson &amp; Robyn Moore - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">After having seven children together – six sons and one daughter – and being married for 33 years, Gibson called it time on the marriage. He has gone on to remarry and had one more child.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3026\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/64.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Tim Allen &amp; Laura Deibel - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Tim Allen is a respected and valued actor all across Hollywood. He married Laura Deibel in 1984; Laura gave birth to their daughter Katherine five years later, in 1989.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3043\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/81.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"311\" height=\"491\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Tim Allen &amp; Laura Deibel - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Tim and Laura remained married until 2003, although they already separated four years earlier. Tim got remarried and had one more child, and Laura chose to step out of the limelight for good.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3044\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/82.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Antonio Banderas &amp; Melanie Griffith - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Antonio and Melanie met on the set of the film \"Too Much\", in which they starred together, and got married a year later, in 1996.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3027\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/65.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"414\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Antonio Banderas &amp; Melanie Griffith - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Not all things last, though, and the two finally got divorced in 2015 after having one daughter together.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3028\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/66.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"391\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Robert Downey Jr. &amp; Deborah Falconer - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Robert Downey Jr. and Deborah Falconer were only dating for 42 days before tying the knot in 1992. They later had one son together, named Indio.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2983\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/21.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"317\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Robert Downey Jr. &amp; Deborah Falconer - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">The couple got divorced in 2004, mainly due to Robert\'s drug abuse related issues. Downey Jr. married his current wife, Susan Downey, a mere one year later. He has managed to get rid of his bad habits and has been one of Hollywood\'s top paid and most sought after actors of the past decade.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2984\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/22.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Burt Reynolds &amp; Lori Anderson – Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Burt Reynolds is truly one of Hollywood\'s greats. He was married twice in his lifetime, and the marriage to his second wife, Lori Anderson, came in 1988.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3031\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/69.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"552\" height=\"375\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Burt Reynolds &amp; Lori Anderson – Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">They eventually broke up five years later, in 1993, after having adopted one child together. Burt Reynolds is still very active in the movie industry and continues to appear in films.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3032\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/70.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Robert De Niro &amp; </span>Diahnne<span style=\"color: #000000;\"> Abbot - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Robert De Niro is one of Hollywood\'s most recognizable faces, and with good reason. The actor has been in the industry for </span></h3>\r\n<h3>decades,</h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"> and has credits in dozens of films. He married Diahnne Abbot in 1976.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3051\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/89.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"388\" height=\"480\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Robert De Niro &amp; </span>Diahnne<span style=\"color: #000000;\"> Abbot - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">The couple managed to sustain their marriage until 1988. De Niro is currently married to Grace Hightower, while </span></h3>\r\nDiahnne\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"> has stepped out of the limelight – little is known about her whereabouts.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3052\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/90.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Russell Crowe &amp; Danielle Spencer - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Danielle Spencer co-starred alongside Russell Crowe in the 1989 film \"The Crossing\" – and that\'s how the two had met. They were involved in a rollercoaster of a relationship, breaking up just to get back together a while later, until finally tying the knot in 2003.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3033\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/71.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"551\" height=\"310\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Russell Crowe &amp; Danielle Spencer - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">The two finally separated for good in 2012, although they are still technically married as they have not gotten officially divorced. They have two sons together.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\" wp-image-3034\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/72.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"338\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Tommy Lee &amp; Heather Locklear - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Rockstar Tommy Lee and beautiful actress Heather Locklear got married in 1986 and formed a true rock-star couple.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3029\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/67.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"416\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Tommy Lee &amp; Heather Locklear - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Their marriage didn\'t last too long, and in 1993, Lee and Locklear finally got divorced, after 7 years of a rollercoaster of a relationship.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3030\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/68.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Mark Hamill &amp; Marilou York - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Mark Hamill met Marilou York at what seemed to be the prime of his life – in the year 1978, just a year after Star Wars: A New Hope was released worldwide and became a cultural phenomenon. The couple got married that same year.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3037\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/75.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"359\" height=\"480\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Mark Hamill &amp; Marilou York - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Although not living in a galaxy far, far away, the two are living happily ever after, and are still married, going strong for almost 40 years. They have three children together – Nathan, Griffin, and Elizabeth.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3038\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/76.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"309\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Alec Baldwin &amp; Kim Basinger - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Alec and Kim were another couple to meet on a shared set, in their case on the set of \"The Marrying Man\" in 1990. They married in 1993 and had one daughter together in 1995.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3039\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/77.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"548\" height=\"355\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Alec Baldwin &amp; Kim Basinger - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">They ultimately divorced in 2002. Baldwin remarried Hilaria Thomas and has three more children with her.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3040\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/78.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"408\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Andre Agassi &amp; Brooke Shields - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">The (now retired) professional tennis player married the gorgeous Brooke Shields in 1997 in what turned out to be a very publicized and public relationship.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3041\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/79.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"417\" height=\"480\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Andre Agassi &amp; Brooke Shields - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Agassi and Shields broke up only two years later, in 1999, without bringing any children to the world together. Sometimes, things just don\'t work out.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3042\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/80.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"266\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">George Clooney &amp; Talia Balsam - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Every man dreams of looking like him, and every woman dreams of being with him – that is how you best describe George Clooney. He married his first wife Talia Balsam before his big breakthrough, in 1989.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3045\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/83.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"339\" height=\"480\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">George Clooney &amp; Talia Balsam - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Clooney and Balsam eventually called it quits in 1993, and Clooney became known as the man who just can\'t keep his relationships going. He is now happily married to Amal Clooney, though, and things are looking differently good for him.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3046\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/84.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Michael Caine &amp; Shakira Caine - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Michael Caine has been a household name in Hollywood for decades, over which he has amassed an honorable reputation as a versatile actor. He married Shakira Caine in 1973.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3047\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/85.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"359\" height=\"480\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Michael Caine &amp; Shakira Caine - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Michael and Shakira are still happily married to this day, with their marriage now spanning over 40 years. They have one daughter together, named Natasha Haleema.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3048\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/86.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"361\" height=\"480\" /></span></h3>','Wives Of The Stars – Then & Now','','inherit','closed','closed','','643-autosave-v1','','','2017-03-12 09:03:15','2017-03-12 09:03:15','',643,'http://www.theladypost.com/2017/03/12/643-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(663,2,'2017-03-12 09:03:03','2017-03-12 09:03:03','<h3>Celebrity couples are nothing new – stars have been known to date amongst themselves for decades. But the nature of the glamor of Hollywood makes it difficult to sustain relationships for long times, as evidenced time and time again with some of Hollywood\'s most iconic couples splitting up. Where did the wives of those Hollywood stars end up after their relationships ended? Which of those memorable couples are still together to this day?</h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">John Travolta &amp; Kelly Preston – Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">John Travolta met Kelly Preston on the set of the film \"The Experts\" in which they were both starring. Kelly was in a relationship with Charlie Sheen, but the two broke up and she married Travolta in 1991. The two had two separate weddings – one legal ceremonial wedding and one wedding in accordance with the rules of Scientology.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2995\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/33.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"345\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">John Travolta &amp; Kelly Preston – Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Travolta and Preston are still married today, and had three children together, although one of their children, Jett, has sadly passed away at the age of 16.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2996\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/34.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"434\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Elvis Presley &amp; Priscilla Presley - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Priscilla Presley was only 14 when Elvis and she met for the first time. Regardless of her young age, Elvis and Priscilla dated for seven years before tying the knot in 1967. The couple had one daughter together, Lisa Marie.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\" wp-image-2965\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"550\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Elvis Presley &amp; Priscilla Presley - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Elvis, as we all know, tragically died in 1977. By the time of his death, the two were divorced for a couple of years, mainly due to Elvis\' drug habit. Priscilla remained in the limelight, although not as much as she had been before.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2966\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Sylvester Stallone &amp; Brigitte Nielson - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Stallone is known worldwide as the face of both Rocky Balboa and Rambo and is considered a legend in Hollywood. He married actress-model Brigitte Nielson in 1985.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\" wp-image-3003\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/41.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"367\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Sylvester Stallone &amp; Brigitte Nielson - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Unfortunately, the marriage didn\'t last long at all, and the two separated after just two years as husband and wife.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3004\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/42.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Anthony Hopkins &amp; Jennifer Leyton - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Anthony Hopkins is a true Hollywood giant. He married Jennifer Leyton in 1973, after being briefly married before to Petronella Barker.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2969\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/7.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"338\" height=\"500\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Anthony Hopkins &amp; Jennifer Leyton - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Hopkins and Leyton remained together for almost 30 years until thy separated in 2002. Hopkins has remarried since, to Stella Arroyave.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2970\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/8.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"326\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Harrison Ford &amp; Calista Flockhart – Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Harrison was already one of Hollywood\'s biggest stars when Calista made her breakthrough. The two met at the 2002 Golden Globe Awards and dated for years before getting married in 2010.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3049\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/87.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"548\" height=\"443\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Harrison Ford &amp; Calista Flockhart – Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Harrison Ford is still going strong with his acting. He famously appeared reprised his role as Han Solo in \"Star Wars: The Force Awakens\" and is scheduled to reprise his role in the \"Blade Runner\" sequel as well. Ford and Flockhart are still </span>married,<span style=\"color: #000000;\"> and make sure to appear together everywhere they go.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3050\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/88.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"409\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Sean Connery &amp; Micheline Roquebrune - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Sean Connery is, without a doubt, one of the most respected and valued actors of all time, most prominently remembered for portraying James Bond. He married Morrocan-French painter Micheline Roquebrune in 1975.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2971\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/9.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"330\" height=\"490\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Sean Connery &amp; Micheline Roquebrune - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Sean and Micheline are still happily married today after all those years, and maintain a healthy and admirable family life with their grandchildren.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\" wp-image-2972\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/10.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"333\" height=\"490\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Clint Eastwood &amp; Maggie Johnson - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">One of the most beautiful men of his time, and undoubtedly one of the most talented, Clint Eastwood was sought after by countless women. He married Maggie Johnson in 1958, but their marriage turned out to be a difficult one.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\" wp-image-2963\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"505\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Clint Eastwood &amp; Maggie Johnson - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">The couple managed to stay together for 31 years before ending the marriage. During this time the couple had two children together, although Eastwood had fathered another child from a different woman while he was still married to Johnson.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2964\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Sean Penn &amp; Madonna – Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Sean Penn and Madonna were a real power couple during their four years of marriage, from 1985 to 1989. The two stars couldn’t keep their marriage intact for any longer and ended their marriage with a bang.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2973\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/11.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"412\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Sean Penn &amp; Madonna – Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">The two went on to have even bigger careers than anyone would have imagined back then. They both got remarried – Sean to Robin Wright and Madonna to Guy Ritchie – and both re-divorced only recently.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2974\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/12.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"445\" /><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Dustin Hoffman &amp; Lisa Hoffman – Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">One of Hollywood\'s most versatile and respected actors, Dustin Hoffman has won two Academy Awards for Best Actor in his long, prosperous career. Lisa Hoffman became his second wife when the two married in 1980.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\" wp-image-2967\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"442\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Dustin Hoffman &amp; Lisa Hoffman – Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">The Hoffmans have managed to maintain their marriage ever since and there\'s no indication that they won\'t continue that way. They have four children together.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2968\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/6.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"357\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Jack Nicholson &amp; Sandra Knight – Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Talented actor Jack Nicholson and Sandra Knight\'s 1962 marriage was a short one, as it only lasted for four years. Even though it was short, the couple managed to have a child together, named Jennifer.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2977\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/15.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"548\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Jack Nicholson &amp; Sandra Knight – Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Nicholson has dated many women since his marriage with Knight fell apart. He, of course, went on with his career in acting, while Knight maintains a career as a writer.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2978\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/16.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Pierce Brosnan &amp; Keely Shaye Smith - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Brosnan\'s first wife, Cassandra Harris, sadly passed away in 1991, after the two had been married for 11 years. Brosnan met the journalist Smith in 1994, and the two got married in 2001.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2979\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/17.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"327\" height=\"489\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Pierce Brosnan &amp; Keely Shaye Smith - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">These two are together to this day. They have two sons together, in addition to Brosnan\'s children with his first wife, which they raised as well.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2980\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/18.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"366\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Warren Beatty &amp; Annette Bening – Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Warren Beatty, the respected actor-filmmaker, has been quite the ladies\' man in his time. He finally settled down with Annette Bening in 1992.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2981\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/19.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"484\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Warren Beatty &amp; Annette Bening – Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">The two are still happily married to this day and have four children together.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2982\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/20.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"309\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Robert Redford &amp; Lola Van Wagenen - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Robert Redford was not only a respected actor and filmmaker but one of the biggest heartthrobs of the 20<sup>th</sup> century. He married the environmental activist Lola Van Wagenen in 1958.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2975\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/13.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"368\" height=\"450\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Robert Redford &amp; Lola Van Wagenen - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Redford and Van Wagenen had four children together during their 30 years of marriage, which ended in 1985. Although they have both remarried other people, the two seem to have remained on good terms with each other.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2976\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/14.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">William Shatner &amp; Elizabeth Shatner – Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Known to generations of fans all over the world for his role as Captain Kirk in \"Star Trek\", William Shatner has been married for four different women in his life. He married his last wife, Elizabeth, in 2001.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2987\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/25.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"306\" height=\"490\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">William Shatner &amp; Elizabeth Shatner – Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">The Shatners are still married and appear together in public quite often.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2988\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/26.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"476\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Jeff Bridges &amp; Susan Geston - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Jeff Bridges was a true heartthrob back in the day, and he met his future wife Susan Geston while working on \"Rancho Deluxe\" in 1976. The two started dating very quickly after meeting and got married in 1977.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\" wp-image-2997\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/35.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"321\" height=\"480\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Jeff Bridges &amp; Susan Geston - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">This is another happy story, as Bridges and </span>Geston are<span style=\"color: #000000;\"> still married today. They have three daughters together, one of which has blessed them with a granddaughter. Bridges famously thanked his wife and family during his Academy Award acceptance speech.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2998\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/36.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"320\" height=\"480\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Bruce Springsteen &amp; Julianne Phillips - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">One of the greatest musical artists of our time, Bruce Springsteen is one of rock &amp; roll\'s gods. He married successful actress Julianne Phillips in 1985.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2989\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/27.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"550\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Bruce Springsteen &amp; Julianna Phillips - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">The marriage only lasted for four years, though, and in 1989 the couple split up, without having any children together.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2990\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/28.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Howard Stern &amp; Alison Berns - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Howard Stern is a true radio star, and he met Alison Berns while still attending university. The couple got married in 1978; They have three daughters together: Emily, Debra, and Ashley.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2991\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/29.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"532\" height=\"314\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Howard Stern &amp; Alison Berns - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">After 23 years together, Stern and Berns got divorced in 2001. Stern remained the radio star that he is while Berns quickly stepped out of the limelight.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2992\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/30.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Bruce Willis &amp; Demi Moore - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Bruce Willis is one of Hollywood\'s top action heroes. His marriage to Demi Moore in 1987 made waves as they formed a true celebrity power couple. During their marriage, they had three daughters together – Rumer, Scout, and Tallulah.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2993\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/31.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"458\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Bruce Willis &amp; Demi Moore - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Willis and Moore got divorced in 2000, but remain on good terms, and they have even attended each other\'s next weddings.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2994\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/32.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"309\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Dennis Quaid &amp; Meg Ryan - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Dennis Quaid and Meg Ryan met on the set of their film \"D.O.A.\" and fell in love instantly. They married in 1991 and had a son together.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2999\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/37.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"309\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Dennis Quaid &amp; Meg Ryan - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">The two enjoyed great success in their professional lives during the 90\'s, but that came at the cost of their private lives, as the couple got divorced in 2001.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3000\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/38.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Paul Newman &amp; Joanne Woodward – Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Paul Newman was considered to be one of the best looking men in the world in his prime. He was married to Jackie Witt for 11 years before the two broke up and he wound up marrying Joanna Woodward in 1958.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3001\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/39.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"533\" height=\"420\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Paul Newman &amp; Joanne Woodward – Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Sadly, Paul died in 2008, after 50 years of marriage with Joanne. The couple had three children together during their long, prosperous marriage.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3002\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/40.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"480\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Michael J. Fox &amp; Tracy Pollan - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Michael J. Fox\'s career in the 80\'s was really hot stuff. He met Tracy Pollan on the set of the film \"Family Ties\", but the two started dating only two years later. Michael and Tracy finally tied the knot in 1988.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2985\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/23.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"521\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Michael J. Fox &amp; Tracy Pollan - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">This story has a happy ending, as Michael and Tracy are still together today. Michael was diagnosed with Parkinson\'s disease, and Tracy has remained by his side to support him at all times in a show of true love.  They have four children together.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2986\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/24.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"412\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Kelsey Grammer &amp; Camille Grammer - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Kelsey Grammer married the former Playboy model Camille in 1997. They had two children together who were born via surrogacy.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3005\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/43.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"501\" height=\"322\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Kelsey Grammer &amp; Camille Grammer - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Kelsey and Camille had a very public breakup and divorce in 2011 and went on their separate ways. Kelsey still acts in films and has appeared in \"The Expendables 3\" and \"Transformers: Age of Extinction\".</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3006\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/44.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Jeff Goldblum &amp; Gina Davis - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Jeff Goldblum and Gina Davis met at the height of their success and gave Hollywood a reason cheer. They starred together in 3 films – \"Transylvania 6-5000\", \"The Fly\" and \"Earth Girls Are Easy\" – and got married in 1987.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3011\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/49.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"365\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Jeff Goldblum &amp; Gina Davis - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Unfortunately, the two got divorced three years later in 1990. Goldblum later remarried Emilie Livingston, with whom he is still together today. Davis is married to Reza Jarrahy since 2001.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3012\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/50.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Michael Douglas &amp; Diandra Luker – Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Academy Award-winning actor Michael Douglas married Diandra Luker in 1977, and the two remained married until 1995. They had one son together during this time.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3007\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/45.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"421\" height=\"491\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Michael Douglas &amp; Diandra Luker – Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Since their breakup, Michael Douglas found his true love in Catherine Zeta-Jones, whom he married in 2000. Douglas and Zeta-Jones have two children together. Luker, meanwhile, has pretty much vanished off the radar after her marriage to Douglas fell apart.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3008\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/46.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Kevin Costner &amp; Cindy Silva - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Kevin Costner and Cindy Silva met each other back in university. They started dating in 1975 and tied the knot officially three years later in 1978.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3009\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/47.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"551\" height=\"413\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Kevin Costner &amp; Cindy Silva - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Costner and Silva\'s love story didn\'t last forever, though, as they got divorced in 1994 after having three children together. Costner went on to become one of Hollywood\'s top actors, while Silva vanished into obscurity.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3010\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/48.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Gene Hackman &amp; Betsy Arakawa – Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Gene Hackman was married for Fay Maltese before he got remarried to Betsy Arakawa in 1991. After their marriage, the two wanted to step out of the public eye, and so they left Hollywood and moved to Santa Fe together.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3013\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/51.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"452\" height=\"365\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Gene Hackman &amp; Betsy Arakawa – Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Staying out of the limelight worked only to some extent, as Gene is still acting today. But doing so clearly worked for their marriage, as they are still happily married.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3014\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/52.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"417\" height=\"489\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Michael York &amp; Patricia McCallum - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Patricia McCallum was a photographer, and that\'s how she met Michael York – she photographed him at a photo shoot. The two fell in love immediately and got married a year after their initial meeting, in 1968.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3015\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/53.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"551\" height=\"428\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Michael York &amp; Patricia McCallum - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">This is a true love story indeed, as the two are still together today, almost 50 years later.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3016\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/54.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"391\" height=\"489\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Colin Firth &amp; Livia Giuggioli - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">The handsome British heartthrob Colin Firth was married to Meg Tilly, but after their divorce fell into the arms of the beautiful Livia, whom he married in 1997. They have two sons together.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-3017\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/55.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"476\" height=\"480\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Colin Firth &amp; Livia Giuggioli - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Colin and Livia\'s marriage still holds strong even with the considerable success they both enjoy in their professional lives.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3018\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/56.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"366\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Gary Oldman &amp; Uma Thurman - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Another one of Britain\'s greatest actors, Gary Oldman married four times during his life, with beautiful actress Uma Thurman being the second in number. The two married in 1990.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3019\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/57.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"408\" height=\"480\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Gary Oldman &amp; Uma Thurman - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Oldman and Thurman broke their marriage just a couple of years later, in 1992, without having any children together. Uma Thurman is currently married to Ethan Hawke, while Gary Oldman has remarried with Alexandra Edenborough; their marriage lasted until 2015.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3020\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/58.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"478\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Jeremy Irons &amp; Sinead </span>Cusck<span style=\"color: #000000;\"> - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">One of the most talented and versatile actors to come out of England, Jeremy Irons married the Irish-born Sinead </span></h3>\r\nCusck\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"> in 1978. This was Irons\' second marriage.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3035\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/73.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"349\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Jeremy Irons &amp; Sinead </span>Cusck<span style=\"color: #000000;\"> - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">It takes true strength for couples to stay together for long in Hollywood, and the Irons-</span></h3>\r\nCusck\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"> couple seems to have that strength. They are still married to this day, going on strong for almost 40 years.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3036\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/74.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"326\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Hank Azaria &amp; Helen Hunt - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Hank Azaria and Helen Hunt\'s love story began in 1994, and the two dated for five whole years before finally getting married in 1999.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3021\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/59.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"320\" height=\"480\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Hank Azaria &amp; Helen Hunt - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Sadly, things took a turn for the worst after their marriage and the two just couldn\'t keep the relationship going. They split and got divorced just one year later, in 2000.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3022\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/60.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Johnny Depp &amp; Lori Anne Allison - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Johnny Depp\'s first wife, Lori Anne Allison, was a make- up artist whom he met in the early 80\'s. The two got married in 1983 but got divorced soon after, in 1985.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3023\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/61.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"344\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Johnny Depp &amp; Lori Anne Allison - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Depp has been married twice since then, with both marriages ending in divorce. Johnny and Lori seem to have remained on good terms, though, as Lori has been testifying on Depp\'s behalf in the domestic violence case he was involved in due to the accusations of his last ex-wife, Amber Heard.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3024\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/62.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Mel Gibson &amp; Robyn Moore - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Mel Gibson is a versatile actor and director with quite a controversial repertoire. He met Robyn Moore on the set of Mad Max, and the two got married in 1980.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3025\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/63.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"300\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Mel Gibson &amp; Robyn Moore - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">After having seven children together – six sons and one daughter – and being married for 33 years, Gibson called it time on the marriage. He has gone on to remarry and had one more child.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3026\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/64.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Tim Allen &amp; Laura Deibel - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Tim Allen is a respected and valued actor all across Hollywood. He married Laura Deibel in 1984; Laura gave birth to their daughter Katherine five years later, in 1989.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3043\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/81.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"311\" height=\"491\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Tim Allen &amp; Laura Deibel - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Tim and Laura remained married until 2003, although they already separated four years earlier. Tim got remarried and had one more child, and Laura chose to step out of the limelight for good.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3044\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/82.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Antonio Banderas &amp; Melanie Griffith - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Antonio and Melanie met on the set of the film \"Too Much\", in which they starred together, and got married a year later, in 1996.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3027\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/65.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"414\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Antonio Banderas &amp; Melanie Griffith - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Not all things last, though, and the two finally got divorced in 2015 after having one daughter together.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3028\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/66.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"391\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Robert Downey Jr. &amp; Deborah Falconer - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Robert Downey Jr. and Deborah Falconer were only dating for 42 days before tying the knot in 1992. They later had one son together, named Indio.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2983\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/21.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"317\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Robert Downey Jr. &amp; Deborah Falconer - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">The couple got divorced in 2004, mainly due to Robert\'s drug abuse related issues. Downey Jr. married his current wife, Susan Downey, a mere one year later. He has managed to get rid of his bad habits and has been one of Hollywood\'s top paid and most sought after actors of the past decade.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-2984\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/22.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Burt Reynolds &amp; Lori Anderson – Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Burt Reynolds is truly one of Hollywood\'s greats. He was married twice in his lifetime, and the marriage to his second wife, Lori Anderson, came in 1988.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3031\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/69.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"552\" height=\"375\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Burt Reynolds &amp; Lori Anderson – Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">They eventually broke up five years later, in 1993, after having adopted one child together. Burt Reynolds is still very active in the movie industry and continues to appear in films.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3032\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/70.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Robert De Niro &amp; </span>Diahnne<span style=\"color: #000000;\"> Abbot - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Robert De Niro is one of Hollywood\'s most recognizable faces, and with good reason. The actor has been in the industry for </span></h3>\r\n<h3>decades,</h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"> and has credits in dozens of films. He married Diahnne Abbot in 1976.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3051\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/89.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"388\" height=\"480\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Robert De Niro &amp; </span>Diahnne<span style=\"color: #000000;\"> Abbot - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">The couple managed to sustain their marriage until 1988. De Niro is currently married to Grace Hightower, while </span></h3>\r\nDiahnne\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"> has stepped out of the limelight – little is known about her whereabouts.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3052\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/90.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Russell Crowe &amp; Danielle Spencer - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Danielle Spencer co-starred alongside Russell Crowe in the 1989 film \"The Crossing\" – and that\'s how the two had met. They were involved in a rollercoaster of a relationship, breaking up just to get back together a while later, until finally tying the knot in 2003.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3033\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/71.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"551\" height=\"310\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Russell Crowe &amp; Danielle Spencer - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">The two finally separated for good in 2012, although they are still technically married as they have not gotten officially divorced. They have two sons together.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\" wp-image-3034\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/72.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"338\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Tommy Lee &amp; Heather Locklear - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Rockstar Tommy Lee and beautiful actress Heather Locklear got married in 1986 and formed a true rock-star couple.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3029\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/67.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"416\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Tommy Lee &amp; Heather Locklear - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Their marriage didn\'t last too long, and in 1993, Lee and Locklear finally got divorced, after 7 years of a rollercoaster of a relationship.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3030\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/68.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Mark Hamill &amp; Marilou York - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Mark Hamill met Marilou York at what seemed to be the prime of his life – in the year 1978, just a year after Star Wars: A New Hope was released worldwide and became a cultural phenomenon. The couple got married that same year.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3037\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/75.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"359\" height=\"480\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Mark Hamill &amp; Marilou York - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Although not living in a galaxy far, far away, the two are living happily ever after, and are still married, going strong for almost 40 years. They have three children together – Nathan, Griffin, and Elizabeth.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3038\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/76.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"309\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Alec Baldwin &amp; Kim Basinger - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Alec and Kim were another couple to meet on a shared set, in their case on the set of \"The Marrying Man\" in 1990. They married in 1993 and had one daughter together in 1995.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3039\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/77.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"548\" height=\"355\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Alec Baldwin &amp; Kim Basinger - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">They ultimately divorced in 2002. Baldwin remarried Hilaria Thomas and has three more children with her.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3040\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/78.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"408\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Andre Agassi &amp; Brooke Shields - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">The (now retired) professional tennis player married the gorgeous Brooke Shields in 1997 in what turned out to be a very publicized and public relationship.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3041\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/79.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"417\" height=\"480\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Andre Agassi &amp; Brooke Shields - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Agassi and Shields broke up only two years later, in 1999, without bringing any children to the world together. Sometimes, things just don\'t work out.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3042\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/80.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"549\" height=\"266\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">George Clooney &amp; Talia Balsam - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Every man dreams of looking like him, and every woman dreams of being with him – that is how you best describe George Clooney. He married his first wife Talia Balsam before his big breakthrough, in 1989.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3045\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/83.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"339\" height=\"480\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">George Clooney &amp; Talia Balsam - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Clooney and Balsam eventually called it quits in 1993, and Clooney became known as the man who just can\'t keep his relationships going. He is now happily married to Amal Clooney, though, and things are looking differently good for him.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3046\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/84.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"550\" height=\"275\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Michael Caine &amp; Shakira Caine - Then</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Michael Caine has been a household name in Hollywood for decades, over which he has amassed an honorable reputation as a versatile actor. He married Shakira Caine in 1973.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3047\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/85.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"359\" height=\"480\" /></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><!--nextpage--></span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Michael Caine &amp; Shakira Caine - Now</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Michael and Shakira are still happily married to this day, with their marriage now spanning over 40 years. They have one daughter together, named Natasha Haleema.</span></h3>\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-3048\" src=\"http://d2581bmrn7s1tf.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/86.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"361\" height=\"480\" /></span></h3>','Wives Of The Stars – Then & Now','','inherit','closed','closed','','643-revision-v1','','','2017-03-12 09:03:03','2017-03-12 09:03:03','',643,'http://www.theladypost.com/2017/03/12/643-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(664,2,'2017-03-12 10:37:41','2017-03-12 10:37:41','<h1>We all love pets, and celebrities are no different. Whether they show them to the world or not, these celebs have the cutest pets you can find.</h1>\n<h1>Taylor Swift and Her Cats</h1>\n<h3>Taylor Swift, besides being a pop sensation, is a known cat enthusiast. Her cats are named Dr. Meredith Grey and Detective Olivia Benson. Both cats have flourishing Instagram accounts.</h3>\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1199\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Taylor.png\" alt=\"taylor\" width=\"480\" height=\"475\" />\n\n<!--nextpage-->\n<h1>Jennifer Lawrence and Pippi</h1>\n<h3>Jennifer Lawrence can\'t seem to do anything wrong, as the young talented actress enjoys incredible success over the past few years. She has a cute puppy called Pippi Lawrence who is very close to her heart.</h3>\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1187\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/jen1.jpg\" alt=\"jen\" width=\"549\" height=\"549\" />\n<!--nextpage-->\n<h1>Cara Delevigne and Cecil The Bunny</h1>\n<h3>Cara Delevigne is a very successful young actor and model, but her bunny Cecil is successful in his own right. Cecil has a Twitter account as well as an Instagram account with thousands of followers on each one.</h3>\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1206\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/cara.png\" alt=\"cara\" width=\"480\" height=\"480\" />\n<!--nextpage-->\n<h1>Miley Cyrus\' Cats and Dogs</h1>\n<h3>Miley Cyrus is a wonderful pet owner. She has been known to adopt many pets – dogs, cats, rabbits and even a pig, once. Her current pet resume includes 6 dogs and 3 cats (that we know of).</h3>\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1193\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/miley.png\" alt=\"miley\" width=\"500\" height=\"500\" />\n\n<!--nextpage-->\n<h1>Ariana Grande and Sirius Black</h1>\n<h3>Ariana Grande is apparently a Harry Potter fan, as she named her newest puppy Sirius Black, after a character in the Harry Potter series.</h3>\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1183\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/grande-black.jpg\" alt=\"grande-black\" width=\"538\" height=\"538\" />\n\n<!--nextpage-->\n<h1>Orlando Bloom and Sidi</h1>\n<h3>The other half of the Perry-Bloom couple, Orlando Bloom is known for his affection for dogs. He has a rescue Saluki mix named Sidi, of whom he takes great care.</h3>\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1196\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/orlando-bloom.jpg\" alt=\"orlando-bloom\" width=\"550\" height=\"447\" />\n<!--nextpage-->\n<h1>Justin Bieber and Esther</h1>\n<h3>Justin Bieber, the teen pop sensation and heartthrob, has a cute puppy named Esther Bieber. He also owns another pup named Phil.</h3>\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1204\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Bieber.jpg\" alt=\"bieber\" width=\"520\" height=\"515\" />\n\n<!--nextpage-->\n<h1>Iggy Azalea</h1>\n<h3>Iggy Azalea has been in the spotlight for the past few years, releasing some hit singles. She owns a French bulldog who goes by the very long name of Shrinkabull Jam Don\'t Shake Like That Jelli Azalea.</h3>\n<h3><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1185\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/iggy.jpg\" alt=\"iggy\" width=\"359\" height=\"479\" /></h3>\n<!--nextpage-->\n<h1>Liam Hemsworth and Dora</h1>\n<h3>Known for his role in \"The Hunger Games\" trilogy, Liam Hemsworth is a known dog lover, and has adopted a pet dog called Dora.</h3>\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1192\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/liam-hem.jpg\" alt=\"liam-hem\" width=\"388\" height=\"479\" />\n\n<!--nextpage-->\n<h1>Emmy Rossum and Cinnamon</h1>\n<h3>Emmy Rossum of the TV series \"Shameless\" has a cute puppy named Cinnamon. She shares pictures of Cinnamon and her frequently on Instagram.</h3>\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1182\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/emmy-rossum.jpg\" alt=\"emmy-rossum\" width=\"550\" height=\"550\" />\n<!--nextpage-->\n<h1>Ariana Grande and Toulouse</h1>\n<h3>Before adopting Sirius Black, Grande has adopted Toulouse from an animal shelter. Toulouse has since modeled for Coach.</h3>\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1184\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/grande-toulouse.jpg\" alt=\"grande-toulouse\" width=\"540\" height=\"540\" />\n\n<!--nextpage-->\n<h1>Paris Hilton and Peter Pan</h1>\n<h3>Paris Hilton\'s pets were always famous, and she is known to keep them by her side at all times. Her most famous current pooch, the Chihuahua Peter Pan Hilton, has over 39 thousand followers on Instagram.</h3>\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1197\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/paris.jpg\" alt=\"paris\" width=\"353\" height=\"480\" />\n<!--nextpage-->\n<h1>Demi Lovato\'s Buddy</h1>\n<h3>Demi Lovato\'s pup named Buddy has his own Twitter following, with over 61 thousand followers on his account.</h3>\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1180\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/demi.jpg\" alt=\"demi\" width=\"297\" height=\"480\" />\n<!--nextpage-->\n<h1>Nikki Reed and Ian Somerhalder\'s dogs</h1>\n<h3>The successful couple owns two dogs, and they make sure to post as many pictures of them on Instagram as they can. The dogs are named Enzo Reed and Nietzsche Somerhalder.</h3>\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1209\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/nikki-reed1.jpg\" alt=\"nikki-reed\" width=\"548\" height=\"517\" />\n\n<!--nextpage-->\n<h1>Amanda Seyfried and Finn</h1>\n<h3>Amanda Seyfried is an American actress known for roles in films such as \"Mean Girls\" and \"Mamma Mia\". Her best friend is an Australian Shepard named Finn.</h3>\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1201\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/amanda.jpg\" alt=\"amanda\" width=\"550\" height=\"550\" />\n<!--nextpage-->\n<h1>Anna Sophia Robb and Sir Ferguson</h1>\nAnna Sophia Robb is a teen actor. She has appeared in numerous successful Hollywood films and is a proud owner of a pet dog named Sir Ferguson.\n\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1202\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/annasophia.png\" alt=\"annasophia\" width=\"549\" height=\"550\" />\n\n<!--nextpage-->\n<h1>Katy Perry and Kitty Purry</h1>\n<h3>Katy Perry is an avid cat lover and has gone on record announcing it on various occasions. Her most famous cat is Kitty Purry, who made a cameo in Perry\'s \"I Kissed a Girl\" video.</h3>\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1189\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Katy_perry_and_kitty_purry.jpg\" alt=\"katy_perry_and_kitty_purry\" width=\"472\" height=\"461\" />\n\n<!--nextpage-->\n<h1>Jessica Chastain and Chaplin</h1>\n<h3>Jessica Chaplain sure has a kind heart. She has adopted a three-legged pooch named Chaplin. The two appeared together on the TV show \"The View\".</h3>\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1188\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/jessica.jpg\" alt=\"jessica\" width=\"550\" height=\"540\" />\n<!--nextpage-->\n<h1>Kaley Cuoco and Ruby</h1>\n<h3>Kaley Cuoco is known for playing the character of Penny in \"The Big Bang Theory\". She also owns a cute little pup she has adopted from an animal shelter, named Ruby.</h3>\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1205\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/caley.jpg\" alt=\"caley\" width=\"551\" height=\"367\" />\n<!--nextpage-->\n<h1>Diana Agron and Freddie</h1>\n<h3>The former \"Glee\" star also owns a cute French bulldog, who she named Freddie. She regularly posts pictures of Freddie on Instagram.</h3>\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1200\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/agron.jpg\" alt=\"agron\" width=\"549\" height=\"548\" />\n\n<!--nextpage-->\n<h1>Chloe Grace Moretz and Missy</h1>\n<h3>Chloe Grace Moretz is a dog enthusiast, and currently owns two dogs, one of which she named Missy. She even took Missy with her to the set of her film \"Carrie\".</h3>\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1208\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/chloe.jpg\" alt=\"chloe\" width=\"351\" height=\"501\" />\n<!--nextpage-->\n<h1>Chelsea Handler</h1>\n<h3>American actress, television host and producer Chelsea Handler has a cute pup named Tammy.</h3>\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1207\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/chelsea.jpeg\" alt=\"chelsea\" width=\"377\" height=\"502\" />\n<!--nextpage-->\n<h1>Lena Dunham and Lamby</h1>\n<h3>Lena Dunham gained fame for writing and starring in the hit TV show \"Girls\". She has a dog named Lamby whom she takes with her everywhere.</h3>\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1191\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/lena.jpg\" alt=\"lena\" width=\"550\" height=\"550\" />\n<!--nextpage-->\n<h1>Ed Sheeran and Graham</h1>\n<h3>Ed Sheeran is known for writing and singing heartfelt songs. The English singer has a big heart himself, and he has adopted a cute little kitten who goes by the name of Graham.</h3>\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1181\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Ed-sheeran.jpg\" alt=\"ed-sheeran\" width=\"541\" height=\"541\" />\n\n<!--nextpage-->\n<h1>Ariel Winter and Chloe</h1>\n<h3>Ariel Winter of \"Modern Family\" fame has recently adopted a beautiful German Shepard and named her Chloe. Besides Chloe, Winter has 2 other dogs.</h3>\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1203\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/ariel.jpg\" alt=\"ariel\" width=\"539\" height=\"540\" />\n\n<!--nextpage-->\n<h1>Jake Gyllenhaal and Atticus</h1>\n<h3>Jake Gyllenhaal is a respected and versatile American actor, known for his Academy Award-nominated performance in \"Brokeback Mountain\". He has a beloved dog named Atticus.</h3>\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1186\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Jake.jpg\" alt=\"jake\" width=\"368\" height=\"502\" />\n\n<!--nextpage-->\n<h1>Chrissy Teigen and Pippa</h1>\n<h3>Chrissy Teigen and her husband, singer-songwriter John Legend, own a handful of dogs. One of which is the cute Pippa, who is a French bulldog.</h3>\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1179\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/chrissy.jpg\" alt=\"chrissy\" width=\"550\" height=\"550\" />\n<!--nextpage-->\n<h1>Sarah Hyland and Barkley</h1>\n<h3>Another \"Modern Family\" star who is a famous pet owner is Sarah Hyland who plays the role of Haley on the show. She owns a cute puppy called Barkley whom she trained all on her own.</h3>\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1198\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Sarah-Hyland-1.jpg\" alt=\"sarah-hyland-1\" width=\"351\" height=\"501\" />\n\n<!--nextpage-->\n<h1>Miranda Kerr and Frankie</h1>\n<h3>Miranda Kerr is an international supermodel. When she has some time off from modeling, though, she enjoys cuddling with her cute puppy Frankie.</h3>\n<img class=\" wp-image-1194\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Miranda-Kerrr.jpg\" alt=\"Australian model Miranda Kerr looking beautiful in blue as she poses with her pet dog while on the set of a commercial in Santa Monica, Ca Pictured: Miranda Kerr Ref: SPL943776 050215 Picture by: London Entertainment /Splash Splash News and Pictures Los Angeles: 310-821-2666 New York: 212-619-2666 London: 870-934-2666 photodesk@splashnews.com \" width=\"404\" height=\"499\" />\n\n<!--nextpage-->\n<h1>Lady Gaga and Miss Asia Kinney</h1>\n<h3>Famous and successful singer and performer Lady Gaga has a black French Bulldog named Miss Asia Kinney. Miss Kinney is a pet model and has also appeared on television.</h3>\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1190\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/lady-gaga1.jpg\" alt=\"lady-gaga\" width=\"519\" height=\"518\" />','30 Celebrities And Their Cute Pets','','inherit','closed','closed','','656-autosave-v1','','','2017-03-12 10:37:41','2017-03-12 10:37:41','',656,'http://www.theladypost.com/2017/03/12/656-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(665,2,'2017-03-12 10:37:52','2017-03-12 10:37:52','<h1><span style=\"color: #ff0000;\"><strong>We all love pets, and celebrities are no different. Whether they show them to the world or not, these celebs have the cutest pets you can find.</strong></span></h1>\r\n<h1>Taylor Swift and Her Cats</h1>\r\n<h3>Taylor Swift, besides being a pop sensation, is a known cat enthusiast. Her cats are named Dr. Meredith Grey and Detective Olivia Benson. Both cats have flourishing Instagram accounts.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1199\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Taylor.png\" alt=\"taylor\" width=\"480\" height=\"475\" />\r\n\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Jennifer Lawrence and Pippi</h1>\r\n<h3>Jennifer Lawrence can\'t seem to do anything wrong, as the young talented actress enjoys incredible success over the past few years. She has a cute puppy called Pippi Lawrence who is very close to her heart.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-1187\" src=\"http://d2o8zujkt7hhe5.cloudfront.net/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/jen1.jpg\" alt=\"jen\" width=\"549\" height=\"549\" />\r\n<!--nextpage-->\r\n<h1>Cara Delevigne and Cecil The Bunny</h1>\r\n<h3>Cara Delevigne is a very successful young actor and model, but her bunny Cecil is successful in his own right. Cecil has a Twitter account as well as an Instagram account with thousands of followers on each one.</h3>\r\n<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-1206\" src=\"http: